Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.75,0:01:02.68,CHT,,0,0,0,,片名：彗星撞地球
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.24,0:01:19.43,CHT,,0,0,0,,“理查蒙鎮，維吉尼亞”
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.88,0:01:30.96,ENG,,0,0,0,,1.567 makes it eight degrees north.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.25,0:01:31.38,CHT,,0,0,0,,1.567位置在北方
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.50,0:01:34.67,ENG,,0,0,0,,Altair, Alpha Centauri and Sirius.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.99,0:01:35.15,CHT,,0,0,0,,牛郎星、天狼星…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.84,0:01:36.38,ENG,,0,0,0,,Matt Shepherd?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.25,0:01:36.65,CHT,,0,0,0,,麥特謝弗？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.01,0:01:39.18,ENG,,0,0,0,,It's just a party, and he asked me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.46,0:01:39.25,CHT,,0,0,0,,他邀我去舞會
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.26,0:01:41.89,ENG,,0,0,0,,- He's really nice. - Yeah, to you, maybe.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.56,0:01:41.86,CHT,,0,0,0,,他人不錯    我不認為
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.97,0:01:43.81,ENG,,0,0,0,,You guys getting some good work done over here?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.46,0:01:44.49,CHT,,0,0,0,,在專心觀察嗎？是的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.89,0:01:45.06,ENG,,0,0,0,,- Yeah. - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.13,0:01:45.79,CHT,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.14,0:01:47.23,ENG,,0,0,0,,Yeah, yeah. Sounds like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.90,0:01:47.53,CHT,,0,0,0,,我相信
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.39,0:01:49.27,ENG,,0,0,0,,What's the bright one?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.83,0:01:49.60,CHT,,0,0,0,,最亮的星叫什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.02,0:01:52.19,ENG,,0,0,0,,Mizar. It's a double star.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.40,0:01:52.74,CHT,,0,0,0,,開陽星，二星合一
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.36,0:01:54.36,ENG,,0,0,0,,Good. The one next to it?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.84,0:01:54.74,CHT,,0,0,0,,很好，旁邊那顆？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.94,0:01:57.36,ENG,,0,0,0,,- Alcor. - Good, Biederman.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.41,0:01:57.14,CHT,,0,0,0,,艾寇星
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.24,0:01:59.34,CHT,,0,0,0,,再旁邊呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.45,0:01:59.45,ENG,,0,0,0,,And the one next to that?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.70,0:02:04.74,ENG,,0,0,0,,- I don't know. - It's Megrez.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.05,0:02:05.14,CHT,,0,0,0,,不知道    麥癸星
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.83,0:02:07.75,ENG,,0,0,0,,- I don't think so. - Well, you just said you didn't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.25,0:02:06.48,CHT,,0,0,0,,不是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.65,0:02:08.18,CHT,,0,0,0,,你說不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.83,0:02:10.67,ENG,,0,0,0,,Well, it's not Megrez. It's something else.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.29,0:02:09.35,CHT,,0,0,0,,不是麥癸星
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.69,0:02:11.28,CHT,,0,0,0,,是別的星
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.25,0:02:12.38,ENG,,0,0,0,,Look.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.59,0:02:12.68,CHT,,0,0,0,,你看
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.30,0:02:16.51,ENG,,0,0,0,,It's south, about 10 degrees.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.70,0:02:17.29,CHT,,0,0,0,,在南方，10度左右
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.22,0:02:22.26,ENG,,0,0,0,,It's probably a satellite.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.54,0:02:21.76,CHT,,0,0,0,,也許是衛星
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.35,0:02:24.72,ENG,,0,0,0,,Let's take another picture. We'll send it to Dr. Wolf.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.77,0:02:25.07,CHT,,0,0,0,,拍照，寄給沃夫博士
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.85,0:02:26.10,ENG,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.17,0:02:26.16,CHT,,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.10,0:02:29.02,ENG,,0,0,0,,- It's Megrez. - It's not Megrez.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.48,0:02:29.14,CHT,,0,0,0,,是麥癸星  不是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.10,0:02:31.31,ENG,,0,0,0,,- It is. - It's not.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.61,0:02:31.55,CHT,,0,0,0,,是    不是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.65,0:02:36.82,ENG,,0,0,0,,It is.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.95,0:02:37.21,CHT,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.03,0:02:50.93,CHT,,0,0,0,,“亞歷桑那愛瑞恩天文台”
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.38,0:03:37.64,CHT,,0,0,0,,“李氏高中天文俱樂部”
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.91,0:04:02.47,CHT,,0,0,0,,“里歐畢德曼攝”
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.62,0:04:11.98,CHT,,0,0,0,,“不知名彗星，軌道未知”
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.50,0:04:19.84,ENG,,0,0,0,,Well, hello there, little fella.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.82,0:04:19.55,CHT,,0,0,0,,你好，小傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.21,0:04:21.71,ENG,,0,0,0,,Do I know you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.53,0:04:22.02,CHT,,0,0,0,,我認識你嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.68,0:04:26.22,ENG,,0,0,0,,Where are you going in such a hurry?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.90,0:04:25.89,CHT,,0,0,0,,急著去哪裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.18,0:04:31.52,ENG,,0,0,0,,And there.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.28,0:04:43.61,CHT,,0,0,0,,“環繞軌道”
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.47,0:05:01.73,CHT,,0,0,0,,“開啟電子郵件”
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.84,0:05:02.63,CHT,,0,0,0,,“伺服器關閉”
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.41,0:05:08.67,CHT,,0,0,0,,“傳送到磁碟機”
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.89,0:05:13.14,ENG,,0,0,0,,Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.25,0:05:12.98,CHT,,0,0,0,,快！可惡！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.08,0:05:13.88,CHT,,0,0,0,,“伺服器關閉”
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.39,0:05:14.64,ENG,,0,0,0,,Damn it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.98,0:05:14.64,CHT,,0,0,0,,媽的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.20,0:05:29.53,ENG,,0,0,0,,Biederman.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.56,0:05:29.22,CHT,,0,0,0,,畢德曼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.20,0:05:31.83,CHT,,0,0,0,,“沃夫一畢德曼”
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.26,0:05:53.81,ENG,,0,0,0,,Come on, you miserable piece of crap.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.59,0:05:54.49,CHT,,0,0,0,,快啊！爛電話
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.47,0:06:07.80,CHT,,0,0,0,,“提神可樂”
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.83,0:06:17.79,ENG,,0,0,0,,Come on, come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.35,0:06:18.18,CHT,,0,0,0,,快接通啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.26,0:06:32.68,ENG,,0,0,0,,You have reached the Department of Planetary Sciences.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.49,0:06:31.86,CHT,,0,0,0,,這裡是行星科學部
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.18,0:06:37.77,ENG,,0,0,0,,If you know the extension of the person you're calling...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.47,0:06:36.56,CHT,,0,0,0,,你如果知道所需內線…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.94,0:06:40.10,ENG,,0,0,0,,Jesus!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.81,0:06:40.57,CHT,,0,0,0,,請直撥分機號碼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.48,0:06:41.69,ENG,,0,0,0,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.71,0:06:41.47,CHT,,0,0,0,,可惡！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.33,0:07:05.67,ENG,,0,0,0,,News relating to the recall of American troops from abroad.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.38,0:07:07.61,CHT,,0,0,0,,“華府，一年後”
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.75,0:07:08.09,ENG,,0,0,0,,Tragedy struck today as a charter aircraft
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.72,0:07:12.12,CHT,,0,0,0,,美軍由日撤軍發生空難悲劇
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.17,0:07:11.76,ENG,,0,0,0,,carrying an Army unit returning from duty in Japan crashed this morning...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.68,0:07:15.85,ENG,,0,0,0,,The White House press office says Secretary of the Treasury Rittenhouse
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.99,0:07:13.98,CHT,,0,0,0,,財政部長…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.09,0:07:19.03,CHT,,0,0,0,,財政部長瑞頓豪因妻病而辭職
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.93,0:07:18.27,ENG,,0,0,0,,is resigning because his wife is sick.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.35,0:07:19.35,ENG,,0,0,0,,Sick, my ass.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.43,0:07:21.27,ENG,,0,0,0,,So, who passed Rittenhouse the hemlock?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.63,0:07:21.43,CHT,,0,0,0,,誰逼他下台的？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.35,0:07:24.69,ENG,,0,0,0,,AFL-CIO wanted him off the Council of Economic Advisers
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.53,0:07:25.47,CHT,,0,0,0,,工聯會與產協會都要他下台
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.77,0:07:26.27,ENG,,0,0,0,,for not supporting the pension bill,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.57,0:07:28.70,CHT,,0,0,0,,總統大選需要勞工票
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.36,0:07:28.40,ENG,,0,0,0,,and the President's going to need Labor next fall.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.49,0:07:31.82,ENG,,0,0,0,,And State's still fuming about the Trade Office screw-up at the G8.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.84,0:07:32.07,CHT,,0,0,0,,他在經濟高峰會的表現失策
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.91,0:07:34.49,ENG,,0,0,0,,Pentagon is unhappy with his readiness reduction proposals.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.18,0:07:34.97,CHT,,0,0,0,,國防部不滿他刪減預算
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.57,0:07:38.49,ENG,,0,0,0,,- Greenspan dislikes him. - Christ! Who didn't this guy piss off?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.08,0:07:36.48,CHT,,0,0,0,,葛士班討厭他
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.78,0:07:38.87,CHT,,0,0,0,,都被他得罪光了！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.58,0:07:42.29,ENG,,0,0,0,,- No wonder the wife's sick. - She's not sick. She's a drunk.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.02,0:07:40.57,CHT,,0,0,0,,難怪太太生病
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.75,0:07:42.81,CHT,,0,0,0,,沒生病，她是酒鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.84,0:07:47.63,ENG,,0,0,0,,How do you know that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.09,0:07:47.15,CHT,,0,0,0,,你怎麼知道？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.71,0:07:50.05,ENG,,0,0,0,,Mike Woodward over at Treasury.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.73,0:07:49.85,CHT,,0,0,0,,財政部的麥克伍華告訴我的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.39,0:07:55.80,ENG,,0,0,0,,Mrs. Rittenhouse started drinking a couple of years ago
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.70,0:07:58.07,CHT,,0,0,0,,他太太因他的外遇而酗酒
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.89,0:07:57.89,ENG,,0,0,0,,when her husband had a series of affairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.97,0:08:01.68,ENG,,0,0,0,,Stepped it up last summer after their son died of leukemia.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.17,0:08:00.93,CHT,,0,0,0,,兒子死於白血病後更糟
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.23,0:08:04.23,ENG,,0,0,0,,You wanna do something on "the price that wives pay"?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.64,0:08:05.20,CHT,,0,0,0,,要採訪相關報導？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.31,0:08:05.98,ENG,,0,0,0,,- What else? - Mike Woodward?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.31,0:08:07.68,CHT,,0,0,0,,麥克伍華？3個孩子的爹？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.06,0:08:08.65,ENG,,0,0,0,,- Wife, three kids? - He's been after me for months,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.78,0:08:09.01,CHT,,0,0,0,,他最近在追我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.73,0:08:12.40,ENG,,0,0,0,,so I threw him a breakfast and hit him up about Rittenhouse.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.11,0:08:12.41,CHT,,0,0,0,,共進早餐時談到瑞頓豪
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.49,0:08:13.95,ENG,,0,0,0,,Bob Campbell's leaving.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.82,0:08:16.75,CHT,,0,0,0,,巴布離職，週末主播從缺
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.03,0:08:16.49,ENG,,0,0,0,,So at midnight Saturday, anchor shift's opening up.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.58,0:08:18.99,ENG,,0,0,0,,Why would I wanna give up the White House for a graveyard weekend?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.86,0:08:19.22,CHT,,0,0,0,,我幹嘛要去做？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.08,0:08:21.41,ENG,,0,0,0,,No, no, no. Not for you. For me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.32,0:08:21.38,CHT,,0,0,0,,不是你，是我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.66,0:08:23.00,ENG,,0,0,0,,- No. - Beth.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.46,0:08:23.72,CHT,,0,0,0,,白宮，貝絲？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.58,0:08:25.50,ENG,,0,0,0,,We'll talk about this later. Very calm.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.83,0:08:24.99,CHT,,0,0,0,,待會再說
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.10,0:08:28.16,CHT,,0,0,0,,沒事，總統明天回華府
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.58,0:08:27.79,ENG,,0,0,0,,The President will be back from Camp David tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.88,0:08:29.46,ENG,,0,0,0,,- Business news, lra? - Beth.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.30,0:08:29.63,CHT,,0,0,0,,商業新聞，艾拉？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.55,0:08:31.96,ENG,,0,0,0,,You know what? Just keep working on Rittenhouse.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.94,0:08:32.27,CHT,,0,0,0,,繼續打探消息
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.05,0:08:34.22,ENG,,0,0,0,,Maybe Mike's available for dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.37,0:08:34.64,CHT,,0,0,0,,吃頓交際晚餐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.30,0:08:37.85,ENG,,0,0,0,,You know, do the usual research, background information.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.74,0:08:37.94,CHT,,0,0,0,,探查基本資料、背景
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.93,0:08:41.52,ENG,,0,0,0,,- I'll talk to you about it after lunch. - Okay. That's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.45,0:08:41.54,CHT,,0,0,0,,好了，散會
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.48,0:08:44.89,ENG,,0,0,0,,Beth, wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.68,0:08:44.88,CHT,,0,0,0,,貝絲，等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.10,0:08:48.94,ENG,,0,0,0,,- Listen, Beth, what if it wasn't... - God, Jenny.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.32,0:08:49.85,CHT,,0,0,0,,聽我說，只是短期…珍妮，拜託
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.02,0:08:51.40,ENG,,0,0,0,,- ...permanent? - Look, honey, this is how it works.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.92,0:08:53.12,CHT,,0,0,0,,運作方式是…做2年採訪
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.48,0:08:54.74,ENG,,0,0,0,,You've done two years of research. Now do three as a segment producer,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.23,0:08:55.02,CHT,,0,0,0,,3年編輯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.82,0:08:56.86,ENG,,0,0,0,,five on-air doing domestic features,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.13,0:09:00.07,CHT,,0,0,0,,5年國內新聞報導2年駐訪落後地區
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.95,0:08:59.87,ENG,,0,0,0,,another two in some cholera-ridden hellhole,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.95,0:09:01.20,ENG,,0,0,0,,and then, you know what?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.17,0:09:03.83,CHT,,0,0,0,,我保證你能當週末主播
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.29,0:09:03.54,ENG,,0,0,0,,I'll quit if they don't give you a weekend anchor shot.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.62,0:09:05.58,ENG,,0,0,0,,Hello, Caitlin, there you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.94,0:09:05.84,CHT,,0,0,0,,凱特琳
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.67,0:09:08.33,ENG,,0,0,0,,Are you protecting me or just holding me back?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.94,0:09:08.74,CHT,,0,0,0,,你是保護我還是嚇阻我？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.42,0:09:09.79,ENG,,0,0,0,,- Yes. - Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.84,0:09:10.24,CHT,,0,0,0,,都有
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.92,0:09:13.30,ENG,,0,0,0,,Rittenhouse tape and text on my desk by 4:00 tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.34,0:09:13.71,CHT,,0,0,0,,明天4點給我瑞頓豪資料
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.38,0:09:14.84,ENG,,0,0,0,,- Yes. - Then we'll drop in the reverses
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.82,0:09:15.68,CHT,,0,0,0,,趕上5點新聞
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.93,0:09:16.68,ENG,,0,0,0,,- for the five. - Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.78,0:09:17.05,CHT,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.89,0:09:20.68,ENG,,0,0,0,,So at this moment right now...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.19,0:09:21.02,CHT,,0,0,0,,在這個時候…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.76,0:09:23.68,ENG,,0,0,0,,Thank you. The pretty little girls are walking down the aisle.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.12,0:09:21.78,CHT,,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.89,0:09:25.45,CHT,,0,0,0,,美麗的小女孩走來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.77,0:09:25.06,ENG,,0,0,0,,They're spreading flowers.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.14,0:09:27.14,ENG,,0,0,0,,- The twins, what are their names? - Emma and Susanna.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.56,0:09:28.79,CHT,,0,0,0,,雙胞胎艾瑪與蘇珊娜
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.23,0:09:29.77,ENG,,0,0,0,,They're walking down the aisles and they're dropping rose petals,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.90,0:09:31.42,CHT,,0,0,0,,她們走在紅毯上灑花瓣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.86,0:09:32.36,ENG,,0,0,0,,- and everyone's smiling at them. - Mother, is this really such a good idea?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.53,0:09:34.02,CHT,,0,0,0,,人人面帶微笑，新娘出場
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.44,0:09:34.03,ENG,,0,0,0,,- Now she's walking down the aisle. Yes. - Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.11,0:09:38.28,ENG,,0,0,0,,And she stands beside him. And the priest says, "Dearly beloved..."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.14,0:09:36.07,CHT,,0,0,0,,她站在他身旁
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.24,0:09:39.37,CHT,,0,0,0,,牧師說…法官，是法官
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.37,0:09:40.57,ENG,,0,0,0,,- Judge. - And the judge says...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.48,0:09:43.17,CHT,,0,0,0,,法官說了一大堆、生病健康
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.28,0:09:44.87,ENG,,0,0,0,,...sickness and health... "Do you, Jason Lerner, take..."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.28,0:09:46.34,CHT,,0,0,0,,傑森你願意娶…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.08,0:09:47.96,ENG,,0,0,0,,"...Chlorine Whatchamacallit?"
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.45,0:09:48.61,CHT,,0,0,0,,克露“妖”什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.04,0:09:49.46,ENG,,0,0,0,,- Mom! - What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.72,0:09:50.48,CHT,,0,0,0,,媽，是克露伊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.54,0:09:51.34,ENG,,0,0,0,,- Chloe. - What did I say?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.79,0:09:51.84,CHT,,0,0,0,,我說什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.42,0:09:54.76,ENG,,0,0,0,,You said... You said, "Chlorine." Her name's Chloe.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.95,0:09:55.75,CHT,,0,0,0,,你說克露妖，是克露伊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.68,0:10:00.39,ENG,,0,0,0,,- Well, it's still a terrible name. - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.99,0:10:00.26,CHT,,0,0,0,,都很難聽
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.85,0:10:04.77,ENG,,0,0,0,,And Jason says, "Lie, lie, lie, lie, till death do us part."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.93,0:10:05.66,CHT,,0,0,0,,傑森說一堆謊，至死不渝
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.48,0:10:07.06,ENG,,0,0,0,,And she says, "Yes," and he says, "Yes,"
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.77,0:10:07.46,CHT,,0,0,0,,然後她願意、他願意
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.14,0:10:10.31,ENG,,0,0,0,,and it's kissy, kissy, kissy and congratulations.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.60,0:10:10.33,CHT,,0,0,0,,吻來吻去，完成婚禮
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.15,0:10:20.53,ENG,,0,0,0,,Jenny, you now have a new stepmother who is two years older than you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.38,0:10:20.84,CHT,,0,0,0,,珍妮，你後母只比你大兩歲
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.33,0:10:24.49,ENG,,0,0,0,,Check.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.49,0:10:24.48,CHT,,0,0,0,,買單
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.00,0:10:28.96,ENG,,0,0,0,,Well, anyway, as much as I would like to stay here and get silly with you, Mom,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.36,0:10:29.16,CHT,,0,0,0,,我想陪你喝醉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.04,0:10:32.04,ENG,,0,0,0,,- I can't. I gotta go. - I know, I know, I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.26,0:10:30.78,CHT,,0,0,0,,但我有事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.90,0:10:32.73,CHT,,0,0,0,,我了解
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.01,0:10:36.80,ENG,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.30,0:10:37.60,CHT,,0,0,0,,我很遺憾
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.47,0:10:39.72,ENG,,0,0,0,,We'll get over it. I love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.70,0:10:39.79,CHT,,0,0,0,,我沒事，愛你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.72,0:10:43.26,ENG,,0,0,0,,I love you, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.17,0:10:43.47,CHT,,0,0,0,,我也愛你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.52,0:10:47.73,ENG,,0,0,0,,Be good.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.84,0:10:48.04,CHT,,0,0,0,,要乖喔
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.07,0:10:57.36,ENG,,0,0,0,,I was with the secretary since he's been governor of Connecticut.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.25,0:10:57.71,CHT,,0,0,0,,瑞頓豪當州長我就跟著他
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.44,0:10:59.57,ENG,,0,0,0,,Came to Washington with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.86,0:11:00.59,CHT,,0,0,0,,他帶我來華府
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.74,0:11:02.99,ENG,,0,0,0,,I moved here because I was dedicated to his career.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.69,0:11:05.13,CHT,,0,0,0,,我全心奉獻他的事業信任他
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.07,0:11:04.74,ENG,,0,0,0,,I trusted the man.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.58,0:11:07.45,ENG,,0,0,0,,And then he fucked me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.96,0:11:07.90,CHT,,0,0,0,,他卻搞我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.87,0:11:10.12,ENG,,0,0,0,,- He what? - No, I didn't have sex with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.00,0:11:08.73,CHT,,0,0,0,,他什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.10,0:11:11.63,CHT,,0,0,0,,不，不是性交
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.21,0:11:14.17,ENG,,0,0,0,,I should say, I didn't have sex with him, but somebody sure did.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.74,0:11:14.80,CHT,,0,0,0,,不是跟我，另有其人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.42,0:11:17.13,ENG,,0,0,0,,It was about to come out, so he resigned.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.91,0:11:17.60,CHT,,0,0,0,,醜聞將爆發，所以辭職
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.21,0:11:20.67,ENG,,0,0,0,,But because I was hired from outside the government pool,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.71,0:11:21.01,CHT,,0,0,0,,因為我不是政府雇員
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.76,0:11:24.76,ENG,,0,0,0,,I don't get conveyed to the next secretary, so now I'm out a job.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.11,0:11:24.31,CHT,,0,0,0,,不能轉任他人秘書，失業了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.68,0:11:28.60,ENG,,0,0,0,,Because he couldn't keep his hands off women.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.05,0:11:29.02,CHT,,0,0,0,,只因他沉迷女色
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.56,0:11:33.98,ENG,,0,0,0,,- Do you have proof? - He thinks he was being so clever.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.89,0:11:32.26,CHT,,0,0,0,,有證據？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.36,0:11:34.42,CHT,,0,0,0,,她自以為聰明
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.65,0:11:37.52,ENG,,0,0,0,,He had a private phone line installed in his office.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.03,0:11:39.90,CHT,,0,0,0,,他有個秘密電話別人不准接
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.61,0:11:39.53,ENG,,0,0,0,,Nobody else could answer it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.61,0:11:43.28,ENG,,0,0,0,,I picked it up once, said hello, and it's nobody home.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.97,0:11:44.30,CHT,,0,0,0,,有一回我接起來，沒人說話
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.28,0:11:47.58,ENG,,0,0,0,,It rings, he shuts the door. Why not hang a sign?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.71,0:11:48.80,CHT,,0,0,0,,電話響就關門，太明顯了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.87,0:11:50.62,ENG,,0,0,0,,Do you have a name?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.14,0:11:50.58,CHT,,0,0,0,,知道她是誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.00,0:11:53.75,ENG,,0,0,0,,This is what I get for talking to the press.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.25,0:11:54.21,CHT,,0,0,0,,接受採訪的代價
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.83,0:11:58.30,ENG,,0,0,0,,I'm selling my soul right now. I can feel it. I can feel it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.31,0:11:59.25,CHT,,0,0,0,,我出賣靈魂，我感覺得到
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.59,0:12:01.55,ENG,,0,0,0,,I name a name and get someone into trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.92,0:12:01.86,CHT,,0,0,0,,說出名字就有人遭殃
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.63,0:12:03.22,ENG,,0,0,0,,So you do have a name.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.96,0:12:02.95,CHT,,0,0,0,,你知道她是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.30,0:12:06.60,ENG,,0,0,0,,Just a first name. Oh, my God, I'm going to say it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.59,0:12:07.19,CHT,,0,0,0,,只知道名字，天！我要說了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.97,0:12:08.14,ENG,,0,0,0,,Ellie.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.26,0:12:08.46,CHT,,0,0,0,,艾麗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.35,0:12:11.14,ENG,,0,0,0,,Ellie? Nothing else?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.60,0:12:12.29,CHT,,0,0,0,,艾麗？還有呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.19,0:12:14.48,ENG,,0,0,0,,I think the President knows about it, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.47,0:12:14.99,CHT,,0,0,0,,總統也知道她
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.56,0:12:17.73,ENG,,0,0,0,,Overheard the secretary talking to him about her.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.10,0:12:18.10,CHT,,0,0,0,,國務卿跟總統談過她
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.15,0:12:19.98,ENG,,0,0,0,,Isn't Washington sick?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.31,0:12:19.86,CHT,,0,0,0,,政府官員都有病
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.65,0:13:01.69,ENG,,0,0,0,,Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.69,0:13:04.19,ENG,,0,0,0,,How you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.02,0:13:03.99,CHT,,0,0,0,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.53,0:13:06.03,ENG,,0,0,0,,Can I help you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.95,0:13:06.25,CHT,,0,0,0,,有事嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.11,0:13:09.70,ENG,,0,0,0,,Well, actually, we're looking for your mom. Is she around?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.56,0:13:10.12,CHT,,0,0,0,,我想找令堂，她在嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.87,0:13:12.12,ENG,,0,0,0,,My mom's sick. She's not here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.26,0:13:12.23,CHT,,0,0,0,,她病了，不在
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.33,0:13:16.25,ENG,,0,0,0,,Gosh, I love boats. Are you going on a trip?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.60,0:13:16.76,CHT,,0,0,0,,我喜歡船！要去旅行？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.58,0:13:17.71,ENG,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.87,0:13:17.89,CHT,,0,0,0,,對
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.21,0:13:20.59,ENG,,0,0,0,,That's exciting. Looks like a...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.54,0:13:23.60,CHT,,0,0,0,,真刺激，看來…是長期旅行
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.92,0:13:22.96,ENG,,0,0,0,,Like a long trip, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.55,0:13:26.47,ENG,,0,0,0,,So listen, do you know where you're going?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.81,0:13:26.87,CHT,,0,0,0,,你們要去哪裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.55,0:13:28.76,ENG,,0,0,0,,She's going back to the house.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.98,0:13:28.44,CHT,,0,0,0,,她要回屋裡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.89,0:13:30.89,ENG,,0,0,0,,Hey. You wanna stop that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.28,0:13:31.15,CHT,,0,0,0,,別拍了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.39,0:13:32.89,ENG,,0,0,0,,Lily, please?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.68,0:13:33.41,CHT,,0,0,0,,莉莉，請進去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.18,0:13:35.27,ENG,,0,0,0,,Lily, that's a pretty name.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.52,0:13:34.78,CHT,,0,0,0,,莉莉，真好聽
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.06,0:13:38.19,ENG,,0,0,0,,Lily, do as I say.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.29,0:13:40.19,CHT,,0,0,0,,莉莉，聽話，進去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.69,0:13:39.81,ENG,,0,0,0,,Go on. I'll be right there.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.90,0:13:42.15,ENG,,0,0,0,,If we could just get a minute of your time.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.29,0:13:42.49,CHT,,0,0,0,,打擾你一下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.23,0:13:43.78,ENG,,0,0,0,,What do you want from me?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.59,0:13:43.99,CHT,,0,0,0,,什麼事？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.86,0:13:46.32,ENG,,0,0,0,,Well, we'd like to talk about your resignation.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.26,0:13:46.70,CHT,,0,0,0,,關於辭職的事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.40,0:13:48.74,ENG,,0,0,0,,My wife is sick. She's in the hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.80,0:13:51.57,CHT,,0,0,0,,內人生病住院，所以辭職
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.82,0:13:51.33,ENG,,0,0,0,,That's why I resigned. Everybody knows this.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.41,0:13:55.41,ENG,,0,0,0,,We could talk about your wife, or we could just talk about Ellie.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.67,0:13:55.30,CHT,,0,0,0,,要談太座還是艾麗？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.43,0:14:10.26,ENG,,0,0,0,,Turn the camera off.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.69,0:14:09.99,CHT,,0,0,0,,關掉攝影機
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.55,0:14:12.93,ENG,,0,0,0,,If you wanna talk to me, turn it off.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.86,0:14:13.22,CHT,,0,0,0,,要談就得關機
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.01,0:14:14.22,ENG,,0,0,0,,Cut it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.77,0:14:18.81,ENG,,0,0,0,,- We know everything. - Nobody knows everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.06,0:14:17.55,CHT,,0,0,0,,我們全都知道
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.66,0:14:19.53,CHT,,0,0,0,,沒人能全都知道
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.48,0:14:22.52,ENG,,0,0,0,,Well, we know about the secret phone lines
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.87,0:14:22.86,CHT,,0,0,0,,我們知道…你用秘密電話
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.61,0:14:25.32,ENG,,0,0,0,,and the whispered calls to the President.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.97,0:14:27.37,CHT,,0,0,0,,與總統聯絡你身為財政部長…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.44,0:14:28.86,ENG,,0,0,0,,And about a secretary of the Treasury who's kept his entire department
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.47,0:14:31.14,CHT,,0,0,0,,背著屬下的醜聞
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.95,0:14:32.66,ENG,,0,0,0,,in the dark about what he's really doing, about a cover story
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.25,0:14:34.81,CHT,,0,0,0,,辭職的真正原因
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.74,0:14:34.54,ENG,,0,0,0,,about his resignation that just fell through.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.62,0:14:37.04,ENG,,0,0,0,,I mean, sir, you want me to go on?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.92,0:14:36.94,CHT,,0,0,0,,要我繼續？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.66,0:14:39.96,ENG,,0,0,0,,And you're just gonna break it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.99,0:14:40.22,CHT,,0,0,0,,你要發佈新聞？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.79,0:14:42.88,ENG,,0,0,0,,Well, that's what we do for a living.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.22,0:14:43.02,CHT,,0,0,0,,這是記者的職責
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.96,0:14:44.80,ENG,,0,0,0,,Well, congratulations.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.02,0:14:48.12,CHT,,0,0,0,,恭喜，天大的新聞
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.67,0:14:48.26,ENG,,0,0,0,,You now have the biggest story in history.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.34,0:14:49.97,ENG,,0,0,0,,Good luck to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.80,0:14:51.20,CHT,,0,0,0,,祝好運，我認為…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.13,0:14:53.05,ENG,,0,0,0,,Personally, I think it's a mistake to run the story,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.90,0:14:53.70,CHT,,0,0,0,,不應該報導
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.14,0:14:55.10,ENG,,0,0,0,,but, hey, what the hell?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.80,0:14:56.97,CHT,,0,0,0,,但管他的！有何不可？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.43,0:14:56.64,ENG,,0,0,0,,Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.14,0:15:00.98,ENG,,0,0,0,,What difference does anything make anymore?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.44,0:15:00.96,CHT,,0,0,0,,報不報導有何差別？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.73,0:15:07.82,ENG,,0,0,0,,Look.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.02,0:15:11.32,CHT,,0,0,0,,聽我說…我知道你是記者
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.90,0:15:11.15,ENG,,0,0,0,,I know you're just a reporter,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.66,0:15:14.32,ENG,,0,0,0,,but you used to be a person, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.89,0:15:15.69,CHT,,0,0,0,,但也曾是平凡人，對嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.50,0:15:22.71,ENG,,0,0,0,,I wanted to be with my family.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.76,0:15:23.73,CHT,,0,0,0,,我想與家人共度
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.55,0:15:27.50,ENG,,0,0,0,,Can you understand that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.84,0:15:27.74,CHT,,0,0,0,,你能諒解嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.28,0:15:51.90,ENG,,0,0,0,,Okay, Secretary of the Treasury Alan Rittenhouse resigns
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.69,0:15:54.43,CHT,,0,0,0,,財政部長瑞頓豪…辭職是因為情婦艾麗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.99,0:15:54.41,ENG,,0,0,0,,because of a mistress named Ellie.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.70,0:15:56.70,ENG,,0,0,0,,Biggest story in history?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.13,0:15:57.62,CHT,,0,0,0,,天大的新聞？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.04,0:15:59.41,ENG,,0,0,0,,What an ego.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.27,0:15:59.90,CHT,,0,0,0,,好狂妄
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.95,0:16:02.25,ENG,,0,0,0,,Now, if it was the President...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.24,0:16:03.23,CHT,,0,0,0,,若是總統…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.17,0:16:06.08,ENG,,0,0,0,,Okay, the President has a mistress named Ellie,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.34,0:16:06.54,CHT,,0,0,0,,總統有個情婦叫艾麗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.17,0:16:08.00,ENG,,0,0,0,,and Rittenhouse pretends that he's having the affair
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.64,0:16:10.27,CHT,,0,0,0,,瑞頓豪替總統背黑鍋辭職
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.09,0:16:12.88,ENG,,0,0,0,,and takes the fall and resigns, and the President buys him a yacht?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.38,0:16:13.75,CHT,,0,0,0,,總統送他游艇？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.64,0:16:16.22,ENG,,0,0,0,,Son of a bitch!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.95,0:16:16.28,CHT,,0,0,0,,渾蛋！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.69,0:16:25.35,ENG,,0,0,0,,Shit. Shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.06,0:16:23.79,CHT,,0,0,0,,慘了！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.66,0:16:25.89,CHT,,0,0,0,,慘了…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.44,0:16:28.27,ENG,,0,0,0,,What? Okay, okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.40,0:16:28.87,CHT,,0,0,0,,好！好…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.23,0:16:31.36,ENG,,0,0,0,,God. No, God.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.33,0:16:31.53,CHT,,0,0,0,,天啊！天…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.92,0:16:54.63,ENG,,0,0,0,,FBI. if you would please, ma'am?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.23,0:16:54.72,CHT,,0,0,0,,調查局，請跟我來
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.72,0:16:56.26,ENG,,0,0,0,,- What do I do with the car? - We'll take care of the car.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.89,0:16:57.86,CHT,,0,0,0,,我的車？上我的車
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.34,0:16:57.80,ENG,,0,0,0,,Just step back to my car.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.89,0:16:59.93,ENG,,0,0,0,,- Get her car here. - Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.26,0:16:59.53,CHT,,0,0,0,,開她的車
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.81,0:17:08.11,ENG,,0,0,0,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.07,0:17:08.06,CHT,,0,0,0,,走
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.54,0:17:23.87,ENG,,0,0,0,,Would you come this way, please?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.79,0:17:23.12,CHT,,0,0,0,,請跟我來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.26,0:17:39.43,ENG,,0,0,0,,Morton Entrekin, Ms. Lerner.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.37,0:17:40.04,CHT,,0,0,0,,我是摩根，藍納小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.64,0:17:43.31,ENG,,0,0,0,,I'm expected back at MSNBC at 6:00,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.81,0:17:44.11,CHT,,0,0,0,,我該在6點趕回電視台
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.48,0:17:46.18,ENG,,0,0,0,,and I think I should be there.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.55,0:17:46.41,CHT,,0,0,0,,他們在等我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.27,0:17:48.77,ENG,,0,0,0,,People knew about the Manhattan Project, you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.52,0:17:51.01,CHT,,0,0,0,,人們知道曼哈頓計劃但三緘其口
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.86,0:17:50.86,ENG,,0,0,0,,and they kept it a secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.98,0:17:54.86,ENG,,0,0,0,,That was just the creation of the atom bomb.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.26,0:17:56.09,CHT,,0,0,0,,不過是製造原子彈計劃
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.85,0:18:24.81,ENG,,0,0,0,,Ms. Lerner? Tom Beck.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.29,0:18:25.38,CHT,,0,0,0,,藍納小姐，我是湯姆貝克
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.14,0:18:27.52,ENG,,0,0,0,,I understand you've come into some information.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.49,0:18:27.89,CHT,,0,0,0,,聽說你掌握重大新聞
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.60,0:18:30.27,ENG,,0,0,0,,Ms. Lerner was just expressing her lack of enthusiasm
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.99,0:18:30.59,CHT,,0,0,0,,藍納表示不在乎國家安全
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.35,0:18:35.19,ENG,,0,0,0,,for matters of national security where journalistic competitiveness is at stake.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.70,0:18:35.66,CHT,,0,0,0,,只關心新聞競爭
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.19,0:18:40.49,ENG,,0,0,0,,Mr. President, I'm not interested in using Ellie to further my career.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.37,0:18:40.40,CHT,,0,0,0,,總統先生，我不想藉艾麗成名
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.70,0:18:42.95,ENG,,0,0,0,,What do you know about E.L.E.?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.04,0:18:42.53,CHT,,0,0,0,,你對ELE了解多少？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.20,0:18:49.21,ENG,,0,0,0,,I know you should have picked a better cover story than a sick wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.48,0:18:49.47,CHT,,0,0,0,,藉口要比妻子生病更好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.29,0:18:51.21,ENG,,0,0,0,,See? What'd I tell you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.58,0:18:51.88,CHT,,0,0,0,,看！我就說吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.21,0:18:56.13,ENG,,0,0,0,,We'd always thought the deadline for going public
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.32,0:18:58.15,CHT,,0,0,0,,原以為將因超支預算而曝光
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.21,0:18:57.80,ENG,,0,0,0,,was the publication of the budget,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.88,0:19:00.47,ENG,,0,0,0,,since we've spent more money than we can hide.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.26,0:19:00.85,CHT,,0,0,0,,龐大的超支
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.55,0:19:03.14,ENG,,0,0,0,,But the budget comes out in two weeks.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.96,0:19:03.36,CHT,,0,0,0,,兩週後會曝光
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.22,0:19:07.31,ENG,,0,0,0,,I don't suppose I could convince you to sit on this for two weeks.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.46,0:19:07.63,CHT,,0,0,0,,你能暫時隱瞞兩週？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.39,0:19:11.35,ENG,,0,0,0,,No such thing as two weeks in the news business.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.74,0:19:11.76,CHT,,0,0,0,,新聞怎能拖延兩週？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.44,0:19:15.90,ENG,,0,0,0,,And I can't appeal to your sense of what's in the nation's best interest.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.87,0:19:15.00,CHT,,0,0,0,,你關心國家利益嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.07,0:19:20.20,ENG,,0,0,0,,Well, I always thought the truth was in the nation's best interest.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.28,0:19:19.71,CHT,,0,0,0,,真相才是國家利益
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.87,0:19:24.57,ENG,,0,0,0,,You wanna hold her?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.12,0:19:24.61,CHT,,0,0,0,,要拘禁她？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.83,0:19:30.75,ENG,,0,0,0,,What if we go public in 48 hours? Now, that's doable, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.05,0:19:31.12,CHT,,0,0,0,,48小時後公佈，可行嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.25,0:19:33.12,ENG,,0,0,0,,That would be very difficult, Mr. President.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.43,0:19:33.19,CHT,,0,0,0,,將很困難
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.21,0:19:34.25,ENG,,0,0,0,,Morton,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.39,0:19:36.46,CHT,,0,0,0,,摩根，若她知情
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.34,0:19:38.76,ENG,,0,0,0,,if she knows, how long can it be before CNN or The Post breaks the story?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.56,0:19:39.73,CHT,,0,0,0,,消息也將很快走漏
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.92,0:19:44.14,ENG,,0,0,0,,Now, this was never gonna be a secret as long as you wanted it to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.30,0:19:43.60,CHT,,0,0,0,,再不情願秘密仍將被揭露
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.64,0:19:47.06,ENG,,0,0,0,,Give us two days, Ms. Lerner.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.81,0:19:50.71,CHT,,0,0,0,,給我兩天記者會給你最佳採訪位置
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.14,0:19:50.56,ENG,,0,0,0,,You'll get second-row center at the White House press conference.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.64,0:19:52.81,ENG,,0,0,0,,Now, from what I know of your career, that's a promotion.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.98,0:19:53.14,CHT,,0,0,0,,是你升遷的良機
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.90,0:19:55.90,ENG,,0,0,0,,- I want exclusivity. - Now, listen, young lady,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.25,0:19:54.55,CHT,,0,0,0,,我要獨家報導
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.65,0:19:58.92,CHT,,0,0,0,,聽好，小姐…這是總統的恩惠
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.90,0:19:59.11,ENG,,0,0,0,,this is a presidential favor.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.53,0:20:02.36,ENG,,0,0,0,,I'm letting you go because I don't want another headache,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.76,0:20:02.66,CHT,,0,0,0,,放你走因我不想添麻煩
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.45,0:20:06.70,ENG,,0,0,0,,and I'm trusting you because I know what this can do for your career.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.76,0:20:06.59,CHT,,0,0,0,,信任你因為事關你升遷
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.12,0:20:09.87,ENG,,0,0,0,,It might seem that we have each other over the same barrel, Ms. Lerner,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.36,0:20:10.26,CHT,,0,0,0,,表面上你未蒙其利
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.95,0:20:12.12,ENG,,0,0,0,,but it just seems that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.37,0:20:13.10,CHT,,0,0,0,,其實不然
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.21,0:20:20.13,ENG,,0,0,0,,- I want the... - "Want"?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.31,0:20:20.10,CHT,,0,0,0,,我要…    你要？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.08,0:20:25.34,CHT,,0,0,0,,我能…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.09,0:20:24.26,ENG,,0,0,0,,May I?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.14,0:20:27.35,ENG,,0,0,0,,May I have the first question?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.45,0:20:27.78,CHT,,0,0,0,,第一個發問嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.72,0:20:31.14,ENG,,0,0,0,,I'll see you Tuesday, Ms. Lerner.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.99,0:20:30.98,CHT,,0,0,0,,週二再見了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.06,0:20:41.03,CHT,,0,0,0,,“搜尋”    “ELE艾麗”
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.94,0:20:52.34,CHT,,0,0,0,,“艾麗旅行社”
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.44,0:20:53.88,CHT,,0,0,0,,“艾麗斐潔洛”
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.29,0:20:56.33,ENG,,0,0,0,,Come on. Come on, come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.55,0:20:56.81,CHT,,0,0,0,,快啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.01,0:21:10.35,ENG,,0,0,0,,E-L-E, E-L-E.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.39,0:21:11.52,CHT,,0,0,0,,艾麗，ELE
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.43,0:21:11.43,ENG,,0,0,0,,E.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.07,0:21:14.93,CHT,,0,0,0,,“ELE縮寫”
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.00,0:21:16.26,CHT,,0,0,0,,“搜尋”
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.19,0:21:19.40,ENG,,0,0,0,,Paleontology.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.57,0:21:20.60,CHT,,0,0,0,,“柏克萊大學古生物學系”
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.48,0:21:23.32,ENG,,0,0,0,,Paleontology. What does paleontology have to do with anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.71,0:21:23.50,CHT,,0,0,0,,跟古生物學何干？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.18,0:21:25.47,CHT,,0,0,0,,快啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.20,0:21:25.20,ENG,,0,0,0,,Come on. Come on, come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.55,0:21:31.85,CHT,,0,0,0,,“地球滅絕研究”
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.29,0:21:35.02,CHT,,0,0,0,,“ELE：地球滅絕事件”
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.02,0:21:39.99,CHT,,0,0,0,,“生物大量滅絕”
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.56,0:21:43.05,CHT,,0,0,0,,“小行星或彗星”
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.06,0:21:46.40,CHT,,0,0,0,,“導致種族滅絕的事件”
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.72,0:21:48.26,ENG,,0,0,0,,- Hey! - Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.72,0:21:50.43,ENG,,0,0,0,,- Look who's working late. - Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.80,0:21:50.29,CHT,,0,0,0,,還在加班啊！  是的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.51,0:21:53.72,ENG,,0,0,0,,- How's Rittenhouse going? - No sign of the wife yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.80,0:21:52.03,CHT,,0,0,0,,調查得如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.14,0:21:54.00,CHT,,0,0,0,,沒找到他太太
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.81,0:21:56.35,ENG,,0,0,0,,- Is she missing? - No. We're still working on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.11,0:21:54.90,CHT,,0,0,0,,她失蹤了？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.01,0:21:56.94,CHT,,0,0,0,,不，還在調查
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.44,0:21:58.10,ENG,,0,0,0,,- We'll get there. - I know. it's a dull story.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.04,0:22:00.74,CHT,,0,0,0,,我知道很無聊保證下次給你較好的題材
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.19,0:22:01.98,ENG,,0,0,0,,I promise you, next time we'll get you something more exciting.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.07,0:22:03.27,ENG,,0,0,0,,Great.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.25,0:22:03.38,CHT,,0,0,0,,好！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.69,0:22:05.19,ENG,,0,0,0,,- Are you okay? - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.92,0:22:05.48,CHT,,0,0,0,,你還好吧？    我很好
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.28,0:22:09.49,ENG,,0,0,0,,- Wanna come to dinner with us? - I can't, I can't. I got... l have plans.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.59,0:22:07.05,CHT,,0,0,0,,一起吃晚餐？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.15,0:22:09.71,CHT,,0,0,0,,不了，我有約會
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.57,0:22:12.08,ENG,,0,0,0,,Okay. Well, we'll see you tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.82,0:22:11.38,CHT,,0,0,0,,好，明天見
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.75,0:22:23.88,ENG,,0,0,0,,- This is your table. - Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.74,0:22:29.11,CHT,,0,0,0,,她來了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.80,0:22:29.26,ENG,,0,0,0,,Here she is.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.09,0:22:31.26,ENG,,0,0,0,,Jenny.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.28,0:22:31.54,CHT,,0,0,0,,珍妮
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.93,0:22:36.02,ENG,,0,0,0,,Hi, Chloe.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.08,0:22:36.24,CHT,,0,0,0,,克露伊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.10,0:22:37.43,ENG,,0,0,0,,Would you like some champagne, miss?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.52,0:22:38.51,CHT,,0,0,0,,要喝香檳？    馬丁尼
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.52,0:22:39.10,ENG,,0,0,0,,Martini. Up.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.62,0:22:40.78,CHT,,0,0,0,,不加冰，大杯
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.52,0:22:40.60,ENG,,0,0,0,,Big.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.56,0:22:42.65,ENG,,0,0,0,,Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.90,0:22:47.28,ENG,,0,0,0,,I missed you. I mean, we missed you yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.99,0:22:48.23,CHT,,0,0,0,,我想你，昨天沒見到你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.83,0:22:51.27,CHT,,0,0,0,,不可否認…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.95,0:22:50.61,ENG,,0,0,0,,I must say, I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.66,0:22:54.41,ENG,,0,0,0,,I'm disturbed that you didn't come to our wedding.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.90,0:22:54.50,CHT,,0,0,0,,你沒來我很難過
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.49,0:22:57.41,ENG,,0,0,0,,- Jason, you promised. - I know I promised,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.60,0:22:56.40,CHT,,0,0,0,,傑森，說好不提的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.51,0:23:01.03,CHT,,0,0,0,,我知道，但婚禮很圓滿
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.79,0:23:00.42,ENG,,0,0,0,,but it was a beautiful event and I missed her.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.50,0:23:04.17,ENG,,0,0,0,,You should've been there. The twins, they were running around like mad
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.14,0:23:03.27,CHT,,0,0,0,,你應該來，那對雙胞胎…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.38,0:23:07.44,CHT,,0,0,0,,跑來跑去，灑花瓣太棒了！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.25,0:23:07.17,ENG,,0,0,0,,and throwing flowers and... it was wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.26,0:23:09.05,ENG,,0,0,0,,Especially Emma. You know, the little one?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.55,0:23:10.88,CHT,,0,0,0,,尤其是艾瑪，她喜歡你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.13,0:23:10.51,ENG,,0,0,0,,She loves you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.59,0:23:11.76,ENG,,0,0,0,,- She adores you. - It was beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.99,0:23:12.62,CHT,,0,0,0,,婚禮很棒
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.84,0:23:14.47,ENG,,0,0,0,,- Yes. She missed you, too. - All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.72,0:23:14.42,CHT,,0,0,0,,艾瑪很想你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.14,0:23:18.14,ENG,,0,0,0,,This is from us, for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.39,0:23:18.99,CHT,,0,0,0,,我們送你的禮物
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.11,0:23:25.32,ENG,,0,0,0,,Are you not going to open it?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.33,0:23:25.23,CHT,,0,0,0,,不打開看看？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.33,0:23:45.17,ENG,,0,0,0,,I knew she wouldn't like...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.42,0:23:45.12,CHT,,0,0,0,,我就知道…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.25,0:23:48.21,ENG,,0,0,0,,You can exchange them if you don't like them.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.49,0:23:48.55,CHT,,0,0,0,,不喜歡可以換
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.30,0:23:52.59,ENG,,0,0,0,,Jenny, I know this is hard. I just want you to be happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.49,0:23:52.90,CHT,,0,0,0,,我知道你很難接受這事實但我希望你快樂
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.68,0:23:53.84,ENG,,0,0,0,,Happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.00,0:23:54.19,CHT,,0,0,0,,快樂？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.64,0:23:58.81,ENG,,0,0,0,,Well, I would like to propose a toast to happiness
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.97,0:24:00.77,CHT,,0,0,0,,我想舉杯祝賀祝快樂，與…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.18,0:24:00.48,ENG,,0,0,0,,and to...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.78,0:24:15.70,ENG,,0,0,0,,Well, are we going to have an evening or not?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.95,0:24:15.61,CHT,,0,0,0,,今晚要這樣聚餐？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.78,0:24:18.08,ENG,,0,0,0,,Jenny, I know that you hate me.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.02,0:24:18.01,CHT,,0,0,0,,我知道你討厭我
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.16,0:24:21.96,ENG,,0,0,0,,I know that you have terrible things that you wanna say to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.42,0:24:21.19,CHT,,0,0,0,,你想羞辱我
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.04,0:24:24.83,ENG,,0,0,0,,You have to get over it. Life goes on.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.19,0:24:23.59,CHT,,0,0,0,,你得看開點
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.70,0:24:26.17,CHT,,0,0,0,,好好活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.96,0:24:27.79,ENG,,0,0,0,,Life goes on, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.27,0:24:28.60,CHT,,0,0,0,,活下去，好
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.84,0:24:32.42,ENG,,0,0,0,,What's so funny?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.94,0:24:32.13,CHT,,0,0,0,,笑什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.51,0:24:33.72,ENG,,0,0,0,,Life...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.81,0:24:33.93,CHT,,0,0,0,,活下去…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.01,0:24:39.00,CHT,,0,0,0,,等著瞧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.05,0:24:38.43,ENG,,0,0,0,,We'll see.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.01,0:24:41.60,ENG,,0,0,0,,What's so funny about "life goes on"?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.28,0:24:40.71,CHT,,0,0,0,,活下去有什麼好笑？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.60,0:24:44.48,ENG,,0,0,0,,What? Life going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.02,0:24:46.92,CHT,,0,0,0,,我不覺得有什麼好笑
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.56,0:24:46.65,ENG,,0,0,0,,I don't think it's so funny that life goes on.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.73,0:24:50.07,ENG,,0,0,0,,Dad, you need to get back together with Mom,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.02,0:24:50.32,CHT,,0,0,0,,爸，你該跟媽破鏡重圓
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.32,0:24:55.66,ENG,,0,0,0,,because she's all alone in the world and she needs you right now, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.69,0:24:55.69,CHT,,0,0,0,,她孤獨無依，需要你
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.03,0:24:59.24,ENG,,0,0,0,,Jenny,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.20,0:25:01.10,CHT,,0,0,0,,珍妮，我剛結婚
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.70,0:25:02.16,ENG,,0,0,0,,- I just got married. - I know, I know, and I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.20,0:25:05.04,CHT,,0,0,0,,抱歉，克露伊，別介意
Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.25,0:25:04.66,ENG,,0,0,0,,Chloe, this has nothing to do with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.75,0:25:08.13,ENG,,0,0,0,,Well, it has to do something for me, for Christ's sake.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.24,0:25:10.01,CHT,,0,0,0,,我也會介意，真瘋狂
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.59,0:25:10.00,ENG,,0,0,0,,This is insane.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.09,0:25:12.71,ENG,,0,0,0,,I have to apologize for my daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.38,0:25:12.94,CHT,,0,0,0,,我為女兒道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.84,0:25:15.01,ENG,,0,0,0,,Listen, it's not your fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.05,0:25:14.61,CHT,,0,0,0,,不是你的錯
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.38,0:25:17.34,ENG,,0,0,0,,All right, I have to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.98,0:25:17.75,CHT,,0,0,0,,我得走了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.60,0:25:20.22,ENG,,0,0,0,,I know you think I'm a bad person. I'm really not.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.85,0:25:20.58,CHT,,0,0,0,,你一定認為我很壞，我不壞
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.31,0:25:21.89,ENG,,0,0,0,,And I don't hate you.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.69,0:25:22.16,CHT,,0,0,0,,我不恨你
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.97,0:25:24.43,ENG,,0,0,0,,I gotta...I just... I gotta go.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.29,0:25:24.95,CHT,,0,0,0,,我只是…得走了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:39.24,0:25:41.78,ENG,,0,0,0,,- Hi, Jane. How are you? - How are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.08,0:25:43.75,ENG,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I'm coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.96,0:25:50.38,ENG,,0,0,0,,She's done exactly what we want her to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:50.46,0:25:52.75,ENG,,0,0,0,,She signed the release, and so you have no problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:52.84,0:25:55.63,ENG,,0,0,0,,Because for her, it does... Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:55.09,0:25:56.08,CHT,,0,0,0,,失陪了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:55.88,0:25:58.22,ENG,,0,0,0,,- Jenny. - Hey! How are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:56.19,0:25:57.32,CHT,,0,0,0,,珍妮
Dialogue: 0,0:25:58.30,0:26:01.35,ENG,,0,0,0,,- What are you doing here? - Excuse me. Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:58.56,0:26:00.75,CHT,,0,0,0,,你怎麼來了？
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.43,0:26:03.06,ENG,,0,0,0,,Did Stuart send you here without telling me?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.63,0:26:03.39,CHT,,0,0,0,,史都華派你來？
Dialogue: 0,0:26:03.14,0:26:04.89,ENG,,0,0,0,,No, Beth. I was gonna talk to you...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:03.50,0:26:05.19,CHT,,0,0,0,,不是…
Dialogue: 0,0:26:04.98,0:26:07.73,ENG,,0,0,0,,You know what, if Stuart thinks he can push me out of the White House...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:05.30,0:26:07.82,CHT,,0,0,0,,若史都華想排擠我
Dialogue: 0,0:26:07.81,0:26:09.65,ENG,,0,0,0,,Ms. Lerner. Hi, Beth.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:07.94,0:26:10.10,CHT,,0,0,0,,藍納小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:26:09.90,0:26:12.82,ENG,,0,0,0,,Right this way. I've got you right down here.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:10.20,0:26:13.44,CHT,,0,0,0,,跟我來，替你留了座位
Dialogue: 0,0:26:19.32,0:26:20.99,ENG,,0,0,0,,Excuse me, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:22.66,0:26:23.74,ENG,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:22.95,0:26:27.32,CHT,,0,0,0,,你首先發問，自己看著辦
Dialogue: 0,0:26:24.08,0:26:28.00,ENG,,0,0,0,,He'll find you for the first question. Then you're on your own.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:28.71,0:26:30.71,ENG,,0,0,0,,Hey. How are you? Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:28.99,0:26:30.25,CHT,,0,0,0,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:26:32.25,0:26:33.75,ENG,,0,0,0,,Ladies and gentlemen.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:32.46,0:26:36.49,CHT,,0,0,0,,先生女士們…請安靜
Dialogue: 0,0:26:33.84,0:26:36.01,ENG,,0,0,0,,Ladies and gentleman, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:37.26,0:26:40.13,ENG,,0,0,0,,The President will begin by addressing the nation.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:37.43,0:26:40.42,CHT,,0,0,0,,總統將向全民演說
Dialogue: 0,0:26:40.22,0:26:43.26,ENG,,0,0,0,,Please hold your questions until he's finished his remarks.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:40.57,0:26:43.56,CHT,,0,0,0,,請等演說完再發問
Dialogue: 0,0:26:43.35,0:26:46.89,ENG,,0,0,0,,Ladies and gentlemen, the President of the United States.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:43.71,0:26:46.20,CHT,,0,0,0,,歡迎美國總統
Dialogue: 0,0:26:50.65,0:26:51.69,ENG,,0,0,0,,Hello, everybody.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:50.78,0:26:51.80,CHT,,0,0,0,,大家好
Dialogue: 0,0:26:51.77,0:26:52.86,ENG,,0,0,0,,- Mr. President. - Mr. President.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:52.94,0:26:55.02,ENG,,0,0,0,,Ten seconds, Mr. President.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:53.15,0:26:55.01,CHT,,0,0,0,,剩10秒鐘
Dialogue: 0,0:26:56.99,0:26:58.44,ENG,,0,0,0,,Five, four...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:57.32,0:26:59.52,CHT,,0,0,0,,5、4…
Dialogue: 0,0:27:01.53,0:27:03.03,ENG,,0,0,0,,Good evening.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:01.62,0:27:02.89,CHT,,0,0,0,,晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:27:04.16,0:27:07.25,ENG,,0,0,0,,A few minutes ago, the United States' ambassadors to every country
Dialogue: 0,0:27:04.39,0:27:07.89,CHT,,0,0,0,,幾分鐘前美國駐各國大使
Dialogue: 0,0:27:07.33,0:27:09.12,ENG,,0,0,0,,in the world told the leaders of those nations
Dialogue: 0,0:27:08.00,0:27:11.20,CHT,,0,0,0,,通知該國領袖這個消息
Dialogue: 0,0:27:09.21,0:27:11.37,ENG,,0,0,0,,what I am about to tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:11.71,0:27:14.25,ENG,,0,0,0,,It's a bit complicated, so it will take some time.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:11.87,0:27:14.63,CHT,,0,0,0,,這件事有些復雜
Dialogue: 0,0:27:14.34,0:27:17.88,ENG,,0,0,0,,So I hope you will bear with me, hear what I have to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:14.74,0:27:18.50,CHT,,0,0,0,,我慢慢解釋，請各位耐心聽
Dialogue: 0,0:27:19.47,0:27:21.51,ENG,,0,0,0,,A little over a year ago,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:19.58,0:27:21.81,CHT,,0,0,0,,一年多前
Dialogue: 0,0:27:21.89,0:27:25.81,ENG,,0,0,0,,two American astronomers, Marcus Wolf and Leo Biederman,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:21.98,0:27:23.91,CHT,,0,0,0,,兩名天文學家
Dialogue: 0,0:27:24.08,0:27:25.88,CHT,,0,0,0,,馬克斯沃夫、里歐畢德曼
Dialogue: 0,0:27:26.14,0:27:28.77,ENG,,0,0,0,,working on a mountaintop in Arizona...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:26.48,0:27:28.58,CHT,,0,0,0,,在亞歷桑那山上做研究
Dialogue: 0,0:27:29.15,0:27:30.95,CHT,,0,0,0,,大家安靜
Dialogue: 0,0:27:29.60,0:27:30.81,ENG,,0,0,0,,Nobody say anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:30.89,0:27:34.15,ENG,,0,0,0,,...saw something in the night sky that caused them great concern.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:31.05,0:27:33.55,CHT,,0,0,0,,觀察到太空中的…
Dialogue: 0,0:27:34.23,0:27:35.44,ENG,,0,0,0,,A comet.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:34.49,0:27:35.93,CHT,,0,0,0,,彗星
Dialogue: 0,0:27:36.78,0:27:39.74,ENG,,0,0,0,,But the comet was... Well,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:36.99,0:27:40.02,CHT,,0,0,0,,那顆彗星…
Dialogue: 0,0:27:40.32,0:27:43.91,ENG,,0,0,0,,there was a remote possibility that the comet was on a path
Dialogue: 0,0:27:40.47,0:27:44.30,CHT,,0,0,0,,有很大的可能
Dialogue: 0,0:27:43.99,0:27:47.49,ENG,,0,0,0,,that could bring it into direct contact with the Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:44.40,0:27:47.37,CHT,,0,0,0,,將會撞擊地球
Dialogue: 0,0:27:49.96,0:27:53.75,ENG,,0,0,0,,Now, we get hit all the time by rocks and meteors.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:50.11,0:27:54.07,CHT,,0,0,0,,地球常遭隕石撞擊
Dialogue: 0,0:27:54.00,0:27:57.34,ENG,,0,0,0,,Some of them the size of cars, some no bigger than your hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:54.28,0:27:57.51,CHT,,0,0,0,,有些大如汽車有些小如手掌
Dialogue: 0,0:27:57.42,0:28:00.72,ENG,,0,0,0,,But the comet we discovered is the size of New York City,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:57.62,0:28:00.59,CHT,,0,0,0,,這顆彗星卻如紐約市般大
Dialogue: 0,0:28:00.80,0:28:04.09,ENG,,0,0,0,,from the north side of Central Park to the Battery.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:00.99,0:28:03.96,CHT,,0,0,0,,自中央公園到貝特曼區
Dialogue: 0,0:28:04.60,0:28:06.39,ENG,,0,0,0,,About 7 miles long.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:04.79,0:28:07.02,CHT,,0,0,0,,近7英里長
Dialogue: 0,0:28:07.22,0:28:08.85,ENG,,0,0,0,,Put another way,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:07.36,0:28:12.02,CHT,,0,0,0,,換句話說…它比聖母峰還大
Dialogue: 0,0:28:09.22,0:28:11.98,ENG,,0,0,0,,this comet is larger than Mount Everest.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:12.14,0:28:15.86,ENG,,0,0,0,,It weighs 500 billion tons.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:12.53,0:28:16.19,CHT,,0,0,0,,重量：5百兆噸
Dialogue: 0,0:28:15.94,0:28:18.11,ENG,,0,0,0,,Now, chances are that this thing will miss us...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:17.84,0:28:20.00,CHT,,0,0,0,,天文學家、天體物理學家
Dialogue: 0,0:28:18.19,0:28:21.86,ENG,,0,0,0,,Astrophysicists, geologists and climatologists.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:20.11,0:28:22.17,CHT,,0,0,0,,地質學家、氣象學家
Dialogue: 0,0:28:21.95,0:28:23.74,ENG,,0,0,0,,Where the hell is Science?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:22.31,0:28:23.94,CHT,,0,0,0,,科學家跑哪去了？
Dialogue: 0,0:28:23.82,0:28:26.82,ENG,,0,0,0,,Paris, London, Tokyo, Tel Aviv. I want it everywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:24.18,0:28:26.44,CHT,,0,0,0,,巴黎、倫敦、東京，都要
Dialogue: 0,0:28:26.55,0:28:28.41,CHT,,0,0,0,,赫爾波普彗星資料
Dialogue: 0,0:28:26.91,0:28:28.33,ENG,,0,0,0,,That guy at Berkeley, did Hale-Bopp stand-ups?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:28.41,0:28:30.62,ENG,,0,0,0,,And graphics? I need graphics!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:28.52,0:28:30.64,CHT,,0,0,0,,座標圖，快給我！
Dialogue: 0,0:28:30.87,0:28:33.12,ENG,,0,0,0,,Comets begin far out in space.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:31.05,0:28:33.48,CHT,,0,0,0,,彗星存在於太空中
Dialogue: 0,0:28:33.37,0:28:36.38,ENG,,0,0,0,,They're what's left over from the creation of the solar system
Dialogue: 0,0:28:33.59,0:28:36.58,CHT,,0,0,0,,太陽系誕生遺留的廢物
Dialogue: 0,0:28:36.46,0:28:39.50,ENG,,0,0,0,,after the planets were formed billions of years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:36.72,0:28:39.75,CHT,,0,0,0,,百萬年前行星誕生
Dialogue: 0,0:28:39.59,0:28:41.38,ENG,,0,0,0,,Now, these chunks of space debris
Dialogue: 0,0:28:39.86,0:28:44.46,CHT,,0,0,0,,這些碎石運行在太陽系
Dialogue: 0,0:28:41.47,0:28:44.22,ENG,,0,0,0,,are in an elongated orbit around our sun.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:44.51,0:28:47.30,ENG,,0,0,0,,But every now and then, one of them gets bumped,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:44.63,0:28:45.89,CHT,,0,0,0,,偶爾…有些彗星
Dialogue: 0,0:28:46.13,0:28:50.19,CHT,,0,0,0,,像撞球台的彈珠
Dialogue: 0,0:28:47.39,0:28:52.27,ENG,,0,0,0,,sort of like a billiard ball on a pool table, and is knocked into a different orbit.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:50.64,0:28:53.07,CHT,,0,0,0,,彈到另一個軌道
Dialogue: 0,0:28:52.35,0:28:55.73,ENG,,0,0,0,,Now, if this comet continues on its path around the sun
Dialogue: 0,0:28:53.17,0:28:57.80,CHT,,0,0,0,,若這顆彗星的行逕不變
Dialogue: 0,0:28:55.81,0:28:57.77,ENG,,0,0,0,,and keeps its present course,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:57.86,0:29:00.90,ENG,,0,0,0,,sometime on August 16, roughly a year from now,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:58.05,0:28:59.74,CHT,,0,0,0,,在8月16日左右
Dialogue: 0,0:28:59.85,0:29:03.44,CHT,,0,0,0,,約一年後，將撞上地球
Dialogue: 0,0:29:00.98,0:29:03.82,ENG,,0,0,0,,there's a chance that we might have impact.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:05.24,0:29:08.41,ENG,,0,0,0,,So for the past eight months, the United States and Russia
Dialogue: 0,0:29:05.35,0:29:08.25,CHT,,0,0,0,,過去8個月，美俄合作
Dialogue: 0,0:29:08.49,0:29:12.16,ENG,,0,0,0,,have been building the largest spaceship ever constructed.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:08.66,0:29:12.79,CHT,,0,0,0,,建造前所未見的超級太空船
Dialogue: 0,0:29:12.66,0:29:15.12,ENG,,0,0,0,,It's being built in orbit around the Earth,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:12.86,0:29:15.30,CHT,,0,0,0,,在地球軌道上
Dialogue: 0,0:29:15.21,0:29:17.33,ENG,,0,0,0,,and we call it the Messiah.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:15.40,0:29:17.92,CHT,,0,0,0,,命名彌賽亞號
Dialogue: 0,0:29:18.04,0:29:20.75,ENG,,0,0,0,,And right now, a team of American astronauts and one Russian
Dialogue: 0,0:29:18.37,0:29:20.30,CHT,,0,0,0,,美俄太空人
Dialogue: 0,0:29:20.40,0:29:22.87,CHT,,0,0,0,,在坎納爾發射基地
Dialogue: 0,0:29:20.84,0:29:22.84,ENG,,0,0,0,,are at Cape Canaveral in Florida.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:22.92,0:29:24.42,ENG,,0,0,0,,In two months,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:23.10,0:29:26.23,CHT,,0,0,0,,將於兩個月後
Dialogue: 0,0:29:24.51,0:29:28.34,ENG,,0,0,0,,they will leave on the shuttle Atlantis to board the Messiah.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:26.34,0:29:28.21,CHT,,0,0,0,,登上彌賽亞號
Dialogue: 0,0:29:28.51,0:29:31.72,ENG,,0,0,0,,This is the crew that will stop the comet.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:28.61,0:29:32.55,CHT,,0,0,0,,這批組員將攔截彗星
Dialogue: 0,0:29:33.52,0:29:35.69,ENG,,0,0,0,,I'd like the world to meet some extraordinary people.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:33.62,0:29:36.02,CHT,,0,0,0,,讓我介紹這一群傑出人士
Dialogue: 0,0:29:35.77,0:29:38.27,ENG,,0,0,0,,First is Mission Commander Oren Monash.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:36.12,0:29:38.68,CHT,,0,0,0,,首先是任務指揮歐仁蒙納希
Dialogue: 0,0:29:38.36,0:29:41.11,ENG,,0,0,0,,Commander, would you introduce us to your team?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:38.79,0:29:41.22,CHT,,0,0,0,,指揮，請介紹組員
Dialogue: 0,0:29:41.19,0:29:43.19,ENG,,0,0,0,,I would be honored, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:41.39,0:29:42.95,CHT,,0,0,0,,我的榮幸
Dialogue: 0,0:29:43.74,0:29:45.53,ENG,,0,0,0,,Pilot, Andrea Baker.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:43.89,0:29:45.66,CHT,,0,0,0,,駕駛：安卓貝克
Dialogue: 0,0:29:45.99,0:29:48.32,ENG,,0,0,0,,Medical Officer Gus Partenza.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:46.33,0:29:48.63,CHT,,0,0,0,,醫護官：葛斯帕廷薩
Dialogue: 0,0:29:48.41,0:29:52.83,ENG,,0,0,0,,From Russia, Nuclear Specialist Colonel Mikhail Tulchinsky.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:48.73,0:29:53.69,CHT,,0,0,0,,來自俄國…核武專家：米凱齊斯基上校
Dialogue: 0,0:29:53.58,0:29:55.12,ENG,,0,0,0,,Navigator Mark Simon,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:53.80,0:29:55.33,CHT,,0,0,0,,領航員：馬克賽門
Dialogue: 0,0:29:55.21,0:29:57.83,ENG,,0,0,0,,and Rendezvous Pilot Spurgeon Tanner.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:55.44,0:29:58.14,CHT,,0,0,0,,近程導航：史波金譚納
Dialogue: 0,0:29:58.46,0:30:00.79,ENG,,0,0,0,,- Hello, Mr. President. - Hello, Mr. President.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:58.61,0:30:00.34,CHT,,0,0,0,,總統先生，好
Dialogue: 0,0:30:00.88,0:30:04.21,ENG,,0,0,0,,Captain Tanner, you flew six shuttle missions.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:01.01,0:30:02.38,CHT,,0,0,0,,譚納上尉
Dialogue: 0,0:30:02.81,0:30:04.75,CHT,,0,0,0,,你出過6次任務
Dialogue: 0,0:30:04.47,0:30:07.13,ENG,,0,0,0,,You were the last man to walk on the moon, weren't you, sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:04.85,0:30:07.32,CHT,,0,0,0,,是最後登陸月球的人
Dialogue: 0,0:30:07.22,0:30:08.38,ENG,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:07.42,0:30:10.78,CHT,,0,0,0,,是的，此次由歐仁駕駛
Dialogue: 0,0:30:08.47,0:30:10.64,ENG,,0,0,0,,but Oren here will be doing most of the flying on this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:10.72,0:30:13.89,ENG,,0,0,0,,I'll just be taking us down to the comet surface.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:10.89,0:30:14.32,CHT,,0,0,0,,我負責降落在彗星上
Dialogue: 0,0:30:14.22,0:30:16.68,ENG,,0,0,0,,Well, it's good to know we're going to have your kind of experience
Dialogue: 0,0:30:14.42,0:30:18.09,CHT,,0,0,0,,有你豐富的經驗令人安心謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:30:16.77,0:30:18.48,ENG,,0,0,0,,- up there, Captain. - Thank you, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:18.56,0:30:21.40,ENG,,0,0,0,,Godspeed to you all. We're counting on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:18.70,0:30:21.43,CHT,,0,0,0,,一路平安，靠你們了
Dialogue: 0,0:30:21.94,0:30:23.07,ENG,,0,0,0,,Thank you, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:22.13,0:30:23.33,CHT,,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:30:23.15,0:30:25.99,ENG,,0,0,0,,Got Beijing, Rome, Sao Paulo, Cairo, Berlin.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:23.84,0:30:26.17,CHT,,0,0,0,,北京、羅馬、柏林…
Dialogue: 0,0:30:26.07,0:30:28.65,ENG,,0,0,0,,Does anyone know how big the one was that killed all the dinosaurs?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:26.27,0:30:28.71,CHT,,0,0,0,,殺恐龍的彗星有多大？
Dialogue: 0,0:30:28.74,0:30:31.03,ENG,,0,0,0,,Something majestic, mysterious, with a fanfare for the intro
Dialogue: 0,0:30:28.81,0:30:33.18,CHT,,0,0,0,,壯觀、神秘、華麗的前奏
Dialogue: 0,0:30:31.12,0:30:33.16,ENG,,0,0,0,,and a theme to the longer promos.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:33.24,0:30:35.41,ENG,,0,0,0,,- It's hitting the goddamn Earth? - That's what he's saying.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:33.28,0:30:34.64,CHT,,0,0,0,,彗星撞地球？
Dialogue: 0,0:30:34.75,0:30:35.94,CHT,,0,0,0,,他是這麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:30:35.50,0:30:39.29,ENG,,0,0,0,,- Bring that up again. - He'll scare the shit out of everybody.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:36.05,0:30:38.14,CHT,,0,0,0,,嚇死老百姓
Dialogue: 0,0:30:39.92,0:30:42.42,ENG,,0,0,0,,Our society will continue as normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:40.12,0:30:43.05,CHT,,0,0,0,,社會將照常運作
Dialogue: 0,0:30:43.00,0:30:44.63,ENG,,0,0,0,,Work will go on.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:43.15,0:30:45.15,CHT,,0,0,0,,照常工作
Dialogue: 0,0:30:45.05,0:30:47.05,ENG,,0,0,0,,You will pay your bills.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:45.26,0:30:46.95,CHT,,0,0,0,,帳單要付
Dialogue: 0,0:30:49.93,0:30:51.97,ENG,,0,0,0,,There will be no hoarding.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:50.10,0:30:52.03,CHT,,0,0,0,,不得貯貨
Dialogue: 0,0:30:52.51,0:30:57.73,ENG,,0,0,0,,There will be no sudden profiteering. I'm freezing all wages, all prices.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:52.63,0:30:54.90,CHT,,0,0,0,,不得賺取暴利
Dialogue: 0,0:30:55.10,0:30:58.37,CHT,,0,0,0,,不得調動工資或物價
Dialogue: 0,0:30:58.77,0:31:01.56,ENG,,0,0,0,,What a bottle of water cost you yesterday,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:58.90,0:31:01.81,CHT,,0,0,0,,昨天水賣多少錢…
Dialogue: 0,0:31:02.44,0:31:04.44,ENG,,0,0,0,,it will cost you tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:02.58,0:31:05.04,CHT,,0,0,0,,明天仍維持原價
Dialogue: 0,0:31:05.28,0:31:07.49,ENG,,0,0,0,,Now I'll take a few questions.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:05.44,0:31:06.50,CHT,,0,0,0,,現在請發問
Dialogue: 0,0:31:08.57,0:31:09.95,ENG,,0,0,0,,Ms. Lerner?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:08.68,0:31:09.38,CHT,,0,0,0,,藍納小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:31:11.82,0:31:14.18,CHT,,0,0,0,,珍妮藍納，國家廣播電視台
Dialogue: 0,0:31:11.99,0:31:13.95,ENG,,0,0,0,,Jenny Lerner, MSNBC.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:14.03,0:31:16.83,ENG,,0,0,0,,- Jenny Lerner? - Son of a bitch.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:14.29,0:31:15.69,CHT,,0,0,0,,珍妮藍納？
Dialogue: 0,0:31:15.79,0:31:17.22,CHT,,0,0,0,,狗屎運！
Dialogue: 0,0:31:18.62,0:31:20.04,ENG,,0,0,0,,Mr. President,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:18.79,0:31:22.49,CHT,,0,0,0,,總統，為何不早公佈消息？
Dialogue: 0,0:31:20.12,0:31:22.83,ENG,,0,0,0,,why wasn't this announcement made sooner?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:22.92,0:31:25.29,ENG,,0,0,0,,Well, until we knew we could build the rocket
Dialogue: 0,0:31:23.03,0:31:25.62,CHT,,0,0,0,,在建造太空船…
Dialogue: 0,0:31:25.38,0:31:27.59,ENG,,0,0,0,,and the comet could be intercepted,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:25.77,0:31:29.86,CHT,,0,0,0,,攔截彗星之前沒必要引起恐慌
Dialogue: 0,0:31:27.67,0:31:30.30,ENG,,0,0,0,,we saw no reason to alarm the planet.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:32.84,0:31:35.01,ENG,,0,0,0,,Do you have another question, Ms. Lerner?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:33.21,0:31:34.70,CHT,,0,0,0,,你還有別的問題？
Dialogue: 0,0:31:35.10,0:31:36.18,ENG,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:35.28,0:31:36.50,CHT,,0,0,0,,有
Dialogue: 0,0:31:37.08,0:31:43.45,CHT,,0,0,0,,彗星與撤軍事件有關嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:31:37.77,0:31:40.10,ENG,,0,0,0,,Is there a connection between the comet
Dialogue: 0,0:31:40.19,0:31:43.23,ENG,,0,0,0,,and the recall of American troops from abroad?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:43.31,0:31:45.19,ENG,,0,0,0,,Our fighting men and women are coming home
Dialogue: 0,0:31:43.55,0:31:46.88,CHT,,0,0,0,,軍隊回國
Dialogue: 0,0:31:45.27,0:31:48.61,ENG,,0,0,0,,because we felt it prudent, in light of domestic security concerns,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:46.99,0:31:49.89,CHT,,0,0,0,,能擔負保國衛民重任
Dialogue: 0,0:31:48.69,0:31:49.74,ENG,,0,0,0,,to have them available.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:49.82,0:31:52.03,ENG,,0,0,0,,Although I certainly hope we don't need to use them.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:50.06,0:31:52.12,CHT,,0,0,0,,希望派不上用場
Dialogue: 0,0:31:52.11,0:31:53.20,ENG,,0,0,0,,Next question.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:52.23,0:31:53.35,CHT,,0,0,0,,下個問題
Dialogue: 0,0:31:54.20,0:31:58.54,ENG,,0,0,0,,Actually, Mr. President, if... Just one final question, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:54.33,0:31:56.19,CHT,,0,0,0,,總統先生
Dialogue: 0,0:31:56.30,0:31:59.10,CHT,,0,0,0,,最後一個問題
Dialogue: 0,0:31:59.83,0:32:03.96,ENG,,0,0,0,,MSNBC has learned that Secretary Rittenhouse
Dialogue: 0,0:32:00.07,0:32:02.26,CHT,,0,0,0,,國家廣播台據悉…
Dialogue: 0,0:32:02.40,0:32:04.60,CHT,,0,0,0,,財政部長離職
Dialogue: 0,0:32:04.04,0:32:07.80,ENG,,0,0,0,,did not leave for the reasons announced by your administration.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:04.71,0:32:07.97,CHT,,0,0,0,,非如官方報導
Dialogue: 0,0:32:07.88,0:32:10.30,ENG,,0,0,0,,In fact, isn't it true, sir,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:08.11,0:32:11.91,CHT,,0,0,0,,是否幕僚人員不信任…
Dialogue: 0,0:32:10.80,0:32:13.97,ENG,,0,0,0,,that not everyone in your administration is convinced
Dialogue: 0,0:32:12.01,0:32:16.25,CHT,,0,0,0,,彌賽亞號能完成使命
Dialogue: 0,0:32:14.05,0:32:16.30,ENG,,0,0,0,,that the Messiah will save us?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:24.90,0:32:28.65,ENG,,0,0,0,,Secretary Rittenhouse served his country with full devotion.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:25.13,0:32:27.89,CHT,,0,0,0,,瑞頓豪部長盡忠職守
Dialogue: 0,0:32:29.15,0:32:31.53,ENG,,0,0,0,,He resigned for personal reasons.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:29.27,0:32:31.67,CHT,,0,0,0,,他因私人理由辭職
Dialogue: 0,0:32:31.74,0:32:35.03,ENG,,0,0,0,,Now, I can promise you this, Ms. Lerner, all of you,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:31.87,0:32:34.39,CHT,,0,0,0,,我向你保證
Dialogue: 0,0:32:34.50,0:32:38.13,CHT,,0,0,0,,向各位與聆聽的民眾保證
Dialogue: 0,0:32:35.41,0:32:37.95,ENG,,0,0,0,,everyone in this room and everyone listening to my voice,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:38.04,0:32:40.91,ENG,,0,0,0,,that at some point over the next 10 months,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:38.24,0:32:41.30,CHT,,0,0,0,,接下來的10個月
Dialogue: 0,0:32:41.37,0:32:45.25,ENG,,0,0,0,,all of us will entertain our worst fears and concerns.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:41.64,0:32:46.08,CHT,,0,0,0,,我們都將面臨最大的恐慌
Dialogue: 0,0:32:46.54,0:32:48.88,ENG,,0,0,0,,But I can also promise you this.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:46.75,0:32:49.31,CHT,,0,0,0,,我能保證的是…
Dialogue: 0,0:32:49.88,0:32:51.46,ENG,,0,0,0,,Life will go on.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:50.05,0:32:52.05,CHT,,0,0,0,,生命將延續
Dialogue: 0,0:32:53.26,0:32:54.88,ENG,,0,0,0,,We will prevail.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:53.46,0:32:55.43,CHT,,0,0,0,,人類能存活
Dialogue: 0,0:32:55.43,0:32:56.97,ENG,,0,0,0,,Mr. President! Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:57.05,0:32:58.68,ENG,,0,0,0,,- Sally. - Sir! Sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:58.30,0:33:00.29,CHT,,0,0,0,,彗星叫什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:32:58.76,0:33:00.14,ENG,,0,0,0,,What is the comet's name?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:00.22,0:33:03.14,ENG,,0,0,0,,The two scientists who found the comet were killed in a car crash
Dialogue: 0,0:33:00.53,0:33:03.40,CHT,,0,0,0,,發現彗星的人死於車禍
Dialogue: 0,0:33:03.23,0:33:06.40,ENG,,0,0,0,,while racing from their observatory to alert the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:03.50,0:33:06.53,CHT,,0,0,0,,因他們當時急於預警
Dialogue: 0,0:33:06.48,0:33:09.57,ENG,,0,0,0,,So we named it for them, Wolf-Biederman.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:06.70,0:33:10.11,CHT,,0,0,0,,以他們命名，沃夫畢德曼
Dialogue: 0,0:33:10.57,0:33:13.03,ENG,,0,0,0,,Leo Biederman. They said it again.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:10.84,0:33:13.28,CHT,,0,0,0,,里歐畢德曼，總統又說了！
Dialogue: 0,0:33:13.11,0:33:14.15,ENG,,0,0,0,,Leo, is he talking about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:13.38,0:33:15.40,CHT,,0,0,0,,里歐，他在說你，對吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:33:14.24,0:33:15.82,ENG,,0,0,0,,- He is, isn't he? - I'm trying to listen.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:15.58,0:33:19.24,CHT,,0,0,0,,俄國為何會加入？
Dialogue: 0,0:33:15.91,0:33:17.95,ENG,,0,0,0,,Why were the Russians brought into the construction phase...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:18.03,0:33:21.33,ENG,,0,0,0,,- Honey, can you get that, please? - Janie, get the door.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:19.35,0:33:20.75,CHT,,0,0,0,,潔妮，開門
Dialogue: 0,0:33:21.41,0:33:24.46,ENG,,0,0,0,,Well, we have the technology to build the ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:21.59,0:33:23.85,CHT,,0,0,0,,我們有能力造太空船
Dialogue: 0,0:33:24.75,0:33:27.25,ENG,,0,0,0,,They have the technology to make it go.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:24.99,0:33:27.32,CHT,,0,0,0,,俄國提供核子動力
Dialogue: 0,0:33:27.33,0:33:30.09,ENG,,0,0,0,,There's someone at the door for you, Leo.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:27.43,0:33:29.69,CHT,,0,0,0,,里歐，有人找你
Dialogue: 0,0:33:32.84,0:33:35.84,ENG,,0,0,0,,You've been watching live coverage of President Tom Beck.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:35.93,0:33:40.18,ENG,,0,0,0,,- I can't believe this. This is so weird. - Dr. Wolf from Astronomy Club?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:36.20,0:33:38.67,CHT,,0,0,0,,不敢相信，真怪異
Dialogue: 0,0:33:38.77,0:33:40.36,CHT,,0,0,0,,天文俱樂部的沃夫博士？
Dialogue: 0,0:33:40.26,0:33:42.89,ENG,,0,0,0,,- Yeah, I guess so. - I think it's really neat.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:40.47,0:33:42.07,CHT,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:33:42.17,0:33:46.11,CHT,,0,0,0,,好帥！首先發現世界將毀滅的人
Dialogue: 0,0:33:42.97,0:33:45.69,ENG,,0,0,0,,Nobody on our block discovered the world was gonna end before.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:45.77,0:33:48.85,ENG,,0,0,0,,He's still very much alive. He's still alive, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:48.01,0:33:51.51,CHT,,0,0,0,,他還活著，活得好好的
Dialogue: 0,0:33:48.94,0:33:51.77,ENG,,0,0,0,,He's right here, and he's still alive. Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:52.61,0:33:54.15,ENG,,0,0,0,,Hey, Leo, cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:52.85,0:33:54.58,CHT,,0,0,0,,里歐，好酷！
Dialogue: 0,0:33:54.28,0:33:57.82,ENG,,0,0,0,,As far as we know, what happened was that Dr. Wolf saw the comet
Dialogue: 0,0:33:54.69,0:33:56.78,CHT,,0,0,0,,事情經過是…
Dialogue: 0,0:33:56.96,0:33:59.08,CHT,,0,0,0,,沃夫博士看到我寄的相片
Dialogue: 0,0:33:57.91,0:34:01.28,ENG,,0,0,0,,in my photograph, so he shared the discovery with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:59.23,0:34:01.89,CHT,,0,0,0,,將榮耀分享給我
Dialogue: 0,0:34:01.70,0:34:03.54,ENG,,0,0,0,,And then he was killed in that crash
Dialogue: 0,0:34:02.00,0:34:04.66,CHT,,0,0,0,,他那夜車禍身亡
Dialogue: 0,0:34:03.62,0:34:06.12,ENG,,0,0,0,,and everything got mixed up in Washington,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:04.83,0:34:06.32,CHT,,0,0,0,,混亂中
Dialogue: 0,0:34:06.21,0:34:08.21,ENG,,0,0,0,,so the President thought I was dead, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:06.43,0:34:08.73,CHT,,0,0,0,,總統以為我也死了
Dialogue: 0,0:34:08.29,0:34:10.96,ENG,,0,0,0,,- Leo! - Jasmine.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:12.46,0:34:15.17,ENG,,0,0,0,,How does it feel having your name on it?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:12.61,0:34:14.94,CHT,,0,0,0,,以你的名字命名感覺如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:34:16.13,0:34:18.55,ENG,,0,0,0,,I don't want anyone to think that I'm trying to take something away
Dialogue: 0,0:34:16.38,0:34:19.94,CHT,,0,0,0,,我不想搶沃夫博士的功勞
Dialogue: 0,0:34:18.64,0:34:21.30,ENG,,0,0,0,,from Dr. Wolf, because I'm not.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:20.48,0:34:23.61,CHT,,0,0,0,,我不想，但感覺很酷
Dialogue: 0,0:34:21.85,0:34:23.72,ENG,,0,0,0,,But it's kind of cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:25.14,0:34:26.31,ENG,,0,0,0,,Jason.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:25.45,0:34:26.44,CHT,,0,0,0,,傑森
Dialogue: 0,0:34:28.10,0:34:29.35,ENG,,0,0,0,,You know,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:28.39,0:34:33.38,CHT,,0,0,0,,你的性經驗將會比別人多
Dialogue: 0,0:34:29.52,0:34:33.65,ENG,,0,0,0,,you're gonna have sex a lot more now than anyone else in our class.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:34.65,0:34:36.44,ENG,,0,0,0,,Don't listen. Don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:41.16,0:34:42.41,ENG,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:41.40,0:34:42.43,CHT,,0,0,0,,真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:34:43.24,0:34:47.29,ENG,,0,0,0,,Thank you for your sexual insight, Mr. Thurman. You can sit down now.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:43.37,0:34:47.54,CHT,,0,0,0,,多謝你的性剖析，請坐
Dialogue: 0,0:34:47.37,0:34:49.87,ENG,,0,0,0,,Famous people always get sex, Mr. Perry.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:47.64,0:34:50.17,CHT,,0,0,0,,名人性經驗豐富
Dialogue: 0,0:34:49.96,0:34:52.96,ENG,,0,0,0,,That's the main reason it's good to be famous.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:50.31,0:34:52.71,CHT,,0,0,0,,所以大家想成名
Dialogue: 0,0:35:01.05,0:35:03.68,ENG,,0,0,0,,Fruit, reactor. Bottle, rocket. Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:01.31,0:35:04.04,CHT,,0,0,0,,水果當反應爐，瓶子當火箭
Dialogue: 0,0:35:04.01,0:35:06.10,ENG,,0,0,0,,- A nuclear reactor in space? - Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:04.14,0:35:07.37,CHT,,0,0,0,,太空中核子反應爐？很危險吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:35:06.18,0:35:07.52,ENG,,0,0,0,,- Isn't that dangerous? - No, no, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:07.48,0:35:10.24,CHT,,0,0,0,,不，是俄國設計的
Dialogue: 0,0:35:07.60,0:35:09.98,ENG,,0,0,0,,This is all Russian design, Russian science.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:10.06,0:35:12.44,ENG,,0,0,0,,The same people who designed Chernobyl.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:10.35,0:35:14.18,CHT,,0,0,0,,設計車諾比核電廠的人車諾比？
Dialogue: 0,0:35:12.52,0:35:15.40,ENG,,0,0,0,,- Chernobyl? - Chernobyl almost worked.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:14.29,0:35:16.31,CHT,,0,0,0,,車諾比幾乎成功啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:35:16.90,0:35:19.36,ENG,,0,0,0,,So what happens after you plant the bomb?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:17.19,0:35:19.75,CHT,,0,0,0,,安置炸彈後呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:35:19.45,0:35:20.61,ENG,,0,0,0,,Well, we have seven hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:19.86,0:35:22.55,CHT,,0,0,0,,有7小時安置炸彈
Dialogue: 0,0:35:20.70,0:35:23.12,ENG,,0,0,0,,We're gonna put bombs inside the comet. Let me follow these two.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:22.66,0:35:24.56,CHT,,0,0,0,,我最好跟著他們
Dialogue: 0,0:35:23.20,0:35:25.91,ENG,,0,0,0,,- I don't trust that combination. - Okay. Right, after seven hours,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:24.66,0:35:26.06,CHT,,0,0,0,,7小時
Dialogue: 0,0:35:25.99,0:35:29.46,ENG,,0,0,0,,the 14-hour rotational cycle of the comet, right, spins.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:26.17,0:35:29.29,CHT,,0,0,0,,彗星自轉14小時
Dialogue: 0,0:35:29.54,0:35:32.46,ENG,,0,0,0,,We're gonna get married. God knows I want to marry you.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:29.60,0:35:33.77,CHT,,0,0,0,,我們會結婚，我很想娶你別在我回來那一天…
Dialogue: 0,0:35:32.54,0:35:35.54,ENG,,0,0,0,,But the day I get back, the last thing I'm gonna do is step inside of a church.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:34.17,0:35:37.23,CHT,,0,0,0,,改個時間
Dialogue: 0,0:35:35.63,0:35:36.84,ENG,,0,0,0,,I don't do churches well.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:36.92,0:35:38.63,ENG,,0,0,0,,'Cause there's only seven hours of darkness.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:37.34,0:35:40.97,CHT,,0,0,0,,經過7小時黑暗面對陽光
Dialogue: 0,0:35:38.72,0:35:40.97,ENG,,0,0,0,,Then the sun starts hitting the surface of the planet and it causes...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:41.05,0:35:42.43,ENG,,0,0,0,,These are your orders.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:41.18,0:35:45.98,CHT,,0,0,0,,任務指派，一進入大氣層
Dialogue: 0,0:35:42.51,0:35:45.60,ENG,,0,0,0,,Upon first entering Earth's atmosphere,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:45.81,0:35:49.85,ENG,,0,0,0,,proceed immediately up the exterior of the mother ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:46.15,0:35:50.15,CHT,,0,0,0,,到母艦外面找奶吃
Dialogue: 0,0:35:50.26,0:35:52.16,CHT,,0,0,0,,陽光直射
Dialogue: 0,0:35:50.48,0:35:51.85,ENG,,0,0,0,,When the sun hits the surface,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:51.94,0:35:54.73,ENG,,0,0,0,,there's gonna be explosive out-gassings that are very dangerous...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:52.26,0:35:55.06,CHT,,0,0,0,,彗星地表噴爆氣體
Dialogue: 0,0:35:54.82,0:35:56.90,ENG,,0,0,0,,- Gus, he's seven. - Brittany.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:55.16,0:35:56.92,CHT,,0,0,0,,葛斯，他才7歲
Dialogue: 0,0:35:57.28,0:36:00.90,ENG,,0,0,0,,You boys were, what, four and six when I went to the moon?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:57.50,0:36:01.56,CHT,,0,0,0,,我上月球時…你們才4歲和6歲
Dialogue: 0,0:36:02.78,0:36:06.16,ENG,,0,0,0,,Now, you saw me go into space seven times, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:02.94,0:36:05.53,CHT,,0,0,0,,你們見我上太空7次
Dialogue: 0,0:36:06.11,0:36:08.27,CHT,,0,0,0,,每次都回來
Dialogue: 0,0:36:06.24,0:36:08.66,ENG,,0,0,0,,I came back every time, didn't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:08.83,0:36:09.91,ENG,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:11.54,0:36:13.62,ENG,,0,0,0,,Your mother and I used to play a game when she was still alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:11.75,0:36:14.04,CHT,,0,0,0,,你媽在世時，我們曾玩游戲
Dialogue: 0,0:36:13.71,0:36:15.38,ENG,,0,0,0,,Now, the game was,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:14.15,0:36:18.28,CHT,,0,0,0,,這個游戲是…假設我可能回不來
Dialogue: 0,0:36:15.59,0:36:18.46,ENG,,0,0,0,,if there was a chance I might not be coming back,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:18.55,0:36:21.34,ENG,,0,0,0,,she wouldn't say it and I wouldn't say it.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:18.75,0:36:20.98,CHT,,0,0,0,,她不說，我也不說
Dialogue: 0,0:36:21.42,0:36:22.47,ENG,,0,0,0,,Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:21.62,0:36:23.99,CHT,,0,0,0,,好嗎？    好的
Dialogue: 0,0:36:22.55,0:36:23.84,ENG,,0,0,0,,- Yes, sir. - Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:23.93,0:36:25.18,ENG,,0,0,0,,- Hey, Fish. - Hey, Mitch.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:24.09,0:36:26.58,CHT,,0,0,0,,小魚，啤酒？
Dialogue: 0,0:36:25.26,0:36:28.35,ENG,,0,0,0,,- How about a beer? - You remember my boys, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:26.70,0:36:28.49,CHT,,0,0,0,,記得我兒子吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:36:28.43,0:36:30.35,ENG,,0,0,0,,- This is Steve and Dwight. - Of course I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:28.66,0:36:29.65,CHT,,0,0,0,,史提夫和戴特
Dialogue: 0,0:36:29.76,0:36:32.73,CHT,,0,0,0,,記得，歡迎來到休士頓
Dialogue: 0,0:36:30.43,0:36:32.89,ENG,,0,0,0,,- Gentlemen, welcome to Houston. - Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:32.98,0:36:35.73,ENG,,0,0,0,,Let me steal your old man for a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:33.17,0:36:34.66,CHT,,0,0,0,,借你爸爸說句話
Dialogue: 0,0:36:35.86,0:36:38.57,ENG,,0,0,0,,- Can I take your picture, please? - Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:36.10,0:36:38.07,CHT,,0,0,0,,能拍張照嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:36:39.36,0:36:40.73,ENG,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:39.54,0:36:40.51,CHT,,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:36:42.86,0:36:45.32,ENG,,0,0,0,,So, what do you think of the crew?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:42.98,0:36:45.54,CHT,,0,0,0,,你認為組員如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:36:45.95,0:36:49.91,ENG,,0,0,0,,Heroes all. That's the finest group I ever had the privilege of working with.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:46.05,0:36:47.04,CHT,,0,0,0,,都是英雄
Dialogue: 0,0:36:47.88,0:36:50.51,CHT,,0,0,0,,我合作過最好的組員
Dialogue: 0,0:36:50.00,0:36:52.29,ENG,,0,0,0,,Yeah, yeah. Off the record?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:51.69,0:36:53.48,CHT,,0,0,0,,說實話
Dialogue: 0,0:36:53.37,0:36:56.38,ENG,,0,0,0,,Well, they've been trained in ways I'll never understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:53.62,0:36:56.62,CHT,,0,0,0,,他們受訓的方式很奇特
Dialogue: 0,0:36:56.46,0:36:59.38,ENG,,0,0,0,,They're smarter and in better shape than we ever were in the old days.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:56.73,0:36:59.63,CHT,,0,0,0,,他們變得聰明又健壯
Dialogue: 0,0:36:59.46,0:37:03.34,ENG,,0,0,0,,Sober, serious. I guess I'd be a little happier about this whole thing
Dialogue: 0,0:36:59.76,0:37:03.56,CHT,,0,0,0,,冷靜、嚴肅…我倒希望知道
Dialogue: 0,0:37:03.43,0:37:06.80,ENG,,0,0,0,,if I thought that any of them were as scared as I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:03.70,0:37:06.33,CHT,,0,0,0,,他們也會害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:37:07.30,0:37:09.05,ENG,,0,0,0,,Well, they're not scared of dying.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:07.44,0:37:09.34,CHT,,0,0,0,,他們不怕死
Dialogue: 0,0:37:09.14,0:37:11.93,ENG,,0,0,0,,They're just scared of looking bad on TV.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:09.44,0:37:12.07,CHT,,0,0,0,,只怕不上鏡頭
Dialogue: 0,0:37:13.73,0:37:15.73,ENG,,0,0,0,,Now, look, I wish I'd been to the moon.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:13.94,0:37:18.24,CHT,,0,0,0,,希望我上過月球，我仰慕他們
Dialogue: 0,0:37:15.81,0:37:17.94,ENG,,0,0,0,,I got respect for everybody who's gone to the moon,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:18.02,0:37:19.65,ENG,,0,0,0,,but this mission ain't going to the moon.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:18.35,0:37:19.71,CHT,,0,0,0,,但這趟不去月球
Dialogue: 0,0:37:19.73,0:37:23.24,ENG,,0,0,0,,That's right. Frank Gifford, he was a great football player in his time,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:19.85,0:37:23.38,CHT,,0,0,0,,對，基福是偉大的足球明星
Dialogue: 0,0:37:23.32,0:37:25.11,ENG,,0,0,0,,but if he played now, he'd get his ass busted.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:23.49,0:37:25.79,CHT,,0,0,0,,但老了有屁用
Dialogue: 0,0:37:25.20,0:37:26.66,ENG,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:34.79,0:37:40.63,ENG,,0,0,0,,All I'm saying is, the moon did not have a rotational cycle of 14 hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:34.93,0:37:39.16,CHT,,0,0,0,,我是說，月球不會14個小時
Dialogue: 0,0:37:39.30,0:37:41.07,CHT,,0,0,0,,自轉一週
Dialogue: 0,0:37:40.71,0:37:44.05,ENG,,0,0,0,,I mean, this is... We only have seven hours of dark when the sun's not up
Dialogue: 0,0:37:41.17,0:37:43.30,CHT,,0,0,0,,趁7小時黑夜安置炸彈
Dialogue: 0,0:37:43.51,0:37:46.44,CHT,,0,0,0,,白晝降落沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:37:44.13,0:37:46.97,ENG,,0,0,0,,to land on this thing. it was light when he landed. This is gonna be dark.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:46.58,0:37:48.24,CHT,,0,0,0,,黑夜看不到
Dialogue: 0,0:37:47.05,0:37:50.22,ENG,,0,0,0,,- We're not gonna be able to see. - You can't see now, Gus.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:48.35,0:37:51.51,CHT,,0,0,0,,你看不到    別擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:37:50.31,0:37:52.43,ENG,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:51.58,0:37:52.61,CHT,,0,0,0,,我們會成功
Dialogue: 0,0:37:52.52,0:37:54.39,ENG,,0,0,0,,- We what? - We can do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:52.68,0:37:53.48,CHT,,0,0,0,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:37:53.58,0:37:55.14,CHT,,0,0,0,,任務能達成
Dialogue: 0,0:37:56.98,0:37:58.65,ENG,,0,0,0,,No, no, stay down.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:57.26,0:37:58.69,CHT,,0,0,0,,不！坐下
Dialogue: 0,0:38:00.32,0:38:05.32,ENG,,0,0,0,,I woke up this morning and I realized none of you want me here.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:00.43,0:38:04.33,CHT,,0,0,0,,我今早起床，想通了
Dialogue: 0,0:38:04.60,0:38:06.29,CHT,,0,0,0,,你們不希望我去
Dialogue: 0,0:38:06.86,0:38:09.28,ENG,,0,0,0,,You don't even really know who I am, which is okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:07.13,0:38:09.57,CHT,,0,0,0,,你們不認識我，無所謂
Dialogue: 0,0:38:09.37,0:38:11.78,ENG,,0,0,0,,I walked on the moon, but I didn't belong to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:09.70,0:38:12.97,CHT,,0,0,0,,我上過月球年紀長你們許多
Dialogue: 0,0:38:11.87,0:38:15.37,ENG,,0,0,0,,I belonged to your daddies. Now, if I ask you to ask your daddies
Dialogue: 0,0:38:13.54,0:38:15.73,CHT,,0,0,0,,若要你們父執輩
Dialogue: 0,0:38:15.46,0:38:18.67,ENG,,0,0,0,,what I meant to them, to explain to you what I'm doing here,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:15.84,0:38:18.50,CHT,,0,0,0,,解釋我的事跡
Dialogue: 0,0:38:18.75,0:38:21.59,ENG,,0,0,0,,that's only gonna make things worse. So...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:18.84,0:38:21.44,CHT,,0,0,0,,只會更糟糕，所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:38:22.55,0:38:24.09,ENG,,0,0,0,,What do we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:22.85,0:38:24.04,CHT,,0,0,0,,怎麼辦？
Dialogue: 0,0:38:31.89,0:38:34.56,ENG,,0,0,0,,You haven't trained for this mission.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:32.19,0:38:34.09,CHT,,0,0,0,,你沒接受訓練
Dialogue: 0,0:38:34.64,0:38:36.18,ENG,,0,0,0,,We respect you.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:34.99,0:38:36.33,CHT,,0,0,0,,我們尊敬你
Dialogue: 0,0:38:36.43,0:38:37.83,CHT,,0,0,0,,很感激
Dialogue: 0,0:38:36.48,0:38:39.10,ENG,,0,0,0,,- I appreciate that. - But you're here...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:37.93,0:38:40.42,CHT,,0,0,0,,但你加入的原因…
Dialogue: 0,0:38:39.56,0:38:41.36,ENG,,0,0,0,,You're here because the powers that be
Dialogue: 0,0:38:40.53,0:38:44.53,CHT,,0,0,0,,是當局需要一張熟悉臉孔
Dialogue: 0,0:38:41.44,0:38:44.19,ENG,,0,0,0,,think we need a familiar face on this trip.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:44.28,0:38:46.78,ENG,,0,0,0,,- You're here for public relations. - No, no. I'm here
Dialogue: 0,0:38:44.64,0:38:46.50,CHT,,0,0,0,,是做公關的
Dialogue: 0,0:38:46.61,0:38:52.05,CHT,,0,0,0,,不，我是曾經登陸月球的人
Dialogue: 0,0:38:46.86,0:38:50.24,ENG,,0,0,0,,because the powers that be know that I'm the only person on this mission
Dialogue: 0,0:38:50.32,0:38:51.99,ENG,,0,0,0,,who's ever landed on the moon.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:52.08,0:38:54.08,ENG,,0,0,0,,And I have 500 landings on aircraft carriers.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:52.28,0:38:54.41,CHT,,0,0,0,,500次艦上起降紀錄
Dialogue: 0,0:38:54.16,0:38:57.75,ENG,,0,0,0,,- We've trained on... - On a flight simulator. Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:54.52,0:38:55.41,CHT,,0,0,0,,我們曾接受…
Dialogue: 0,0:38:55.52,0:38:58.21,CHT,,0,0,0,,模擬訓練，對嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:38:58.42,0:39:02.58,ENG,,0,0,0,,And this... l mean, this is not a video game, son. it really isn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:59.65,0:39:02.52,CHT,,0,0,0,,這不是電動游戲，不是
Dialogue: 0,0:39:04.59,0:39:06.51,ENG,,0,0,0,,It really isn't. No.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:04.86,0:39:06.66,CHT,,0,0,0,,真的不是
Dialogue: 0,0:39:11.30,0:39:12.85,ENG,,0,0,0,,We are a go for auto-sequence start.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:11.67,0:39:13.22,CHT,,0,0,0,,將啟動自動發射裝置
Dialogue: 0,0:39:13.34,0:39:15.46,CHT,,0,0,0,,電腦將操控各項功能
Dialogue: 0,0:39:14.56,0:39:15.76,ENG,,0,0,0,,Atlantis' four on board computers
Dialogue: 0,0:39:15.64,0:39:19.16,CHT,,0,0,0,,“彌賽亞計劃，第一天”
Dialogue: 0,0:39:15.85,0:39:19.06,ENG,,0,0,0,,now have primary control of all the vehicle's critical functions.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:19.14,0:39:20.56,ENG,,0,0,0,,Okay, all flight controllers.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:19.27,0:39:22.90,CHT,,0,0,0,,基地人員，倒數30秒計時
Dialogue: 0,0:39:20.65,0:39:23.31,ENG,,0,0,0,,We're at T-minus 30 seconds and counting.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:23.40,0:39:24.69,ENG,,0,0,0,,Let's take a close look.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:23.48,0:39:24.78,CHT,,0,0,0,,仔細檢查
Dialogue: 0,0:39:24.77,0:39:27.74,ENG,,0,0,0,,APUs look good, logs and LH2 are pressurized.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:24.88,0:39:28.08,CHT,,0,0,0,,輔助裝置正常液態氫氧已加壓
Dialogue: 0,0:39:27.90,0:39:30.82,ENG,,0,0,0,,- Ten, nine, eight... - Flight, we're go for auto-sequence.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:29.62,0:39:30.88,CHT,,0,0,0,,啟動自動裝置
Dialogue: 0,0:39:30.91,0:39:32.03,ENG,,0,0,0,,- Roger, Jerry. - ...seven, six...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:30.99,0:39:33.72,CHT,,0,0,0,,知道了，一路平安
Dialogue: 0,0:39:32.12,0:39:34.91,ENG,,0,0,0,,- Good luck and Godspeed, Atlantis. - Thanks, Mitch.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:33.82,0:39:34.98,CHT,,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:39:34.99,0:39:37.58,ENG,,0,0,0,,...three, two, one.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:35.16,0:39:38.09,CHT,,0,0,0,,…3、2、1
Dialogue: 0,0:39:51.76,0:39:54.64,ENG,,0,0,0,,Propelled by 500,000 pounds of liquid fuel,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:51.84,0:39:55.14,CHT,,0,0,0,,50萬磅的液體燃料
Dialogue: 0,0:39:54.97,0:39:58.02,ENG,,0,0,0,,the shuttle crew heads toward their initial destination.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:55.24,0:39:58.18,CHT,,0,0,0,,將太空組員送往目的地
Dialogue: 0,0:39:58.10,0:39:59.73,ENG,,0,0,0,,When the crew enters the Messiah,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:58.28,0:40:02.58,CHT,,0,0,0,,抵達彌賽亞號後機上載有8枚核彈
Dialogue: 0,0:39:59.81,0:40:02.48,ENG,,0,0,0,,they will find a payload of eight nuclear devices
Dialogue: 0,0:40:02.56,0:40:05.23,ENG,,0,0,0,,that will eventually be used to blow up the comet.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:02.69,0:40:05.28,CHT,,0,0,0,,藉以炸燬彗星
Dialogue: 0,0:40:05.32,0:40:06.57,ENG,,0,0,0,,The Messiah itself will be powered
Dialogue: 0,0:40:05.42,0:40:09.29,CHT,,0,0,0,,彌賽亞號採實驗動力引擎
Dialogue: 0,0:40:06.65,0:40:09.19,ENG,,0,0,0,,by an experimental nuclear propulsion system
Dialogue: 0,0:40:09.28,0:40:11.90,ENG,,0,0,0,,that was originally created for a very different purpose.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:09.39,0:40:12.06,CHT,,0,0,0,,並非當初研發的目的
Dialogue: 0,0:40:13.20,0:40:15.45,ENG,,0,0,0,,That program was called Orion.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:13.40,0:40:17.13,CHT,,0,0,0,,實驗引擎稱作獵戶座
Dialogue: 0,0:40:16.45,0:40:18.45,ENG,,0,0,0,,Now, with the help of Russian engineers,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:17.23,0:40:19.33,CHT,,0,0,0,,藉俄國工程師支援
Dialogue: 0,0:40:19.33,0:40:22.62,ENG,,0,0,0,,a technology designed to propel weapons of mass destruction
Dialogue: 0,0:40:19.44,0:40:22.77,CHT,,0,0,0,,將毀滅性武器推進系統
Dialogue: 0,0:40:22.83,0:40:25.21,ENG,,0,0,0,,will power the ship that will intercept the greatest threat
Dialogue: 0,0:40:22.87,0:40:27.57,CHT,,0,0,0,,供作太空船動力以攔截彗星
Dialogue: 0,0:40:25.29,0:40:27.34,ENG,,0,0,0,,our planet has ever faced.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:36.89,0:40:39.55,CHT,,0,0,0,,獵戶座推進，倒數10…
Dialogue: 0,0:40:36.89,0:40:41.81,ENG,,0,0,0,,Orion burn in ten, nine, eight,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:40.30,0:40:40.97,CHT,,0,0,0,,9
Dialogue: 0,0:40:41.43,0:40:42.10,CHT,,0,0,0,,8
Dialogue: 0,0:40:42.23,0:40:44.90,ENG,,0,0,0,,seven, six, five,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:42.39,0:40:45.06,CHT,,0,0,0,,7、6、5
Dialogue: 0,0:40:45.15,0:40:49.44,ENG,,0,0,0,,four, three, two, one, zero.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:45.16,0:40:46.60,CHT,,0,0,0,,4、3
Dialogue: 0,0:40:47.07,0:40:48.53,CHT,,0,0,0,,2、1
Dialogue: 0,0:40:48.84,0:40:49.51,CHT,,0,0,0,,0
Dialogue: 0,0:41:00.58,0:41:04.41,ENG,,0,0,0,,Okay. Beth, White House reactions. Marianne, the whole world watching.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:00.65,0:41:02.20,CHT,,0,0,0,,貝絲，查知白宮反應瑪莉安，各地反應
Dialogue: 0,0:41:02.31,0:41:05.11,CHT,,0,0,0,,{\pos(185,230)}“五個月後”
Dialogue: 0,0:41:04.50,0:41:06.63,ENG,,0,0,0,,- We have enough satellite space? - Seventy-eight uplinks.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:05.22,0:41:06.71,CHT,,0,0,0,,衛星？    78個頻道
Dialogue: 0,0:41:06.71,0:41:09.92,ENG,,0,0,0,,Tim, mission control in Houston. lra, the science guys lined up?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:06.82,0:41:10.05,CHT,,0,0,0,,提姆，聯絡休士頓艾拉，科學家呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:41:10.00,0:41:11.38,ENG,,0,0,0,,If they got a Ph.D., we own them.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:10.16,0:41:11.52,CHT,,0,0,0,,到齊了
Dialogue: 0,0:41:11.46,0:41:16.26,ENG,,0,0,0,,All right, this is the most important story of our lives. Let's not muck it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:11.63,0:41:13.79,CHT,,0,0,0,,世紀最大的新聞
Dialogue: 0,0:41:13.89,0:41:15.29,CHT,,0,0,0,,別搞砸了
Dialogue: 0,0:41:16.33,0:41:17.80,CHT,,0,0,0,,史都華，我做什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:41:16.34,0:41:18.97,ENG,,0,0,0,,- Stuart, what about me? - You're on the anchor desk.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:17.90,0:41:21.03,CHT,,0,0,0,,你上主播台，你早就該上了
Dialogue: 0,0:41:19.06,0:41:20.81,ENG,,0,0,0,,And you could have been there a lot sooner.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:20.89,0:41:23.02,ENG,,0,0,0,,- What are you talking about? - You know what I'm talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:21.13,0:41:22.07,CHT,,0,0,0,,什麼意思？
Dialogue: 0,0:41:22.17,0:41:25.23,CHT,,0,0,0,,你心裡有數，別再隱瞞新聞
Dialogue: 0,0:41:23.10,0:41:25.98,ENG,,0,0,0,,Don't ever hold back a story from me again.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:38.28,0:41:42.83,ENG,,0,0,0,,Messiah, Houston. Transfer trajectory is go. Cancel MCC 1.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:38.49,0:41:41.58,CHT,,0,0,0,,彌賽亞呼叫休士頓已轉入彗星軌道
Dialogue: 0,0:41:41.69,0:41:45.68,CHT,,0,0,0,,航道正常，無動力漂浮
Dialogue: 0,0:41:43.08,0:41:45.50,ENG,,0,0,0,,You're go to configure for coast.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:46.67,0:41:49.38,ENG,,0,0,0,,Roger, Houston, we're looking good here.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:46.79,0:41:49.39,CHT,,0,0,0,,知悉，目前狀況良好
Dialogue: 0,0:41:52.05,0:41:53.76,ENG,,0,0,0,,Jesus, that's big.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:52.07,0:41:53.62,CHT,,0,0,0,,天啊！好大！
Dialogue: 0,0:41:54.47,0:41:55.84,ENG,,0,0,0,,Holy shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:54.60,0:41:56.00,CHT,,0,0,0,,大得嚇人！
Dialogue: 0,0:41:56.24,0:41:57.64,CHT,,0,0,0,,天啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:42:01.06,0:42:02.85,ENG,,0,0,0,,Sweet mother of God.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:01.08,0:42:03.48,CHT,,0,0,0,,我的媽啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:42:14.28,0:42:17.28,ENG,,0,0,0,,All circuit breakers are open. Master arm is off.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:14.36,0:42:15.72,CHT,,0,0,0,,切斷回路裝置
Dialogue: 0,0:42:15.82,0:42:17.35,CHT,,0,0,0,,關閉主控鈕
Dialogue: 0,0:42:17.36,0:42:20.07,ENG,,0,0,0,,Roger. And the detonator system is safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:17.46,0:42:20.39,CHT,,0,0,0,,知悉，設定引爆保護
Dialogue: 0,0:42:23.53,0:42:25.47,CHT,,0,0,0,,“核彈取出”
Dialogue: 0,0:42:39.18,0:42:41.64,ENG,,0,0,0,,Messiah, Houston. Stand by for an uplink
Dialogue: 0,0:42:39.35,0:42:41.84,CHT,,0,0,0,,彌賽亞，休士頓呼叫
Dialogue: 0,0:42:41.72,0:42:44.43,ENG,,0,0,0,,of the final MOLE coordinates. Confirm when complete.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:41.95,0:42:44.58,CHT,,0,0,0,,確實做好座標設定並待命
Dialogue: 0,0:42:44.52,0:42:46.10,ENG,,0,0,0,,Wilco, Houston.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:44.69,0:42:45.85,CHT,,0,0,0,,好的！休士頓
Dialogue: 0,0:42:46.27,0:42:48.06,ENG,,0,0,0,,Hey, how's it coming?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:46.39,0:42:47.58,CHT,,0,0,0,,情況如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:42:48.19,0:42:50.15,ENG,,0,0,0,,Loading first nuke now.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:48.29,0:42:50.42,CHT,,0,0,0,,裝入第一顆核彈
Dialogue: 0,0:43:18.62,0:43:20.49,CHT,,0,0,0,,距離1千英尺
Dialogue: 0,0:43:18.68,0:43:20.72,ENG,,0,0,0,,1,000 feet to standoff.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:20.80,0:43:24.22,ENG,,0,0,0,,Rdot 3, 5x, 2y.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:20.89,0:43:24.85,CHT,,0,0,0,,半徑速率點3.5X、2Y
Dialogue: 0,0:43:28.10,0:43:34.02,ENG,,0,0,0,,500 feet. Rdot.3, 3x, 1 .5y.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:28.17,0:43:31.33,CHT,,0,0,0,,5百英尺，半徑速率點3
Dialogue: 0,0:43:31.64,0:43:32.57,CHT,,0,0,0,,3X
Dialogue: 0,0:43:32.70,0:43:34.50,CHT,,0,0,0,,1.5Y
Dialogue: 0,0:43:35.02,0:43:36.90,ENG,,0,0,0,,Go for auto trajectory.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:35.21,0:43:37.14,CHT,,0,0,0,,自動導入軌道
Dialogue: 0,0:43:39.78,0:43:42.11,CHT,,0,0,0,,開啟  調整誤差
Dialogue: 0,0:43:39.78,0:43:40.86,ENG,,0,0,0,,We're there.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:41.03,0:43:43.49,ENG,,0,0,0,,- Residuals are nulled. - Disengage Orion.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:42.21,0:43:43.18,CHT,,0,0,0,,脫離獵戶座
Dialogue: 0,0:43:44.91,0:43:47.41,ENG,,0,0,0,,Orion disengaged. You're on bi-prop.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:45.12,0:43:48.02,CHT,,0,0,0,,脫離，採二元推進器
Dialogue: 0,0:43:59.01,0:44:03.89,ENG,,0,0,0,,This is a special presentation of MSNBC News with Jenny Lerner.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:59.31,0:44:03.07,CHT,,0,0,0,,國家廣播電台特別報導
Dialogue: 0,0:44:03.18,0:44:04.58,CHT,,0,0,0,,珍妮藍納主播
Dialogue: 0,0:44:10.31,0:44:11.81,ENG,,0,0,0,,Good evening.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:10.32,0:44:11.75,CHT,,0,0,0,,晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:44:11.85,0:44:13.61,CHT,,0,0,0,,一小時後
Dialogue: 0,0:44:11.89,0:44:14.60,ENG,,0,0,0,,Sometime in the next hour, the Messiah mission
Dialogue: 0,0:44:13.72,0:44:16.75,CHT,,0,0,0,,彌賽亞將執行任務
Dialogue: 0,0:44:14.69,0:44:16.52,ENG,,0,0,0,,will enter its most critical phase.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:16.61,0:44:20.53,ENG,,0,0,0,,The interception of Wolf-Biederman and the setting of the nuclear devices
Dialogue: 0,0:44:16.86,0:44:18.95,CHT,,0,0,0,,攔截沃夫畢德曼彗星
Dialogue: 0,0:44:19.06,0:44:23.26,CHT,,0,0,0,,用核彈將它打偏航道
Dialogue: 0,0:44:20.61,0:44:24.24,ENG,,0,0,0,,that will deflect it off its collision course with Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:24.57,0:44:28.66,CHT,,0,0,0,,首先，譚納得通過…
Dialogue: 0,0:44:24.57,0:44:28.54,ENG,,0,0,0,,But first, Captain Spurgeon Tanner will have to guide the spacecraft
Dialogue: 0,0:44:28.62,0:44:33.12,ENG,,0,0,0,,through the blizzard of rocks, sand and ice that make up the comet's tail,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:28.77,0:44:31.24,CHT,,0,0,0,,混合砂、石、冰的慧尾
Dialogue: 0,0:44:31.34,0:44:34.71,CHT,,0,0,0,,才能著陸在慧星之上
Dialogue: 0,0:44:33.42,0:44:34.62,ENG,,0,0,0,,or coma.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:34.71,0:44:37.84,ENG,,0,0,0,,The crew will have to complete its work before the sun rises.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:34.81,0:44:37.64,CHT,,0,0,0,,任務須在日升之前完成
Dialogue: 0,0:44:37.92,0:44:41.51,ENG,,0,0,0,,- Sublimator looks good, Mick. - Disengaging auto now.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:37.98,0:44:39.57,CHT,,0,0,0,,蒸氣機正常
Dialogue: 0,0:44:39.85,0:44:44.22,CHT,,0,0,0,,脫離自動控制，改由我操控
Dialogue: 0,0:44:41.88,0:44:44.18,ENG,,0,0,0,,I'm eyeballs out from here on in.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:44.26,0:44:46.60,ENG,,0,0,0,,How come that doesn't make me feel any better?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:44.32,0:44:46.65,CHT,,0,0,0,,聽了令人擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:44:46.68,0:44:48.14,ENG,,0,0,0,,I heard that.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:46.76,0:44:47.92,CHT,,0,0,0,,我聽到了
Dialogue: 0,0:44:48.26,0:44:49.60,ENG,,0,0,0,,Lights on.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:48.29,0:44:49.35,CHT,,0,0,0,,開頭燈
Dialogue: 0,0:44:50.59,0:44:51.72,CHT,,0,0,0,,啟動攝影機
Dialogue: 0,0:44:50.64,0:44:51.89,ENG,,0,0,0,,Cameras on.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:51.98,0:44:53.94,ENG,,0,0,0,,On the Mississippi River in Mark Twain's time,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:52.26,0:44:54.09,CHT,,0,0,0,,密西西比河上的船夫
Dialogue: 0,0:44:54.02,0:44:57.69,ENG,,0,0,0,,there were riverboat pilots who only knew a few miles of the river.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:54.20,0:44:57.63,CHT,,0,0,0,,只熟悉幾里的河道
Dialogue: 0,0:44:57.73,0:45:01.13,CHT,,0,0,0,,河道千變萬化，不能盡知
Dialogue: 0,0:44:57.77,0:45:01.61,ENG,,0,0,0,,I mean, conditions changed so much you couldn't know the whole trip.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:01.69,0:45:03.95,ENG,,0,0,0,,Floods, sandbars, fallen logs.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:01.74,0:45:05.70,CHT,,0,0,0,,泛濫、沙洲、斷木船夫只能…
Dialogue: 0,0:45:04.45,0:45:06.03,ENG,,0,0,0,,It was all a riverboat pilot could do,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:05.81,0:45:09.84,CHT,,0,0,0,,靈活運用經驗
Dialogue: 0,0:45:06.12,0:45:09.16,ENG,,0,0,0,,was to know his little piece of the puzzle.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:10.41,0:45:13.08,CHT,,0,0,0,,我將是這艘船的船夫
Dialogue: 0,0:45:10.41,0:45:13.33,ENG,,0,0,0,,So, for the next few hours, this is my ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:14.29,0:45:16.17,ENG,,0,0,0,,We start our approach.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:14.32,0:45:15.94,CHT,,0,0,0,,開始降落
Dialogue: 0,0:45:28.22,0:45:32.39,ENG,,0,0,0,,...are images from cameras mounted inside the cargo bay of the Messiah.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:28.23,0:45:32.50,CHT,,0,0,0,,這是彌賽亞貨艙攝影機的鏡頭
Dialogue: 0,0:45:32.48,0:45:35.81,ENG,,0,0,0,,Now, these images are delayed by approximately 20 seconds,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:32.60,0:45:36.00,CHT,,0,0,0,,畫面因傳送距離遙遠
Dialogue: 0,0:45:35.90,0:45:38.06,ENG,,0,0,0,,due to the distance they must travel.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:36.11,0:45:38.47,CHT,,0,0,0,,導致延誤約20秒
Dialogue: 0,0:45:38.15,0:45:41.36,ENG,,0,0,0,,Okay, you can see that the image is breaking up a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:38.58,0:45:41.04,CHT,,0,0,0,,畫面目前不太清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:45:41.14,0:45:43.64,CHT,,0,0,0,,休士頓預料這情況可能發生
Dialogue: 0,0:45:41.44,0:45:43.61,ENG,,0,0,0,,Houston is prepared for this.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:43.69,0:45:46.15,ENG,,0,0,0,,They've informed us that due to the uncertain makeup
Dialogue: 0,0:45:43.75,0:45:47.77,CHT,,0,0,0,,因無法確定彗星的構造
Dialogue: 0,0:45:46.24,0:45:47.74,ENG,,0,0,0,,of the comet's coma,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:47.82,0:45:51.24,ENG,,0,0,0,,they're unsure whether or not transmission will be possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:47.88,0:45:51.18,CHT,,0,0,0,,故不確定能否接收訊號
Dialogue: 0,0:45:51.29,0:45:55.42,CHT,,0,0,0,,目前接收不良
Dialogue: 0,0:45:51.33,0:45:54.96,ENG,,0,0,0,,Okay, now it appears we're losing reception here.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:56.17,0:46:00.71,ENG,,0,0,0,,Okay, we've lost picture now, but we will stay on the air.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:56.36,0:46:00.63,CHT,,0,0,0,,畫面消失但我們會繼續報導
Dialogue: 0,0:46:00.73,0:46:03.43,CHT,,0,0,0,,與各位一同等待
Dialogue: 0,0:46:00.80,0:46:03.51,ENG,,0,0,0,,We'll stay with you through all of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:06.97,0:46:10.81,CHT,,0,0,0,,動力96%，下降中
Dialogue: 0,0:46:07.01,0:46:08.51,ENG,,0,0,0,,Prop, 96%.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:09.39,0:46:12.39,ENG,,0,0,0,,- DAP is in descent. - Roger, descent.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:10.91,0:46:12.40,CHT,,0,0,0,,知悉，下降中
Dialogue: 0,0:46:19.19,0:46:22.90,ENG,,0,0,0,,Oh, my God. Look at these, they're the size of houses.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:19.45,0:46:20.38,CHT,,0,0,0,,天啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:46:21.09,0:46:23.45,CHT,,0,0,0,,跟房子一樣大
Dialogue: 0,0:46:23.28,0:46:25.36,ENG,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I know. I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:23.56,0:46:25.46,CHT,,0,0,0,,可不是
Dialogue: 0,0:46:39.71,0:46:41.21,ENG,,0,0,0,,Jesus Christ.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:39.81,0:46:41.40,CHT,,0,0,0,,老天！
Dialogue: 0,0:46:41.67,0:46:43.00,ENG,,0,0,0,,Prop, 88%.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:41.84,0:46:42.93,CHT,,0,0,0,,動力88%
Dialogue: 0,0:46:44.01,0:46:45.63,ENG,,0,0,0,,Cabin press, 5.7.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:44.24,0:46:46.27,CHT,,0,0,0,,艙壓5.7
Dialogue: 0,0:46:46.76,0:46:48.76,ENG,,0,0,0,,Negative guidance errors.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:46.91,0:46:48.28,CHT,,0,0,0,,導航系統正常
Dialogue: 0,0:47:13.47,0:47:14.81,CHT,,0,0,0,,用主推進器
Dialogue: 0,0:47:13.49,0:47:16.29,ENG,,0,0,0,,- Use primary thrusters. - Engage thrusters.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:15.54,0:47:16.74,CHT,,0,0,0,,主推進器
Dialogue: 0,0:47:27.67,0:47:31.09,ENG,,0,0,0,,- What's the descent rate? - Three feet per second. Two.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:27.69,0:47:29.95,CHT,,0,0,0,,下降速度？    每秒3英尺
Dialogue: 0,0:47:30.32,0:47:31.29,CHT,,0,0,0,,2英尺
Dialogue: 0,0:47:31.43,0:47:33.89,ENG,,0,0,0,,- Fire tether pitons. - Pitons fired.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:31.63,0:47:32.75,CHT,,0,0,0,,發射固定鏈栓
Dialogue: 0,0:47:32.89,0:47:33.62,CHT,,0,0,0,,發射
Dialogue: 0,0:47:47.44,0:47:49.15,ENG,,0,0,0,,She's leveling out.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:47.54,0:47:48.87,CHT,,0,0,0,,水平下降
Dialogue: 0,0:48:16.01,0:48:19.89,ENG,,0,0,0,,- Depressurizing bay. - Opening payload doors.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:16.31,0:48:18.00,CHT,,0,0,0,,貨艙減壓
Dialogue: 0,0:48:18.47,0:48:20.64,CHT,,0,0,0,,打開艙門
Dialogue: 0,0:48:21.04,0:48:24.38,CHT,,0,0,0,,別被微弱的動力唬了
Dialogue: 0,0:48:21.14,0:48:25.19,ENG,,0,0,0,,Don't let that little bit of gravity down there go to your heads.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:25.90,0:48:26.98,ENG,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:28.28,0:48:29.90,ENG,,0,0,0,,Start the clock.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:28.29,0:48:29.65,CHT,,0,0,0,,開始計時
Dialogue: 0,0:49:21.00,0:49:25.12,ENG,,0,0,0,,If all is going according to schedule, the astronauts should now be placing
Dialogue: 0,0:49:21.17,0:49:23.37,CHT,,0,0,0,,若依照進度…
Dialogue: 0,0:49:23.48,0:49:27.31,CHT,,0,0,0,,太空人正在彗星操作“錢鼠”
Dialogue: 0,0:49:25.21,0:49:27.29,ENG,,0,0,0,,the MOLEs on the comet surface.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:27.38,0:49:30.71,ENG,,0,0,0,,The MOLEs are... Well, they're what they sound like.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:27.55,0:49:32.14,CHT,,0,0,0,,“錢鼠”是攜核彈鑽土機
Dialogue: 0,0:49:30.88,0:49:35.55,ENG,,0,0,0,,They are drilling machines that burrow to a depth of 100 meters,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:32.25,0:49:35.71,CHT,,0,0,0,,深入地下1百公尺
Dialogue: 0,0:49:35.64,0:49:37.80,ENG,,0,0,0,,where they wait to be detonated.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:35.82,0:49:39.19,CHT,,0,0,0,,等待引爆，每個錢鼠
Dialogue: 0,0:49:37.89,0:49:41.60,ENG,,0,0,0,,Each one carries a 5,000 kiloton warhead.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:39.29,0:49:42.75,CHT,,0,0,0,,攜帶5千千噸威力核彈
Dialogue: 0,0:49:58.41,0:49:59.47,CHT,,0,0,0,,還有多少時間？
Dialogue: 0,0:49:58.45,0:50:01.58,ENG,,0,0,0,,- How's our time? - It's getting tight. 1:36:30.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:59.75,0:50:01.81,CHT,,0,0,0,,只剩1小時36分30秒
Dialogue: 0,0:50:01.91,0:50:03.75,ENG,,0,0,0,,It's taking too long.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:01.92,0:50:03.25,CHT,,0,0,0,,進度太慢
Dialogue: 0,0:50:04.58,0:50:05.66,ENG,,0,0,0,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:08.59,0:50:11.92,CHT,,0,0,0,,“距離日升：1點35分58秒”
Dialogue: 0,0:50:12.13,0:50:15.72,CHT,,0,0,0,,若沒能及時離開彗星會如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:50:12.17,0:50:16.13,ENG,,0,0,0,,What happens if they do not get off the comet's surface in time?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:16.34,0:50:18.34,ENG,,0,0,0,,The sun striking the comet will cause the temperature
Dialogue: 0,0:50:16.36,0:50:19.73,CHT,,0,0,0,,太陽直射彗星，溫度驟升
Dialogue: 0,0:50:18.43,0:50:21.55,ENG,,0,0,0,,to rise 350 degrees in just a few minutes,
Dialogue: 0,0:50:19.80,0:50:21.79,CHT,,0,0,0,,幾分鐘內升高350度
Dialogue: 0,0:50:21.76,0:50:24.35,ENG,,0,0,0,,and activate the high-speed gas jets.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:22.10,0:50:24.77,CHT,,0,0,0,,引發地底噴射流
Dialogue: 0,0:50:24.89,0:50:29.10,ENG,,0,0,0,,Well, if that happens, it will be like trying to work in a minefield.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:25.11,0:50:29.37,CHT,,0,0,0,,一旦爆發就像身處佈雷區
Dialogue: 0,0:50:29.56,0:50:33.69,ENG,,0,0,0,,- Mark, what's your MOLE 4 readout? - MOLE 4 running true at 75 feet.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:29.58,0:50:31.34,CHT,,0,0,0,,錢鼠4號情形如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:50:31.45,0:50:33.85,CHT,,0,0,0,,鑽入75英尺
Dialogue: 0,0:50:38.32,0:50:39.55,CHT,,0,0,0,,渾蛋！
Dialogue: 0,0:50:38.32,0:50:40.16,ENG,,0,0,0,,- Son of a bitch. - What?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:39.65,0:50:41.71,CHT,,0,0,0,,怎麼了？    卡住了
Dialogue: 0,0:50:40.24,0:50:42.53,ENG,,0,0,0,,- It's stuck. - Try backing it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:41.82,0:50:44.02,CHT,,0,0,0,,反轉試試    深度多少？
Dialogue: 0,0:50:42.95,0:50:45.41,ENG,,0,0,0,,- What's your depth? - Seventy-five feet.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:44.23,0:50:45.42,CHT,,0,0,0,,75英尺
Dialogue: 0,0:50:45.50,0:50:47.79,ENG,,0,0,0,,- Is that enough? - No, that'll just break pieces
Dialogue: 0,0:50:45.70,0:50:46.75,CHT,,0,0,0,,夠深了？
Dialogue: 0,0:50:46.86,0:50:48.63,CHT,,0,0,0,,不夠，只能炸碎表面
Dialogue: 0,0:50:47.87,0:50:49.62,ENG,,0,0,0,,- off the surface. - That's not deep enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:48.73,0:50:49.70,CHT,,0,0,0,,不夠深
Dialogue: 0,0:50:49.71,0:50:52.50,ENG,,0,0,0,,Yeah, Fish, I know that's not deep enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:49.83,0:50:52.30,CHT,,0,0,0,,我知道不夠深
Dialogue: 0,0:50:53.50,0:50:55.60,CHT,,0,0,0,,我下去    不，歐仁
Dialogue: 0,0:50:53.55,0:50:55.34,ENG,,0,0,0,,- I'm going in. - Oren, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:55.42,0:50:58.05,ENG,,0,0,0,,No, I'm gonna see if I can free it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:55.74,0:50:57.60,CHT,,0,0,0,,試試能否修好
Dialogue: 0,0:50:58.68,0:51:01.59,ENG,,0,0,0,,- Standby tether attached. - All right, I got you.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:58.84,0:51:00.40,CHT,,0,0,0,,準備支援
Dialogue: 0,0:51:00.51,0:51:01.84,CHT,,0,0,0,,抓緊了
Dialogue: 0,0:51:01.68,0:51:04.18,ENG,,0,0,0,,Oren, suit pressure, 3.5.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:01.94,0:51:04.07,CHT,,0,0,0,,歐仁，太空衣壓力3.5
Dialogue: 0,0:51:12.69,0:51:14.49,CHT,,0,0,0,,“距離日升：24分06秒”
Dialogue: 0,0:51:16.28,0:51:17.90,ENG,,0,0,0,,Come on, come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:16.36,0:51:17.88,CHT,,0,0,0,,快啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:51:21.87,0:51:24.28,ENG,,0,0,0,,- How's my time? - 23:57.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:22.07,0:51:23.09,CHT,,0,0,0,,剩多少時間？
Dialogue: 0,0:51:23.20,0:51:24.43,CHT,,0,0,0,,23分57秒
Dialogue: 0,0:51:24.37,0:51:28.12,ENG,,0,0,0,,Another six minutes, they won't have time to get back to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:24.54,0:51:26.44,CHT,,0,0,0,,他們無法及時趕回
Dialogue: 0,0:51:28.96,0:51:30.83,ENG,,0,0,0,,Blow the tethers. Let's go get them.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:29.04,0:51:31.06,CHT,,0,0,0,,鬆脫固定鏈栓，去接他們
Dialogue: 0,0:51:30.92,0:51:33.33,ENG,,0,0,0,,If we go after them, we may not have enough fuel to get off the surface.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:31.18,0:51:33.27,CHT,,0,0,0,,這樣會用掉太多燃料
Dialogue: 0,0:51:33.38,0:51:34.90,CHT,,0,0,0,,鬆脫固定鏈栓！
Dialogue: 0,0:51:33.42,0:51:34.96,ENG,,0,0,0,,Go on, blow the goddamn tethers!
Dialogue: 0,0:51:36.51,0:51:39.26,ENG,,0,0,0,,MOLE 3 at depth. We're heading your way, Oren.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:36.58,0:51:38.78,CHT,,0,0,0,,錢鼠3號裝妥，我們過來了
Dialogue: 0,0:51:39.34,0:51:42.22,ENG,,0,0,0,,Calculate exactly how much prop we need to get off this rock.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:39.45,0:51:42.25,CHT,,0,0,0,,扣除回程所需動力
Dialogue: 0,0:51:42.30,0:51:45.31,ENG,,0,0,0,,- We'll shut it down when we hit it. - Will do.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:42.39,0:51:44.08,CHT,,0,0,0,,我們只用剩餘動力
Dialogue: 0,0:51:44.52,0:51:54.75,CHT,,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:51:54.65,0:51:58.82,ENG,,0,0,0,,It opens up into a cave down here. MOLE gotjammed against the side.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:54.75,0:51:57.08,CHT,,0,0,0,,挖鑿了一個洞穴
Dialogue: 0,0:51:57.18,0:51:58.98,CHT,,0,0,0,,錢鼠被洞壁卡住
Dialogue: 0,0:52:00.69,0:52:03.99,CHT,,0,0,0,,第2小隊抵達錢鼠4號
Dialogue: 0,0:52:00.70,0:52:04.28,ENG,,0,0,0,,Okay, Fish, team two at location four. Give me your hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:07.04,0:52:08.95,ENG,,0,0,0,,- What in the hell happened? - I don't know. I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:07.09,0:52:08.46,CHT,,0,0,0,,怎麼回事？不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:52:08.56,0:52:11.96,CHT,,0,0,0,,突然卡在75英尺處
Dialogue: 0,0:52:09.04,0:52:12.58,ENG,,0,0,0,,Everything was going great. We gotjammed up at 75 feet.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:14.20,0:52:15.73,CHT,,0,0,0,,“燃料存量顯示”
Dialogue: 0,0:52:21.30,0:52:22.80,ENG,,0,0,0,,Okay, hold up.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:21.48,0:52:22.84,CHT,,0,0,0,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:52:23.76,0:52:26.93,ENG,,0,0,0,,- All right, try backing it up. - Roger that.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:23.98,0:52:26.21,CHT,,0,0,0,,試著反轉錢鼠
Dialogue: 0,0:52:26.38,0:52:27.41,CHT,,0,0,0,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:52:43.66,0:52:45.70,ENG,,0,0,0,,- That's it. - No, a little more, a little more.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:43.73,0:52:44.56,CHT,,0,0,0,,到達極限
Dialogue: 0,0:52:44.67,0:52:45.79,CHT,,0,0,0,,不，還有一些
Dialogue: 0,0:52:45.78,0:52:47.62,ENG,,0,0,0,,- Shut it down. - No, look, they always put extra
Dialogue: 0,0:52:45.90,0:52:46.60,CHT,,0,0,0,,關掉
Dialogue: 0,0:52:46.70,0:52:48.07,CHT,,0,0,0,,會有額外的油
Dialogue: 0,0:52:47.70,0:52:50.25,ENG,,0,0,0,,- in these tanks. - Fish, shut it down.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:48.14,0:52:50.33,CHT,,0,0,0,,小魚！關引擎
Dialogue: 0,0:52:52.33,0:52:53.41,ENG,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:59.12,0:53:01.88,CHT,,0,0,0,,快啊！渾蛋，快轉！
Dialogue: 0,0:52:59.26,0:53:02.92,ENG,,0,0,0,,Come on, you bastard! Come on! Time.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:02.15,0:53:02.81,CHT,,0,0,0,,時間？
Dialogue: 0,0:53:03.26,0:53:04.26,ENG,,0,0,0,,1:02.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:03.39,0:53:06.62,CHT,,0,0,0,,剩1分2秒，我來接你們
Dialogue: 0,0:53:04.34,0:53:06.72,ENG,,0,0,0,,Figured we'd better pick you kids up after school.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:06.80,0:53:08.85,ENG,,0,0,0,,Check your six, 100 yards.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:06.99,0:53:09.02,CHT,,0,0,0,,6點鐘方向，1百碼處
Dialogue: 0,0:53:11.27,0:53:13.60,ENG,,0,0,0,,I think we'd better hurry, boys.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:11.30,0:53:12.79,CHT,,0,0,0,,我們最好快一點
Dialogue: 0,0:53:15.23,0:53:17.29,CHT,,0,0,0,,“日升達地平線”
Dialogue: 0,0:53:21.44,0:53:23.86,ENG,,0,0,0,,All right, it's going! it's going.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:21.61,0:53:23.10,CHT,,0,0,0,,動了！動了
Dialogue: 0,0:53:38.56,0:53:40.25,CHT,,0,0,0,,“日升達地平線”
Dialogue: 0,0:53:40.25,0:53:42.13,ENG,,0,0,0,,MOLE'S at 125 feet.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:40.36,0:53:42.09,CHT,,0,0,0,,錢鼠深達125英尺
Dialogue: 0,0:53:42.19,0:53:44.56,CHT,,0,0,0,,太陽升起，速度很快
Dialogue: 0,0:53:42.21,0:53:44.59,ENG,,0,0,0,,The sun's rising behind you. It's coming up fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:49.77,0:53:50.76,CHT,,0,0,0,,“日升高於地平線”
Dialogue: 0,0:53:51.04,0:53:52.44,CHT,,0,0,0,,拉下護面罩
Dialogue: 0,0:53:51.14,0:53:52.60,ENG,,0,0,0,,Face shields down!
Dialogue: 0,0:53:53.87,0:53:55.31,CHT,,0,0,0,,天啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:53:54.06,0:53:55.31,ENG,,0,0,0,,Christ.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:55.81,0:53:57.85,ENG,,0,0,0,,Get the hell out of there!
Dialogue: 0,0:53:55.97,0:53:57.44,CHT,,0,0,0,,快離開那裡！
Dialogue: 0,0:54:00.61,0:54:02.10,CHT,,0,0,0,,“日升高於地平線”
Dialogue: 0,0:54:09.53,0:54:12.62,ENG,,0,0,0,,Oren, get your visor down! Get your visor down!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:09.76,0:54:12.28,CHT,,0,0,0,,拉下護面罩
Dialogue: 0,0:54:17.54,0:54:18.79,ENG,,0,0,0,,My eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:17.73,0:54:18.89,CHT,,0,0,0,,我的眼睛…
Dialogue: 0,0:54:22.71,0:54:26.01,ENG,,0,0,0,,- All right, we got him. - Oh, God! My eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:22.87,0:54:24.10,CHT,,0,0,0,,扶住他了
Dialogue: 0,0:54:25.14,0:54:26.23,CHT,,0,0,0,,我的眼睛
Dialogue: 0,0:55:07.59,0:55:09.97,ENG,,0,0,0,,God, we're losing one. He's got escape velocity.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:07.72,0:55:11.91,CHT,,0,0,0,,天！失去一名組員噴離1百英尺遠
Dialogue: 0,0:55:10.05,0:55:12.22,ENG,,0,0,0,,1,000 feet and climbing.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:15.35,0:55:18.14,ENG,,0,0,0,,Mark, Mikhail, get the hell out of there!
Dialogue: 0,0:55:15.52,0:55:18.19,CHT,,0,0,0,,馬克、米海爾，快離開！
Dialogue: 0,0:55:34.51,0:55:35.38,CHT,,0,0,0,,“升降環”
Dialogue: 0,0:55:39.00,0:55:41.50,ENG,,0,0,0,,- Firing primary thrusters. - Payload doors still open.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:39.18,0:55:40.27,CHT,,0,0,0,,啟動推進器
Dialogue: 0,0:55:40.38,0:55:41.44,CHT,,0,0,0,,貨艙門還沒關
Dialogue: 0,0:55:41.55,0:55:42.64,CHT,,0,0,0,,起飛後關上
Dialogue: 0,0:55:41.58,0:55:43.33,ENG,,0,0,0,,Close them as we go.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:02.60,0:56:06.61,ENG,,0,0,0,,Houston, all MOLEs are at depth. Nukes hot and ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:02.74,0:56:06.90,CHT,,0,0,0,,休士頓，錢鼠已就位核彈預備
Dialogue: 0,0:56:08.15,0:56:10.90,ENG,,0,0,0,,We lost Partenza to explosive out-gassing,
Dialogue: 0,0:56:08.28,0:56:11.21,CHT,,0,0,0,,帕廷薩遭噴射流噴走
Dialogue: 0,0:56:12.11,0:56:13.99,ENG,,0,0,0,,and Monash is injured.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:12.32,0:56:14.15,CHT,,0,0,0,,蒙納許受傷
Dialogue: 0,0:56:19.12,0:56:21.75,ENG,,0,0,0,,- We have to go get Gus. - There's no time for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:19.19,0:56:20.68,CHT,,0,0,0,,回去接葛斯
Dialogue: 0,0:56:20.79,0:56:23.96,CHT,,0,0,0,,沒時間了，貨艙加壓
Dialogue: 0,0:56:21.83,0:56:25.38,ENG,,0,0,0,,- Re-pressurize the cargo bay. - He's going to die out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:24.13,0:56:26.60,CHT,,0,0,0,,他會死，我可以找到他
Dialogue: 0,0:56:25.46,0:56:26.71,ENG,,0,0,0,,We can still find him. He has a beacon.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:26.70,0:56:30.40,CHT,,0,0,0,,沒時間爭執，坐下、安靜！
Dialogue: 0,0:56:26.80,0:56:30.21,ENG,,0,0,0,,I don't have time to argue with you. Just sit down, be quiet.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:30.30,0:56:32.76,ENG,,0,0,0,,- Turn on the fucking locator! - We used most of our propellant
Dialogue: 0,0:56:30.50,0:56:31.73,CHT,,0,0,0,,我們能找到他！
Dialogue: 0,0:56:31.84,0:56:34.00,CHT,,0,0,0,,我們已用完剩餘燃料
Dialogue: 0,0:56:32.84,0:56:34.80,ENG,,0,0,0,,- to get us out of the coma. - We can't just leave him.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:34.11,0:56:35.73,CHT,,0,0,0,,不能把他丟在那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:56:34.89,0:56:37.22,ENG,,0,0,0,,- We have to go back! - If we go back for Gus, we all die.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:35.84,0:56:37.21,CHT,,0,0,0,,回去大家都死
Dialogue: 0,0:56:37.31,0:56:39.30,CHT,,0,0,0,,不能把他丟在太空中
Dialogue: 0,0:56:37.31,0:56:39.72,ENG,,0,0,0,,We can't just leave him in space!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:40.31,0:56:42.11,CHT,,0,0,0,,坐下！麥克，坐下
Dialogue: 0,0:56:40.43,0:56:43.48,ENG,,0,0,0,,Sit down, Mick. Sit down. it's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:42.91,0:56:44.44,CHT,,0,0,0,,沒事了
Dialogue: 0,0:56:55.78,0:56:59.20,ENG,,0,0,0,,The Messiah has safely lifted off the comet,
Dialogue: 0,0:56:55.83,0:56:59.23,CHT,,0,0,0,,彌賽亞號安全離開彗星
Dialogue: 0,0:56:59.29,0:57:01.91,ENG,,0,0,0,,but, sadly, Gus Partenza has been lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:59.33,0:57:02.30,CHT,,0,0,0,,不幸的，帕廷薩失蹤了
Dialogue: 0,0:57:02.70,0:57:06.30,CHT,,0,0,0,,帕廷薩生於賓州哈利斯堡
Dialogue: 0,0:57:02.75,0:57:06.21,ENG,,0,0,0,,Gus Partenza, a native of Harrisburg, Pennsylvania,
Dialogue: 0,0:57:06.29,0:57:09.13,ENG,,0,0,0,,and graduate of Carnegie Mellon University,
Dialogue: 0,0:57:06.41,0:57:09.31,CHT,,0,0,0,,畢業於卡內基米勒大學
Dialogue: 0,0:57:09.34,0:57:11.09,ENG,,0,0,0,,joined the NASA space program
Dialogue: 0,0:57:09.41,0:57:12.57,CHT,,0,0,0,,完成醫事訓練後
Dialogue: 0,0:57:11.17,0:57:15.18,ENG,,0,0,0,,shortly after completing his medical training at Duke University.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:12.68,0:57:15.84,CHT,,0,0,0,,加入太空任務
Dialogue: 0,0:57:16.22,0:57:19.43,ENG,,0,0,0,,Dr. Partenza was selected specifically for this mission
Dialogue: 0,0:57:16.25,0:57:19.45,CHT,,0,0,0,,帕廷薩被選任除了醫學專長外
Dialogue: 0,0:57:19.52,0:57:23.94,ENG,,0,0,0,,not only for his medical expertise, but also for his dedication
Dialogue: 0,0:57:19.55,0:57:26.86,CHT,,0,0,0,,對先進太空科技多所專研
Dialogue: 0,0:57:24.02,0:57:26.65,ENG,,0,0,0,,to the advancement of space technology.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:29.98,0:57:31.11,ENG,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:40.95,0:57:44.79,ENG,,0,0,0,,With the loss of Dr. Gus Partenza and with Oren Monash injured,
Dialogue: 0,0:57:41.08,0:57:44.84,CHT,,0,0,0,,由於帕廷薩失蹤蒙納許受傷
Dialogue: 0,0:57:44.87,0:57:48.42,ENG,,0,0,0,,Captain Spurgeon Tanner is now in charge of the mission.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:44.95,0:57:48.58,CHT,,0,0,0,,任務由譚納上尉指揮
Dialogue: 0,0:57:48.67,0:57:52.46,ENG,,0,0,0,,The Messiah has successfully docked with the Orion-powered boosters
Dialogue: 0,0:57:48.68,0:57:52.41,CHT,,0,0,0,,彌賽亞靠獵戶座成功降落彗星
Dialogue: 0,0:57:52.52,0:57:54.61,CHT,,0,0,0,,目前準備引爆…
Dialogue: 0,0:57:52.55,0:57:56.72,ENG,,0,0,0,,and is now prepared to detonate the bombs planted on Wolf-Biederman.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:54.72,0:57:56.88,CHT,,0,0,0,,埋在彗星上的核彈
Dialogue: 0,0:57:57.09,0:58:00.51,ENG,,0,0,0,,The Messiah's exterior-mounted camera will show us the detonation
Dialogue: 0,0:57:57.23,0:58:00.75,CHT,,0,0,0,,彌賽亞艙外攝影機將拍錄過程
Dialogue: 0,0:58:00.60,0:58:04.68,ENG,,0,0,0,,but not before being temporarily blocked out by the nuclear blast.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:00.86,0:58:04.86,CHT,,0,0,0,,但收訊會暫遭核爆波影響
Dialogue: 0,0:58:04.85,0:58:08.27,ENG,,0,0,0,,Once again, let me remind you, there is a 20-second delay,
Dialogue: 0,0:58:04.97,0:58:08.33,CHT,,0,0,0,,畫面較實際時間延遲20秒
Dialogue: 0,0:58:08.36,0:58:10.94,ENG,,0,0,0,,so when the picture comes back to us,
Dialogue: 0,0:58:08.44,0:58:10.67,CHT,,0,0,0,,接收到畫面時
Dialogue: 0,0:58:11.11,0:58:14.20,CHT,,0,0,0,,彗星應已偏離
Dialogue: 0,0:58:11.11,0:58:14.24,ENG,,0,0,0,,the comet should already have been knocked off its present course.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:23.66,0:58:26.21,ENG,,0,0,0,,Prepare to remove safeties and fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:23.75,0:58:26.12,CHT,,0,0,0,,解除引爆保護裝置
Dialogue: 0,0:58:29.54,0:58:31.17,ENG,,0,0,0,,Safeties removed.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:29.66,0:58:31.52,CHT,,0,0,0,,已解除
Dialogue: 0,0:58:39.17,0:58:40.23,CHT,,0,0,0,,準備引爆
Dialogue: 0,0:58:39.30,0:58:40.80,ENG,,0,0,0,,Weapons armed.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:47.18,0:58:49.44,CHT,,0,0,0,,“接受指令”
Dialogue: 0,0:58:49.55,0:58:51.04,CHT,,0,0,0,,“最後倒數”  “引爆或取消”
Dialogue: 0,0:58:51.68,0:58:53.74,CHT,,0,0,0,,3、2、1
Dialogue: 0,0:58:51.73,0:58:53.44,ENG,,0,0,0,,Three, two, one.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:53.78,0:58:54.82,ENG,,0,0,0,,Now.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:53.85,0:58:54.98,CHT,,0,0,0,,引爆
Dialogue: 0,0:59:00.59,0:59:03.65,CHT,,0,0,0,,我們在等待畫面恢復
Dialogue: 0,0:59:00.70,0:59:04.16,ENG,,0,0,0,,So now we're just waiting for the picture to come back.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:15.84,0:59:17.64,CHT,,0,0,0,,第6區失壓
Dialogue: 0,0:59:15.84,0:59:17.88,ENG,,0,0,0,,Decompression in area six.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:28.22,0:59:30.28,CHT,,0,0,0,,我去關艙門
Dialogue: 0,0:59:28.31,0:59:30.31,ENG,,0,0,0,,Mick, I'll get the halon.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:52.75,0:59:54.77,CHT,,0,0,0,,是，我在聽
Dialogue: 0,0:59:52.79,0:59:54.54,ENG,,0,0,0,,Yes. I'm still here.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:19.86,1:00:23.20,ENG,,0,0,0,,...even larger. We've lost contact with the Messiah.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:33.50,1:00:35.50,ENG,,0,0,0,,We're live in 10 seconds.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:33.62,1:00:35.24,CHT,,0,0,0,,10秒後實況轉播
Dialogue: 0,1:00:36.46,1:00:38.13,ENG,,0,0,0,,Cue the President.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:36.59,1:00:37.78,CHT,,0,0,0,,倒數計時
Dialogue: 0,1:00:38.30,1:00:41.84,ENG,,0,0,0,,Mr. President, five, four, three...
Dialogue: 0,1:00:38.49,1:00:42.86,CHT,,0,0,0,,總統先生，5、4、3…
Dialogue: 0,1:00:46.36,1:00:47.73,CHT,,0,0,0,,各位美國公民
Dialogue: 0,1:00:46.39,1:00:47.93,ENG,,0,0,0,,Hello, America.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:48.64,1:00:52.89,ENG,,0,0,0,,It is my unhappy duty to report to you that the Messiah has failed.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:48.67,1:00:53.33,CHT,,0,0,0,,不幸告知彌賽亞任務失敗
Dialogue: 0,1:00:53.27,1:00:55.65,ENG,,0,0,0,,This computer-enhanced radar image from Houston
Dialogue: 0,1:00:53.44,1:00:57.63,CHT,,0,0,0,,電腦雷達畫面顯示引爆成功
Dialogue: 0,1:00:55.73,1:01:00.44,ENG,,0,0,0,,shows how the detonation succeeded, however, did not destroy the comet.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:58.51,1:01:00.87,CHT,,0,0,0,,但未能摧毀彗星
Dialogue: 0,1:01:00.90,1:01:03.99,ENG,,0,0,0,,There are now two pieces, one 6 miles wide,
Dialogue: 0,1:01:01.01,1:01:02.50,CHT,,0,0,0,,彗星一分為二
Dialogue: 0,1:01:02.61,1:01:06.45,CHT,,0,0,0,,大的6英里寬小的1.5英里寬
Dialogue: 0,1:01:04.28,1:01:06.37,ENG,,0,0,0,,the other a mile and a half.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:06.45,1:01:09.16,ENG,,0,0,0,,Both are still on a path towards Earth.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:06.55,1:01:08.64,CHT,,0,0,0,,仍直衝地球而來
Dialogue: 0,1:01:10.04,1:01:12.54,ENG,,0,0,0,,We've lost communication with the Messiah spacecraft,
Dialogue: 0,1:01:10.12,1:01:13.15,CHT,,0,0,0,,我們與彌賽亞號失去聯絡
Dialogue: 0,1:01:12.62,1:01:15.46,ENG,,0,0,0,,although we continue to track it visually.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:13.26,1:01:16.28,CHT,,0,0,0,,但顯示器上仍有蹤跡
Dialogue: 0,1:01:16.17,1:01:20.13,ENG,,0,0,0,,We don't know how many are alive. We don't know their condition.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:16.39,1:01:21.09,CHT,,0,0,0,,組員生死未知、情況未明
Dialogue: 0,1:01:21.97,1:01:24.88,ENG,,0,0,0,,Now we have to make some decisions together.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:22.07,1:01:25.09,CHT,,0,0,0,,我們現在必須做下決定
Dialogue: 0,1:01:25.43,1:01:31.31,ENG,,0,0,0,,What do we do? You have a choice. We have a choice right now.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:25.44,1:01:27.03,CHT,,0,0,0,,怎麼做？
Dialogue: 0,1:01:27.57,1:01:32.37,CHT,,0,0,0,,你能選擇，我們能選擇
Dialogue: 0,1:01:33.19,1:01:34.69,ENG,,0,0,0,,Ever since the comet was discovered,
Dialogue: 0,1:01:33.35,1:01:34.94,CHT,,0,0,0,,自從發現彗星後
Dialogue: 0,1:01:34.77,1:01:37.52,ENG,,0,0,0,,we've been hoping and working for the best,
Dialogue: 0,1:01:35.05,1:01:37.68,CHT,,0,0,0,,我們積極因應對策
Dialogue: 0,1:01:37.61,1:01:40.44,ENG,,0,0,0,,but we've also been planning for the worst.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:37.78,1:01:40.65,CHT,,0,0,0,,但也做了最壞打算
Dialogue: 0,1:01:40.69,1:01:42.94,ENG,,0,0,0,,Our strategy has been twofold.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:40.75,1:01:43.22,CHT,,0,0,0,,計劃分兩頭進行
Dialogue: 0,1:01:43.78,1:01:45.99,ENG,,0,0,0,,First, our Strategic Missile Command
Dialogue: 0,1:01:43.89,1:01:46.15,CHT,,0,0,0,,第一，核彈研發部…
Dialogue: 0,1:01:46.07,1:01:47.70,ENG,,0,0,0,,is preparing to coordinate with the Russians
Dialogue: 0,1:01:46.26,1:01:48.09,CHT,,0,0,0,,與俄國聯手
Dialogue: 0,1:01:47.78,1:01:51.49,ENG,,0,0,0,,a massive strike of Titan missiles to intercept the comets.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:48.19,1:01:51.49,CHT,,0,0,0,,發射洲際飛彈攔截彗星
Dialogue: 0,1:01:52.33,1:01:54.96,ENG,,0,0,0,,If we can deflect these comets enough,
Dialogue: 0,1:01:52.50,1:01:55.52,CHT,,0,0,0,,若能打偏彗星航向
Dialogue: 0,1:01:55.46,1:01:58.46,ENG,,0,0,0,,they will bounce harmlessly off our atmosphere
Dialogue: 0,1:01:55.63,1:01:59.40,CHT,,0,0,0,,彗星將掠過大氣層
Dialogue: 0,1:01:59.29,1:02:01.42,ENG,,0,0,0,,and head on out into space.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:59.51,1:02:02.20,CHT,,0,0,0,,進入外太空
Dialogue: 0,1:02:02.30,1:02:05.26,ENG,,0,0,0,,Unfortunately, the Titans cannot be launched
Dialogue: 0,1:02:02.41,1:02:05.00,CHT,,0,0,0,,但是洲際飛彈
Dialogue: 0,1:02:05.11,1:02:07.77,CHT,,0,0,0,,必須在近程發射
Dialogue: 0,1:02:05.34,1:02:07.59,ENG,,0,0,0,,until the comets are only a few hours away.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:07.68,1:02:11.39,ENG,,0,0,0,,And while we are confident the missile attack will succeed,
Dialogue: 0,1:02:07.88,1:02:11.84,CHT,,0,0,0,,在抱著必成的信心的同時
Dialogue: 0,1:02:11.77,1:02:14.31,ENG,,0,0,0,,it is only prudent that we now take cautionary steps
Dialogue: 0,1:02:11.95,1:02:14.04,CHT,,0,0,0,,我們必需設法保證
Dialogue: 0,1:02:14.15,1:02:17.18,CHT,,0,0,0,,生命將延續下去
Dialogue: 0,1:02:14.39,1:02:17.27,ENG,,0,0,0,,to ensure the continuation of our way of life,
Dialogue: 0,1:02:17.35,1:02:20.40,ENG,,0,0,0,,to guarantee that there will be enough of us left
Dialogue: 0,1:02:17.42,1:02:22.45,CHT,,0,0,0,,確保…足夠的人類能重建新世界
Dialogue: 0,1:02:20.48,1:02:22.32,ENG,,0,0,0,,to rebuild a new world
Dialogue: 0,1:02:22.48,1:02:26.11,ENG,,0,0,0,,in the unlikely event that the comets do strike the Earth.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:22.56,1:02:26.12,CHT,,0,0,0,,雖然被彗星撞擊的機率很小
Dialogue: 0,1:02:26.66,1:02:29.99,ENG,,0,0,0,,So in the soft limestone of Missouri,
Dialogue: 0,1:02:26.73,1:02:30.60,CHT,,0,0,0,,因此我們在密蘇里州的石灰巖區
Dialogue: 0,1:02:30.53,1:02:33.54,ENG,,0,0,0,,we've been preparing a network of immense caves.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:30.70,1:02:35.51,CHT,,0,0,0,,挖鑿了很大的洞穴現在已將近完工
Dialogue: 0,1:02:33.62,1:02:35.37,ENG,,0,0,0,,And they're almost finished.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:35.46,1:02:38.17,ENG,,0,0,0,,And we can put a million people in them.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:35.61,1:02:38.27,CHT,,0,0,0,,能容納百萬人
Dialogue: 0,1:02:38.33,1:02:42.55,ENG,,0,0,0,,And that million people can survive there, underground, for two years,
Dialogue: 0,1:02:38.48,1:02:42.61,CHT,,0,0,0,,人們在洞穴中能存活2年
Dialogue: 0,1:02:42.63,1:02:45.67,ENG,,0,0,0,,until the air clears and the dust settles.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:42.72,1:02:46.81,CHT,,0,0,0,,等待空氣濾清、塵埃落定
Dialogue: 0,1:02:46.80,1:02:50.80,ENG,,0,0,0,,Now, the cave is more than a dormitory. It is our new Noah's Ark.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:46.92,1:02:49.32,CHT,,0,0,0,,洞穴不只是居所
Dialogue: 0,1:02:49.42,1:02:51.52,CHT,,0,0,0,,還是現代的諾亞方舟
Dialogue: 0,1:02:51.47,1:02:56.43,ENG,,0,0,0,,We're storing seeds and seedlings, plants, animals. Enough to start over.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:51.63,1:02:55.32,CHT,,0,0,0,,儲存種子、植物、動物
Dialogue: 0,1:02:55.43,1:02:57.36,CHT,,0,0,0,,讓生命延續
Dialogue: 0,1:02:57.44,1:03:01.98,ENG,,0,0,0,,On August 10th, a computer will randomly select 800,000 Americans
Dialogue: 0,1:02:57.60,1:02:59.09,CHT,,0,0,0,,在8月10日…
Dialogue: 0,1:02:59.20,1:03:02.47,CHT,,0,0,0,,電腦將抽80萬人
Dialogue: 0,1:03:02.57,1:03:04.80,CHT,,0,0,0,,會同預先選出的科學家
Dialogue: 0,1:03:02.57,1:03:05.44,ENG,,0,0,0,,to join the 200,000 scientists, doctors,
Dialogue: 0,1:03:04.91,1:03:09.78,CHT,,0,0,0,,醫生、工程師、教師、軍人藝術家，共20萬人
Dialogue: 0,1:03:05.53,1:03:09.78,ENG,,0,0,0,,engineers, teachers, soldiers and artists who have already been chosen.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:09.87,1:03:13.28,ENG,,0,0,0,,Other countries are preparing similar caves along whatever lines they feel
Dialogue: 0,1:03:09.98,1:03:12.88,CHT,,0,0,0,,別國也視當地情況
Dialogue: 0,1:03:12.98,1:03:16.32,CHT,,0,0,0,,設置避難所
Dialogue: 0,1:03:13.37,1:03:16.08,ENG,,0,0,0,,are best to preserve their way of life.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:16.37,1:03:17.83,ENG,,0,0,0,,This is ours.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:16.52,1:03:17.88,CHT,,0,0,0,,這是我們的方式
Dialogue: 0,1:03:18.67,1:03:22.13,ENG,,0,0,0,,Beginning tonight and continuing until the crisis passes,
Dialogue: 0,1:03:18.79,1:03:22.22,CHT,,0,0,0,,從今晚到危機解除前
Dialogue: 0,1:03:22.21,1:03:24.84,ENG,,0,0,0,,I am declaring a state of martial law.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:22.32,1:03:25.26,CHT,,0,0,0,,我發佈戒嚴令
Dialogue: 0,1:03:25.42,1:03:27.26,ENG,,0,0,0,,The armed forces and the National Guard
Dialogue: 0,1:03:25.59,1:03:29.55,CHT,,0,0,0,,軍隊與預備隊將與警方配合
Dialogue: 0,1:03:27.34,1:03:30.05,ENG,,0,0,0,,are working with local law enforcement.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:30.18,1:03:32.68,ENG,,0,0,0,,A national curfew begins at midnight tonight.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:30.23,1:03:32.96,CHT,,0,0,0,,今晚午夜全面戒嚴
Dialogue: 0,1:03:32.76,1:03:35.72,ENG,,0,0,0,,Now, wherever you are, go home.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:33.07,1:03:36.33,CHT,,0,0,0,,不論各位現在身在何處請盡快回家
Dialogue: 0,1:03:36.73,1:03:39.06,ENG,,0,0,0,,Stay off the roads after sunset.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:36.84,1:03:39.21,CHT,,0,0,0,,天黑後別逗留在外
Dialogue: 0,1:03:39.48,1:03:43.27,ENG,,0,0,0,,Crimes against persons or property will be dealt with swiftly
Dialogue: 0,1:03:39.64,1:03:43.60,CHT,,0,0,0,,侵害人身或財產罪將從速…
Dialogue: 0,1:03:43.77,1:03:45.19,ENG,,0,0,0,,and harshly.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:43.85,1:03:45.44,CHT,,0,0,0,,從重量刑
Dialogue: 0,1:03:45.94,1:03:48.40,ENG,,0,0,0,,News stations around the nation are being faxed copies
Dialogue: 0,1:03:45.98,1:03:49.78,CHT,,0,0,0,,我們將提供抽簽規則給各媒體
Dialogue: 0,1:03:48.49,1:03:50.32,ENG,,0,0,0,,of the lottery procedure as we speak,
Dialogue: 0,1:03:49.89,1:03:54.02,CHT,,0,0,0,,媒體稍候將做詳細播報
Dialogue: 0,1:03:50.41,1:03:54.41,ENG,,0,0,0,,and they'll be broadcasting the details to you in a few moments.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:01.92,1:04:03.21,ENG,,0,0,0,,I wish...
Dialogue: 0,1:04:02.03,1:04:03.36,CHT,,0,0,0,,我希望…
Dialogue: 0,1:04:06.09,1:04:07.13,ENG,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:06.17,1:04:10.97,CHT,,0,0,0,,不，不是希望
Dialogue: 0,1:04:09.17,1:04:10.84,ENG,,0,0,0,,Wishing is wrong.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:11.59,1:04:15.01,ENG,,0,0,0,,It's the wrong word right now. That's not what I mean.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:11.68,1:04:15.01,CHT,,0,0,0,,不該這麼說，不是這意思
Dialogue: 0,1:04:16.77,1:04:18.39,ENG,,0,0,0,,What I mean is...
Dialogue: 0,1:04:16.78,1:04:18.81,CHT,,0,0,0,,我的意思是…
Dialogue: 0,1:04:20.32,1:04:22.55,CHT,,0,0,0,,我相信神
Dialogue: 0,1:04:20.39,1:04:22.02,ENG,,0,0,0,,I believe in God.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:23.27,1:04:24.44,ENG,,0,0,0,,Relax.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:23.39,1:04:24.62,CHT,,0,0,0,,放輕鬆
Dialogue: 0,1:04:24.98,1:04:29.36,ENG,,0,0,0,,I know a lot of you don't, but I still want to offer a prayer
Dialogue: 0,1:04:25.12,1:04:27.22,CHT,,0,0,0,,很多人不信
Dialogue: 0,1:04:27.76,1:04:29.59,CHT,,0,0,0,,但我仍要祈禱
Dialogue: 0,1:04:30.74,1:04:32.36,ENG,,0,0,0,,for our survival,
Dialogue: 0,1:04:30.76,1:04:32.96,CHT,,0,0,0,,祈求救贖
Dialogue: 0,1:04:33.95,1:04:35.45,ENG,,0,0,0,,mine included.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:34.10,1:04:36.00,CHT,,0,0,0,,包括我的性命
Dialogue: 0,1:04:36.45,1:04:38.91,ENG,,0,0,0,,Because I believe that God,
Dialogue: 0,1:04:36.50,1:04:37.63,CHT,,0,0,0,,因為我相信…
Dialogue: 0,1:04:37.97,1:04:39.10,CHT,,0,0,0,,神
Dialogue: 0,1:04:39.58,1:04:41.29,ENG,,0,0,0,,whomever you hold that to be,
Dialogue: 0,1:04:39.74,1:04:41.43,CHT,,0,0,0,,不論信的是什麼神
Dialogue: 0,1:04:41.87,1:04:43.54,ENG,,0,0,0,,hears all prayers,
Dialogue: 0,1:04:42.07,1:04:44.64,CHT,,0,0,0,,會傾聽祈禱
Dialogue: 0,1:04:44.71,1:04:47.21,ENG,,0,0,0,,even if sometimes the answer is no.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:44.84,1:04:47.81,CHT,,0,0,0,,雖然有時拒絕所求
Dialogue: 0,1:04:48.84,1:04:50.88,ENG,,0,0,0,,So may the Lord bless you.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:49.02,1:04:51.35,CHT,,0,0,0,,願神祝福大家
Dialogue: 0,1:04:51.72,1:04:53.59,ENG,,0,0,0,,May the Lord keep you.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:51.85,1:04:53.91,CHT,,0,0,0,,保佑大家
Dialogue: 0,1:04:54.30,1:04:57.64,ENG,,0,0,0,,May the Lord lift up his divine countenance upon you
Dialogue: 0,1:04:54.49,1:04:59.48,CHT,,0,0,0,,願神的恩典降臨大家
Dialogue: 0,1:04:59.52,1:05:01.27,ENG,,0,0,0,,and give you peace.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:59.56,1:05:01.49,CHT,,0,0,0,,保佑大家平安
Dialogue: 0,1:05:06.15,1:05:10.53,ENG,,0,0,0,,And in five, four, three, two...
Dialogue: 0,1:05:06.33,1:05:11.00,CHT,,0,0,0,,5、4、3、2…
Dialogue: 0,1:05:19.45,1:05:22.62,ENG,,0,0,0,,We now have the details for the national lottery.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:19.68,1:05:23.55,CHT,,0,0,0,,現在公佈抽簽規則
Dialogue: 0,1:05:24.95,1:05:27.11,CHT,,0,0,0,,被預先選出者
Dialogue: 0,1:05:25.00,1:05:26.92,ENG,,0,0,0,,Those of you who have been preselected
Dialogue: 0,1:05:27.00,1:05:29.92,ENG,,0,0,0,,will be notified within the next few minutes.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:27.22,1:05:30.38,CHT,,0,0,0,,稍候將接到通知
Dialogue: 0,1:05:30.34,1:05:35.30,ENG,,0,0,0,,For the rest, on the night of August 10th, those whose Social Security numbers
Dialogue: 0,1:05:30.49,1:05:31.46,CHT,,0,0,0,,其他人
Dialogue: 0,1:05:31.56,1:05:33.25,CHT,,0,0,0,,將於8月10日晚上
Dialogue: 0,1:05:33.33,1:05:39.43,CHT,,0,0,0,,憑社會福利證號隨意抽出者也將被通知
Dialogue: 0,1:05:35.39,1:05:39.31,ENG,,0,0,0,,have been randomly selected by computer will be notified.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:39.68,1:05:41.43,ENG,,0,0,0,,While some Americans
Dialogue: 0,1:05:39.87,1:05:42.50,CHT,,0,0,0,,除了一些…
Dialogue: 0,1:05:42.02,1:05:45.60,ENG,,0,0,0,,over 50 years of age have been preselected for the Ark
Dialogue: 0,1:05:42.60,1:05:47.06,CHT,,0,0,0,,年齡超過50被預選者
Dialogue: 0,1:05:45.69,1:05:49.02,ENG,,0,0,0,,due to their expertise in a necessary field of study,
Dialogue: 0,1:05:47.18,1:05:50.77,CHT,,0,0,0,,因為他們能貢獻專業知識
Dialogue: 0,1:05:49.86,1:05:53.03,ENG,,0,0,0,,no men and women over 50 in the general population
Dialogue: 0,1:05:50.88,1:05:53.11,CHT,,0,0,0,,其他超過50歲者
Dialogue: 0,1:05:53.11,1:05:55.45,ENG,,0,0,0,,will be included in the lottery.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:53.21,1:05:56.21,CHT,,0,0,0,,不得抽簽
Dialogue: 0,1:06:03.49,1:06:08.69,CHT,,0,0,0,,被抽中者
Dialogue: 0,1:06:03.50,1:06:04.66,ENG,,0,0,0,,The...
Dialogue: 0,1:06:05.21,1:06:09.17,ENG,,0,0,0,,The... The evacuation of those who have been selected for the Ark
Dialogue: 0,1:06:08.80,1:06:12.63,CHT,,0,0,0,,將於2天內進入方舟
Dialogue: 0,1:06:09.25,1:06:13.01,ENG,,0,0,0,,will take no longer than two days, beginning on August 12th.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:13.21,1:06:17.43,ENG,,0,0,0,,During this two-day period, no unofficial travel will be permitted.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:13.24,1:06:15.20,CHT,,0,0,0,,在這兩天中
Dialogue: 0,1:06:15.30,1:06:17.70,CHT,,0,0,0,,不准私人旅行
Dialogue: 0,1:06:17.64,1:06:20.10,ENG,,0,0,0,,Those selected will be taken by bus and train
Dialogue: 0,1:06:17.81,1:06:20.28,CHT,,0,0,0,,選中者將搭巴士、火車
Dialogue: 0,1:06:20.18,1:06:23.39,ENG,,0,0,0,,to the underground Ark site by military personnel.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:20.38,1:06:23.90,CHT,,0,0,0,,由軍隊護送到方舟
Dialogue: 0,1:06:24.23,1:06:26.27,ENG,,0,0,0,,Civil defense teams have been formed
Dialogue: 0,1:06:24.28,1:06:30.62,CHT,,0,0,0,,凡人口超過五千的城鎮將設立民兵護衛隊
Dialogue: 0,1:06:26.35,1:06:29.61,ENG,,0,0,0,,in every town with a population over 5,000.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:30.52,1:06:33.65,ENG,,0,0,0,,They will distribute supplies and organize group shelters
Dialogue: 0,1:06:30.72,1:06:34.09,CHT,,0,0,0,,並在地下停車場或適當地點
Dialogue: 0,1:06:33.74,1:06:37.57,ENG,,0,0,0,,in underground parking facilities and other appropriate sites.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:34.19,1:06:37.65,CHT,,0,0,0,,提供民眾補給與組織避難所
Dialogue: 0,1:06:37.91,1:06:42.45,ENG,,0,0,0,,Construction plans, equipment lists and locations
Dialogue: 0,1:06:38.06,1:06:40.22,CHT,,0,0,0,,建物構造圖…
Dialogue: 0,1:06:40.33,1:06:41.63,CHT,,0,0,0,,提供器材…
Dialogue: 0,1:06:41.73,1:06:44.93,CHT,,0,0,0,,保障供應…
Dialogue: 0,1:06:42.54,1:06:45.45,ENG,,0,0,0,,- for securing the necessary provisions... - Hello?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:45.54,1:06:47.37,ENG,,0,0,0,,- ...along with information... - Yes, this is Ellen Biederman.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:46.27,1:06:48.70,CHT,,0,0,0,,是，我是艾琳畢德曼
Dialogue: 0,1:06:47.46,1:06:51.34,ENG,,0,0,0,,...on how to grow your own food underground and how to purify water
Dialogue: 0,1:06:51.42,1:06:54.05,ENG,,0,0,0,,are now available on the internet at...
Dialogue: 0,1:06:54.13,1:06:59.97,ENG,,0,0,0,,- We've been preselected. - ...www.fcda.gov.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:54.21,1:06:56.37,CHT,,0,0,0,,我們被預選了
Dialogue: 0,1:07:00.97,1:07:03.43,ENG,,0,0,0,,Chuck, Chuck. Where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:01.15,1:07:03.78,CHT,,0,0,0,,查克…你去哪裡？
Dialogue: 0,1:07:03.68,1:07:07.14,ENG,,0,0,0,,- Our phone. They could be calling. - ...beginning on August 9th.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:03.89,1:07:05.22,CHT,,0,0,0,,回去等電話
Dialogue: 0,1:07:07.23,1:07:12.11,ENG,,0,0,0,,The only phones that ring will be those of the people selected.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:07.36,1:07:09.62,CHT,,0,0,0,,被選中者
Dialogue: 0,1:07:10.10,1:07:12.59,CHT,,0,0,0,,將以電話通知
Dialogue: 0,1:07:13.98,1:07:15.32,ENG,,0,0,0,,That's it.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:14.13,1:07:15.07,CHT,,0,0,0,,就是這樣
Dialogue: 0,1:07:16.32,1:07:18.11,ENG,,0,0,0,,That's all there is.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:16.34,1:07:18.03,CHT,,0,0,0,,以上便是所有規則內容
Dialogue: 0,1:07:26.12,1:07:28.79,ENG,,0,0,0,,The interior camera circuitry is shot.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:26.28,1:07:29.21,CHT,,0,0,0,,攝影機內部回路損毀
Dialogue: 0,1:07:29.04,1:07:30.79,ENG,,0,0,0,,So, Andy, can we get back into the cargo bay
Dialogue: 0,1:07:29.31,1:07:32.84,CHT,,0,0,0,,能進貨艙修改回路裝置？
Dialogue: 0,1:07:30.88,1:07:32.79,ENG,,0,0,0,,to reroute the video functions?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:32.88,1:07:35.96,ENG,,0,0,0,,Starboard cargo porthole's blown. We could go in with the EVAs,
Dialogue: 0,1:07:32.95,1:07:34.82,CHT,,0,0,0,,貨艙窗有破洞
Dialogue: 0,1:07:34.99,1:07:38.55,CHT,,0,0,0,,可穿太空衣進入但氧氣不夠
Dialogue: 0,1:07:36.05,1:07:38.30,ENG,,0,0,0,,but there's not much left in the life-support packs.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:38.38,1:07:42.64,ENG,,0,0,0,,We should be able to raise Houston on the low band once we get closer.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:38.66,1:07:42.53,CHT,,0,0,0,,接近地球時可用低頻聯絡基地
Dialogue: 0,1:07:43.26,1:07:44.72,ENG,,0,0,0,,And the Orion is still functioning?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:43.36,1:07:44.89,CHT,,0,0,0,,獵戶座仍可運作？
Dialogue: 0,1:07:44.81,1:07:48.39,ENG,,0,0,0,,System check was okay, but I don't know about the radiation shielding.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:45.00,1:07:48.53,CHT,,0,0,0,,正常，但輻射護罩不穩
Dialogue: 0,1:07:48.48,1:07:51.40,ENG,,0,0,0,,So if we fire it up, we beat the comet back to Earth,
Dialogue: 0,1:07:48.64,1:07:51.54,CHT,,0,0,0,,若啟動引擎我們可以比彗星早到地球
Dialogue: 0,1:07:51.48,1:07:54.48,ENG,,0,0,0,,but we may end up glowing in the dark.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:51.64,1:07:55.94,CHT,,0,0,0,,但是…我們可能吸收過多輻射
Dialogue: 0,1:07:58.07,1:07:59.78,ENG,,0,0,0,,Okay. So...
Dialogue: 0,1:07:58.15,1:08:00.20,CHT,,0,0,0,,好，那麼…
Dialogue: 0,1:08:02.41,1:08:03.66,ENG,,0,0,0,,Anybody?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:02.52,1:08:04.38,CHT,,0,0,0,,有異議？
Dialogue: 0,1:08:12.79,1:08:14.29,ENG,,0,0,0,,Let's go home.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:12.93,1:08:14.45,CHT,,0,0,0,,回家吧！
Dialogue: 0,1:08:20.68,1:08:21.80,ENG,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:31.81,1:08:35.15,ENG,,0,0,0,,I have to say, it's liberating knowing that I'm not going to be called.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:32.01,1:08:36.71,CHT,,0,0,0,,“距離撞擊時間：4週零2天”沒被選中真是解脫
Dialogue: 0,1:08:36.15,1:08:40.11,ENG,,0,0,0,,I don't think I've ever been happier. I've even stopped smoking.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:36.82,1:08:41.02,CHT,,0,0,0,,我從沒這麼快樂過我戒煙了
Dialogue: 0,1:08:41.28,1:08:44.87,ENG,,0,0,0,,What are you gonna do with all that extra money you save?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:41.36,1:08:44.99,CHT,,0,0,0,,省下的煙錢要做什麼？
Dialogue: 0,1:08:47.40,1:08:52.06,CHT,,0,0,0,,博物館將所有館藏運往方舟
Dialogue: 0,1:08:47.45,1:08:49.91,ENG,,0,0,0,,Do you know the National Gallery is saving all of the art?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:50.00,1:08:52.29,ENG,,0,0,0,,They're shipping it to the caves.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:52.37,1:08:56.04,ENG,,0,0,0,,I've given them my beautiful 18th-century desk from New England
Dialogue: 0,1:08:52.40,1:08:56.34,CHT,,0,0,0,,我捐出18世紀英國書桌
Dialogue: 0,1:08:56.13,1:08:58.25,ENG,,0,0,0,,and all the Sheraton silver.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:56.44,1:08:58.41,CHT,,0,0,0,,和名牌銀器
Dialogue: 0,1:08:58.34,1:09:01.22,ENG,,0,0,0,,I really feel like I'd protected something
Dialogue: 0,1:08:58.51,1:09:04.07,CHT,,0,0,0,,我捐出這些…深覺與有榮焉
Dialogue: 0,1:09:01.80,1:09:03.47,ENG,,0,0,0,,when I gave them.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:05.80,1:09:09.06,ENG,,0,0,0,,You should see my apartment. There's nothing there.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:05.88,1:09:07.87,CHT,,0,0,0,,該看看我的住處
Dialogue: 0,1:09:07.99,1:09:11.98,CHT,,0,0,0,,搬空了，像日式房捨
Dialogue: 0,1:09:09.35,1:09:11.39,ENG,,0,0,0,,It's practically Japanese.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:14.56,1:09:16.90,ENG,,0,0,0,,Seems kind of unfair that I got picked.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:14.63,1:09:17.15,CHT,,0,0,0,,我被選中很不公平
Dialogue: 0,1:09:16.98,1:09:19.78,ENG,,0,0,0,,You know, I'm not a doctor or a scientist.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:17.26,1:09:20.13,CHT,,0,0,0,,我不是醫生或科學家
Dialogue: 0,1:09:21.82,1:09:24.78,ENG,,0,0,0,,People need continuity. Everyone knows you,
Dialogue: 0,1:09:21.93,1:09:23.80,CHT,,0,0,0,,人們需要資訊
Dialogue: 0,1:09:23.90,1:09:25.87,CHT,,0,0,0,,大家認識你
Dialogue: 0,1:09:25.87,1:09:27.57,ENG,,0,0,0,,and they trust you.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:25.97,1:09:27.56,CHT,,0,0,0,,信任你
Dialogue: 0,1:09:28.62,1:09:31.12,ENG,,0,0,0,,But I can't help you.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:28.71,1:09:32.01,CHT,,0,0,0,,但我幫不了你
Dialogue: 0,1:09:32.33,1:09:34.12,ENG,,0,0,0,,Don't worry about me.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:32.41,1:09:34.04,CHT,,0,0,0,,別替我擔心
Dialogue: 0,1:09:34.62,1:09:38.42,ENG,,0,0,0,,I'm going to be happy as long as I know you're going to live.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:34.71,1:09:37.94,CHT,,0,0,0,,知道你能活著我就開心了
Dialogue: 0,1:09:58.06,1:09:59.15,ENG,,0,0,0,,Mr. Hotchner?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:58.10,1:09:59.19,CHT,,0,0,0,,哈奇納先生
Dialogue: 0,1:09:59.23,1:10:02.23,ENG,,0,0,0,,Who did I think I was gonna be when I bought that bike?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:59.30,1:10:02.20,CHT,,0,0,0,,當初買摩托車幹嘛？
Dialogue: 0,1:10:02.32,1:10:05.15,ENG,,0,0,0,,Well, every kid on the block wants one now.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:02.37,1:10:04.93,CHT,,0,0,0,,孩子們都想要
Dialogue: 0,1:10:05.24,1:10:07.28,ENG,,0,0,0,,Every parent on the block hates you for it.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:05.34,1:10:07.40,CHT,,0,0,0,,家長因此痛恨你
Dialogue: 0,1:10:07.37,1:10:09.66,ENG,,0,0,0,,Well, thank you, Leo. That's the best news I've had in years.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:07.51,1:10:09.77,CHT,,0,0,0,,謝謝，這是今年最好的消息
Dialogue: 0,1:10:09.74,1:10:10.70,ENG,,0,0,0,,Sir?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:09.84,1:10:10.83,CHT,,0,0,0,,哈奇納先生…
Dialogue: 0,1:10:10.79,1:10:12.66,ENG,,0,0,0,,Can you give me a hand over here for a second?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:10.91,1:10:15.21,CHT,,0,0,0,,幫我個忙，好嗎？我想裝上鐵窗
Dialogue: 0,1:10:12.75,1:10:15.04,ENG,,0,0,0,,- Yes, sir. - I just wanna get these bars up.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:15.12,1:10:16.67,ENG,,0,0,0,,- Hello, Mrs. Hotchner. - Hi, Leo.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:15.32,1:10:16.65,CHT,,0,0,0,,哈太太，你好
Dialogue: 0,1:10:16.75,1:10:20.21,CHT,,0,0,0,,挖土機出租行老板…
Dialogue: 0,1:10:16.75,1:10:19.92,ENG,,0,0,0,,A mob attacked and killed a Miami rental yard operator
Dialogue: 0,1:10:20.00,1:10:24.05,ENG,,0,0,0,,who was charging $5,000 an hour for backhoe and tractor rentals.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:20.32,1:10:23.26,CHT,,0,0,0,,因收費過高，惹起民忿
Dialogue: 0,1:10:23.36,1:10:25.92,CHT,,0,0,0,,遭群毆而死，軍隊出動…盡是這些新聞
Dialogue: 0,1:10:24.13,1:10:27.84,ENG,,0,0,0,,Same old crap on the TV. I'm really sick of it, you know?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:26.29,1:10:28.42,CHT,,0,0,0,,阻止暴力蔓延煩死人了
Dialogue: 0,1:10:28.47,1:10:30.14,ENG,,0,0,0,,- Mrs. Hotchner? - Sarah's on the hill.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:28.53,1:10:29.50,CHT,,0,0,0,,哈太太
Dialogue: 0,1:10:29.60,1:10:31.16,CHT,,0,0,0,,莎拉在山上謝謝
Dialogue: 0,1:10:30.22,1:10:31.56,ENG,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:39.27,1:10:41.06,ENG,,0,0,0,,Where were you today?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:39.34,1:10:40.90,CHT,,0,0,0,,你去哪了？
Dialogue: 0,1:10:41.90,1:10:44.44,ENG,,0,0,0,,I've been looking all over for you.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:42.08,1:10:46.34,CHT,,0,0,0,,我到處找你，怎麼沒上學？
Dialogue: 0,1:10:44.61,1:10:48.24,ENG,,0,0,0,,- Why weren't you at school? - My dad said I didn't have to go.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:46.45,1:10:50.48,CHT,,0,0,0,,爸說不必去！沒必要
Dialogue: 0,1:10:48.32,1:10:50.32,ENG,,0,0,0,,He said there's no point.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:56.33,1:10:57.71,ENG,,0,0,0,,I talked to civil defense.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:56.66,1:10:58.39,CHT,,0,0,0,,我問過民兵護衛隊
Dialogue: 0,1:10:57.79,1:11:02.29,ENG,,0,0,0,,They said if you and I got married, we'd be family and I could get you in.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:58.49,1:11:01.79,CHT,,0,0,0,,我們結婚，你就能上方舟
Dialogue: 0,1:11:02.67,1:11:05.96,ENG,,0,0,0,,Well, what about my parents? They're not your family.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:02.77,1:11:05.89,CHT,,0,0,0,,我父母呢？他們不是你家人
Dialogue: 0,1:11:06.05,1:11:08.76,ENG,,0,0,0,,- I don't wanna go without my parents. - You don't have to.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:06.10,1:11:07.43,CHT,,0,0,0,,我不要丟下他們
Dialogue: 0,1:11:07.54,1:11:10.53,CHT,,0,0,0,,不會，我是里歐畢德曼
Dialogue: 0,1:11:08.84,1:11:12.68,ENG,,0,0,0,,I'm the famous Leo Biederman, and I haven't used my fame for anything.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:10.64,1:11:14.70,CHT,,0,0,0,,靠我的名氣，能為他們爭取
Dialogue: 0,1:11:12.76,1:11:15.60,ENG,,0,0,0,,But I got them to let your family go, too.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:20.52,1:11:21.61,ENG,,0,0,0,,You...
Dialogue: 0,1:11:20.55,1:11:24.15,CHT,,0,0,0,,這是你唯一存活的機會
Dialogue: 0,1:11:21.69,1:11:24.19,ENG,,0,0,0,,This is your only chance to survive.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:40.04,1:11:44.46,ENG,,0,0,0,,Across the country, looters continue to set fire to abandoned stores.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:40.14,1:11:44.84,CHT,,0,0,0,,不斷傳出搶奪、放火事件
Dialogue: 0,1:11:44.63,1:11:47.46,ENG,,0,0,0,,Fires have been left to burn, since many firefighters
Dialogue: 0,1:11:44.94,1:11:47.71,CHT,,0,0,0,,失火沒有消防員管
Dialogue: 0,1:11:47.55,1:11:50.34,ENG,,0,0,0,,have been called to help prepare shelters.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:47.81,1:11:50.44,CHT,,0,0,0,,因為消防員要幫手蓋庇護站
Dialogue: 0,1:11:50.68,1:11:52.84,ENG,,0,0,0,,Throughout Latin America's major cities,
Dialogue: 0,1:11:50.85,1:11:53.58,CHT,,0,0,0,,中南美洲各大城市的商業區…
Dialogue: 0,1:11:52.93,1:11:56.47,ENG,,0,0,0,,business districts have been abandoned to looting gangs.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:53.68,1:11:56.71,CHT,,0,0,0,,遭黑道占據
Dialogue: 0,1:12:03.73,1:12:07.23,ENG,,0,0,0,,Emergency airlifts have been ruled out as too dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:04.56,1:12:07.66,CHT,,0,0,0,,空運救援因危險暫停
Dialogue: 0,1:12:08.36,1:12:12.24,ENG,,0,0,0,,More street fighting in Moscow as food and fuel shortages continue...
Dialogue: 0,1:12:08.43,1:12:10.96,CHT,,0,0,0,,莫斯科食物短缺
Dialogue: 0,1:12:11.07,1:12:13.20,CHT,,0,0,0,,引發暴動
Dialogue: 0,1:12:25.21,1:12:30.09,ENG,,0,0,0,,"...believes all things, hopes all things, endures all things.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:25.28,1:12:27.31,CHT,,0,0,0,,愛包容一切
Dialogue: 0,1:12:27.42,1:12:31.41,CHT,,0,0,0,,相信、希望、忍耐
Dialogue: 0,1:12:32.18,1:12:34.89,ENG,,0,0,0,,"When I was a child, I spoke like a child,
Dialogue: 0,1:12:32.23,1:12:35.22,CHT,,0,0,0,,我小的時候，說話像小孩
Dialogue: 0,1:12:34.97,1:12:38.43,ENG,,0,0,0,,"I thought like a child, I reasoned like a child.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:35.33,1:12:39.09,CHT,,0,0,0,,想法像小孩，行為像小孩
Dialogue: 0,1:12:39.52,1:12:43.02,ENG,,0,0,0,,"When I became a man, I gave up childish ways.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:39.67,1:12:43.60,CHT,,0,0,0,,我長大後，放棄幼稚行為
Dialogue: 0,1:12:44.27,1:12:48.11,ENG,,0,0,0,,"For now we see in a mirror dimly, but then face to face.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:44.30,1:12:46.70,CHT,,0,0,0,,如今看鏡中的自己
Dialogue: 0,1:12:46.91,1:12:50.81,CHT,,0,0,0,,面對自己，漸漸了解
Dialogue: 0,1:12:48.99,1:12:53.49,ENG,,0,0,0,,"Now I know in part, then I shall understand fully,
Dialogue: 0,1:12:51.18,1:12:55.88,CHT,,0,0,0,,我早該面對真實的自己
Dialogue: 0,1:12:53.57,1:12:55.95,ENG,,0,0,0,,"even as I have been fully understood."
Dialogue: 0,1:13:06.75,1:13:10.21,ENG,,0,0,0,,Do you, Leo, take Sarah to be your wife,
Dialogue: 0,1:13:07.80,1:13:12.73,CHT,,0,0,0,,你願娶莎拉為妻
Dialogue: 0,1:13:10.76,1:13:13.72,ENG,,0,0,0,,to have and to hold from this day forward,
Dialogue: 0,1:13:12.83,1:13:14.60,CHT,,0,0,0,,互相容忍
Dialogue: 0,1:13:14.43,1:13:18.14,ENG,,0,0,0,,for better, for worse, for richer, for poorer,
Dialogue: 0,1:13:14.70,1:13:16.97,CHT,,0,0,0,,甘苦與共
Dialogue: 0,1:13:17.07,1:13:19.10,CHT,,0,0,0,,相愛相守
Dialogue: 0,1:13:18.85,1:13:20.77,ENG,,0,0,0,,to love and to cherish?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:19.21,1:13:22.11,CHT,,0,0,0,,至死不渝？
Dialogue: 0,1:13:29.32,1:13:31.99,ENG,,0,0,0,,I now pronounce you husband and wife.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:29.52,1:13:32.68,CHT,,0,0,0,,我宣告你們結為夫妻
Dialogue: 0,1:14:07.42,1:14:11.83,CHT,,0,0,0,,“距離撞擊時間：2週零3天”
Dialogue: 0,1:14:51.57,1:14:54.61,ENG,,0,0,0,,Here. Let me help you. I'll get it.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:51.70,1:14:53.40,CHT,,0,0,0,,我幫你
Dialogue: 0,1:14:53.94,1:14:55.13,CHT,,0,0,0,,讓我來
Dialogue: 0,1:14:57.95,1:14:59.87,ENG,,0,0,0,,Yeah. How you feeling?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:58.94,1:15:00.04,CHT,,0,0,0,,感覺如何？
Dialogue: 0,1:15:01.61,1:15:02.81,CHT,,0,0,0,,還好
Dialogue: 0,1:15:02.20,1:15:04.41,ENG,,0,0,0,,- Fine. - I wanna tell you something.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:02.91,1:15:08.15,CHT,,0,0,0,,告訴你…你們都沒帶好書來看
Dialogue: 0,1:15:04.50,1:15:08.12,ENG,,0,0,0,,You children didn't bring any real books to read, did you know that?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:08.21,1:15:10.58,ENG,,0,0,0,,I brought Moby Dick and Huckleberry Finn,
Dialogue: 0,1:15:08.25,1:15:10.88,CHT,,0,0,0,,我帶了…白鯨記和頑童歷險記
Dialogue: 0,1:15:10.67,1:15:13.38,ENG,,0,0,0,,and Baker and Simon had never read them.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:10.99,1:15:13.72,CHT,,0,0,0,,貝克他們都沒看過
Dialogue: 0,1:15:13.67,1:15:18.47,ENG,,0,0,0,,Now, I'm afraid to ask you, have you ever read Melville or Twain?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:13.83,1:15:19.26,CHT,,0,0,0,,我想問你…讀過梅爾維爾的著作？
Dialogue: 0,1:15:21.10,1:15:24.51,ENG,,0,0,0,,Hey, I'm a child of the movies, Fish.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:22.50,1:15:24.94,CHT,,0,0,0,,我們生於電影年代
Dialogue: 0,1:15:24.85,1:15:26.73,ENG,,0,0,0,,Okay, I see.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:25.04,1:15:27.01,CHT,,0,0,0,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,1:15:27.44,1:15:28.56,ENG,,0,0,0,,So...
Dialogue: 0,1:15:30.08,1:15:34.41,CHT,,0,0,0,,你的運氣不好，真的
Dialogue: 0,1:15:30.19,1:15:33.02,ENG,,0,0,0,,You got a shitty deal, Oren, you know that?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:33.32,1:15:34.40,ENG,,0,0,0,,You truly did.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:34.48,1:15:36.61,ENG,,0,0,0,,- Don't worry about me. - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:34.52,1:15:35.71,CHT,,0,0,0,,別替我擔心
Dialogue: 0,1:15:35.82,1:15:37.65,CHT,,0,0,0,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,1:15:37.74,1:15:40.16,ENG,,0,0,0,,- I mean that, really. - Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:37.75,1:15:41.92,CHT,,0,0,0,,說真的，別替我擔心
Dialogue: 0,1:15:40.24,1:15:42.37,ENG,,0,0,0,,- Don't worry about me. - Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:43.66,1:15:45.41,ENG,,0,0,0,,My whole life, I...
Dialogue: 0,1:15:43.72,1:15:45.69,CHT,,0,0,0,,我這一生…
Dialogue: 0,1:15:48.50,1:15:50.83,CHT,,0,0,0,,你知道我們這種人
Dialogue: 0,1:15:48.58,1:15:51.12,ENG,,0,0,0,,You know how it is for guys like us.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:52.33,1:15:55.43,CHT,,0,0,0,,你跟我是一樣的
Dialogue: 0,1:15:52.34,1:15:54.96,ENG,,0,0,0,,You and... You and I, we're the same.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:55.46,1:15:57.46,ENG,,0,0,0,,How do you mean by that?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:55.54,1:15:57.13,CHT,,0,0,0,,什麼意思？
Dialogue: 0,1:15:57.97,1:16:01.70,CHT,,0,0,0,,要做最棒的    原來如此
Dialogue: 0,1:15:57.97,1:16:01.64,ENG,,0,0,0,,- Gotta be the best. - I see. Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:01.78,1:16:04.40,CHT,,0,0,0,,做最棒的
Dialogue: 0,1:16:01.80,1:16:04.18,ENG,,0,0,0,,- Be the best. - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:16.86,1:16:20.89,CHT,,0,0,0,,有時我看到閃光
Dialogue: 0,1:16:16.98,1:16:20.15,ENG,,0,0,0,,Sometimes I see flashes of light.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:21.06,1:16:24.23,CHT,,0,0,0,,是彩色的
Dialogue: 0,1:16:21.07,1:16:23.57,ENG,,0,0,0,,You know, like colors.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:27.08,1:16:30.54,ENG,,0,0,0,,I fall asleep and I dream.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:27.14,1:16:29.20,CHT,,0,0,0,,我睡著時…
Dialogue: 0,1:16:29.64,1:16:31.11,CHT,,0,0,0,,做夢時
Dialogue: 0,1:16:32.01,1:16:35.34,CHT,,0,0,0,,我有一部份仍保持清醒
Dialogue: 0,1:16:32.04,1:16:35.00,ENG,,0,0,0,,But there's a part of me that's always awake,
Dialogue: 0,1:16:35.34,1:16:37.59,ENG,,0,0,0,,and I can see myself dreaming.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:35.44,1:16:37.94,CHT,,0,0,0,,看到自己在做夢
Dialogue: 0,1:16:43.18,1:16:46.05,ENG,,0,0,0,,I'm just... I'm seeing things differently, Fish.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:43.19,1:16:46.02,CHT,,0,0,0,,我的想法轉變了，小魚
Dialogue: 0,1:16:46.12,1:16:47.92,CHT,,0,0,0,,很好…
Dialogue: 0,1:16:46.14,1:16:48.14,ENG,,0,0,0,,That's good. That's good.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:49.26,1:16:50.45,CHT,,0,0,0,,小魚
Dialogue: 0,1:16:49.35,1:16:50.43,ENG,,0,0,0,,Fish.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:53.36,1:16:55.33,CHT,,0,0,0,,為何叫你小魚？
Dialogue: 0,1:16:53.40,1:16:55.90,ENG,,0,0,0,,Why the hell do they call you Fish?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:56.80,1:17:01.07,CHT,,0,0,0,,我名字聽來像鱘魚，小魚
Dialogue: 0,1:16:56.86,1:17:00.82,ENG,,0,0,0,,Well, Spurgeon, sturgeon, Fish.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:01.03,1:17:04.57,ENG,,0,0,0,,I mean, it took about 15 minutes of my first day at the naval academy.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:01.17,1:17:04.87,CHT,,0,0,0,,一進軍校就被取綽號
Dialogue: 0,1:17:04.66,1:17:07.83,ENG,,0,0,0,,Yeah. Your kids go there?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:06.94,1:17:08.34,CHT,,0,0,0,,孩子也念軍校？
Dialogue: 0,1:17:09.65,1:17:12.21,CHT,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,1:17:09.75,1:17:11.75,ENG,,0,0,0,,Yeah, they did. They did.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:12.25,1:17:14.46,ENG,,0,0,0,,And they're good men, both of them.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:12.32,1:17:14.48,CHT,,0,0,0,,他們都很優秀
Dialogue: 0,1:17:14.54,1:17:18.38,ENG,,0,0,0,,I don't see as much of them as I used to when Mary was alive.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:14.59,1:17:18.15,CHT,,0,0,0,,妻子過世後不常見到他們
Dialogue: 0,1:17:19.32,1:17:20.95,CHT,,0,0,0,,你可以不用談
Dialogue: 0,1:17:19.42,1:17:23.76,ENG,,0,0,0,,- You don't have to talk about it. it's okay. - No, it's okay. it's okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:21.43,1:17:23.89,CHT,,0,0,0,,沒關系
Dialogue: 0,1:17:24.00,1:17:25.96,CHT,,0,0,0,,你結過婚能了解
Dialogue: 0,1:17:24.05,1:17:25.47,ENG,,0,0,0,,You're a married man, you know what it's like.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:25.55,1:17:29.26,ENG,,0,0,0,,I mean, every marriage has its good years and its bad years.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:26.06,1:17:29.56,CHT,,0,0,0,,每個婚姻都有苦有樂
Dialogue: 0,1:17:29.67,1:17:31.53,CHT,,0,0,0,,結束時很美滿
Dialogue: 0,1:17:29.68,1:17:31.68,ENG,,0,0,0,,We ended on a great year.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:35.86,1:17:36.94,ENG,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:38.18,1:17:40.17,CHT,,0,0,0,,開始念了
Dialogue: 0,1:17:38.23,1:17:40.28,ENG,,0,0,0,,Anyway, let's get started.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:42.38,1:17:44.21,CHT,,0,0,0,,白鯨記，第一章
Dialogue: 0,1:17:42.45,1:17:44.24,ENG,,0,0,0,,Moby Dick, Chapter 1.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:47.82,1:17:48.81,CHT,,0,0,0,,叫我以實瑪利…
Dialogue: 0,1:17:47.95,1:17:49.20,ENG,,0,0,0,,"Call me lshmael.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:49.25,1:17:52.31,CHT,,0,0,0,,幾年前，別管確切時間
Dialogue: 0,1:17:49.29,1:17:52.08,ENG,,0,0,0,,"Several years ago, never mind how long precisely,
Dialogue: 0,1:17:52.16,1:17:54.00,ENG,,0,0,0,,"having little or no money in my purse..."
Dialogue: 0,1:17:52.42,1:17:55.19,CHT,,0,0,0,,我身上只有幾塊錢
Dialogue: 0,1:17:54.08,1:17:56.83,ENG,,0,0,0,,"Whenever I find myself growing grim about the mouth,
Dialogue: 0,1:17:55.30,1:17:58.13,CHT,,0,0,0,,那是個潮濕…
Dialogue: 0,1:17:56.92,1:18:00.59,ENG,,0,0,0,,"whenever it is a damp, drizzly November in my soul,
Dialogue: 0,1:17:58.23,1:18:01.00,CHT,,0,0,0,,陰雨的11月
Dialogue: 0,1:18:01.30,1:18:04.01,ENG,,0,0,0,,"whenever I find myself knocking people's hats off,
Dialogue: 0,1:18:04.09,1:18:10.18,ENG,,0,0,0,,"then I account it high time to get to sea as soon as I can."
Dialogue: 0,1:18:04.17,1:18:07.94,CHT,,0,0,0,,我算準了是漲潮的時候
Dialogue: 0,1:18:08.01,1:18:26.24,CHT,,0,0,0,,盡快趕到海邊
Dialogue: 0,1:18:26.24,1:18:27.50,CHT,,0,0,0,,聽好…    不要動
Dialogue: 0,1:18:26.28,1:18:27.86,ENG,,0,0,0,,- Listen up. - Hold it right there.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:27.84,1:18:29.14,CHT,,0,0,0,,畢德曼  我們是
Dialogue: 0,1:18:27.95,1:18:29.24,ENG,,0,0,0,,- Biederman. - Yeah, that's us.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:29.24,1:18:30.37,CHT,,0,0,0,,身份證
Dialogue: 0,1:18:29.33,1:18:30.45,ENG,,0,0,0,,IDs, please.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:30.53,1:18:31.83,ENG,,0,0,0,,Got them right here.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:31.91,1:18:33.95,ENG,,0,0,0,,There's four of us. Lewis?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:31.98,1:18:33.07,CHT,,0,0,0,,在這裡，我們四人
Dialogue: 0,1:18:34.85,1:18:37.25,CHT,,0,0,0,,我太太莎拉，結婚證書
Dialogue: 0,1:18:34.91,1:18:38.17,ENG,,0,0,0,,This is my wife, Sarah. We have a marriage license.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:38.38,1:18:40.17,ENG,,0,0,0,,I have it right here.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:46.59,1:18:47.46,CHT,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,1:18:46.80,1:18:49.89,ENG,,0,0,0,,Okay. All right, let's go. Let's move it out.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:48.16,1:18:49.72,CHT,,0,0,0,,走，出發
Dialogue: 0,1:18:50.56,1:18:53.50,CHT,,0,0,0,,媽！等一下我父母也要一起
Dialogue: 0,1:18:50.60,1:18:53.52,ENG,,0,0,0,,Mom. Wait. Sir, my parents are coming, too.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:53.60,1:18:55.16,CHT,,0,0,0,,等一下…還有哈奇納家人
Dialogue: 0,1:18:53.60,1:18:55.52,ENG,,0,0,0,,Wait, wait, the Hotchners are coming, too.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:55.27,1:18:56.90,CHT,,0,0,0,,HOTC…
Dialogue: 0,1:18:55.60,1:18:58.35,ENG,,0,0,0,,- H-O-T-C... - H-N-E-R.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:57.34,1:18:58.70,CHT,,0,0,0,,HNER
Dialogue: 0,1:18:59.47,1:19:00.13,CHT,,0,0,0,,不在名單上
Dialogue: 0,1:18:59.65,1:19:01.73,ENG,,0,0,0,,- No, it's not here. - No, no. it has to be there.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:00.57,1:19:03.77,CHT,,0,0,0,,不，名單已送至白宮上面沒有
Dialogue: 0,1:19:01.82,1:19:03.48,ENG,,0,0,0,,They sent their names to the White House.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:03.57,1:19:06.28,ENG,,0,0,0,,- They're not there. - Just check the goddamn list again.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:03.88,1:19:06.24,CHT,,0,0,0,,再查查看
Dialogue: 0,1:19:06.35,1:19:07.81,CHT,,0,0,0,,行李給我一定有
Dialogue: 0,1:19:06.36,1:19:07.74,ENG,,0,0,0,,- Leo, give me your bag. - They must be there.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:07.82,1:19:09.57,ENG,,0,0,0,,- Look closely. - Ellen, give me your bag, sweetie.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:07.92,1:19:09.61,CHT,,0,0,0,,你的行李
Dialogue: 0,1:19:09.66,1:19:10.78,ENG,,0,0,0,,No. They're not on the list.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:09.72,1:19:13.45,CHT,,0,0,0,,不在名單，抱歉，走了！
Dialogue: 0,1:19:10.87,1:19:12.66,ENG,,0,0,0,,- Wait, wait. - I'm sorry. Let's go. We have to go.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:12.74,1:19:14.91,ENG,,0,0,0,,- Sir, you don't understand. - Leo, can you check it one more time?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:13.69,1:19:15.42,CHT,,0,0,0,,能再查一次？
Dialogue: 0,1:19:15.00,1:19:18.42,ENG,,0,0,0,,I put you on the list. They said your names were on the list.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:15.52,1:19:18.58,CHT,,0,0,0,,他們說你們在名單上
Dialogue: 0,1:19:18.50,1:19:22.00,ENG,,0,0,0,,- Sarah, I put them on the list. - We're not on the list.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:18.69,1:19:21.39,CHT,,0,0,0,,莎拉，我登記了名單上沒我們
Dialogue: 0,1:19:22.50,1:19:24.75,ENG,,0,0,0,,I need the Biedermans on the bus now.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:22.53,1:19:24.73,CHT,,0,0,0,,畢德曼家人立刻上車
Dialogue: 0,1:19:24.83,1:19:26.60,CHT,,0,0,0,,怎麼辦？我跟你們一起
Dialogue: 0,1:19:24.84,1:19:26.59,ENG,,0,0,0,,- Dad, I wanna stay with you. - What?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:26.67,1:19:29.26,ENG,,0,0,0,,- No, no, no. We have to go. - Leo, let's get her on the bus.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:26.77,1:19:29.53,CHT,,0,0,0,,不…快上車
Dialogue: 0,1:19:29.34,1:19:32.14,ENG,,0,0,0,,- Yes, I need to stay with you. - Sarah.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:29.64,1:19:31.10,CHT,,0,0,0,,我要陪著你們
Dialogue: 0,1:19:31.21,1:19:33.90,CHT,,0,0,0,,莎拉，你必須上車
Dialogue: 0,1:19:32.51,1:19:33.89,ENG,,0,0,0,,Sarah, you need to go.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:33.97,1:19:35.14,ENG,,0,0,0,,No, I have to stay with you, Dad.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:34.01,1:19:35.34,CHT,,0,0,0,,我要陪你們
Dialogue: 0,1:19:35.22,1:19:37.31,ENG,,0,0,0,,Listen, I'm not going anywhere without you.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:35.44,1:19:37.21,CHT,,0,0,0,,沒有你，我不走
Dialogue: 0,1:19:37.31,1:19:39.11,CHT,,0,0,0,,你在做糊塗事
Dialogue: 0,1:19:37.39,1:19:38.94,ENG,,0,0,0,,Sarah, you don't know what you're doing.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:39.02,1:19:40.60,ENG,,0,0,0,,Come or stay, young lady, this bus is moving out.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:39.21,1:19:40.94,CHT,,0,0,0,,快決定！巴士要開了
Dialogue: 0,1:19:40.69,1:19:43.82,ENG,,0,0,0,,Son, on the bus. Get on the bus!
Dialogue: 0,1:19:41.05,1:19:44.02,CHT,,0,0,0,,里歐，上車，快上車！
Dialogue: 0,1:19:44.07,1:19:45.28,ENG,,0,0,0,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:45.36,1:19:48.19,ENG,,0,0,0,,Chuck, we'll work it out when we get there.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:45.42,1:19:46.75,CHT,,0,0,0,,到了再想辦法
Dialogue: 0,1:19:57.17,1:19:59.90,CHT,,0,0,0,,我愛你
Dialogue: 0,1:20:08.38,1:20:12.26,ENG,,0,0,0,,- What's that, the crates? - Jenny, there's a phone call for you.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:08.81,1:20:11.18,CHT,,0,0,0,,珍妮，你的電話
Dialogue: 0,1:20:15.45,1:20:18.22,CHT,,0,0,0,,我就是
Dialogue: 0,1:20:15.51,1:20:17.72,ENG,,0,0,0,,Yes. This is she.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:19.09,1:20:21.75,CHT,,0,0,0,,蘿冰藍納，我母親
Dialogue: 0,1:20:19.23,1:20:21.44,ENG,,0,0,0,,It's Robin Lerner. My mother.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:29.43,1:20:30.59,CHT,,0,0,0,,什麼時候？
Dialogue: 0,1:20:29.61,1:20:30.74,ENG,,0,0,0,,When?
Dialogue: 0,1:20:35.31,1:20:37.37,CHT,,0,0,0,,61歲
Dialogue: 0,1:20:35.78,1:20:37.12,ENG,,0,0,0,,Sixty-one.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:39.38,1:20:41.85,CHT,,0,0,0,,我就下來，謝謝
Dialogue: 0,1:20:39.50,1:20:42.12,ENG,,0,0,0,,I'll come down there, then. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:43.15,1:20:44.88,CHT,,0,0,0,,非常感激
Dialogue: 0,1:20:43.21,1:20:44.96,ENG,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:49.05,1:20:51.11,CHT,,0,0,0,,需要幫忙嗎？
Dialogue: 0,1:20:49.09,1:20:51.67,ENG,,0,0,0,,Jenny, do you want me to do something?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:55.32,1:21:56.88,CHT,,0,0,0,,你來遲了
Dialogue: 0,1:21:55.41,1:21:58.66,ENG,,0,0,0,,You're too late. I already took care of everything.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:56.99,1:21:59.08,CHT,,0,0,0,,我已處理好了
Dialogue: 0,1:22:01.16,1:22:04.50,CHT,,0,0,0,,快上車，你會生病，拜託
Dialogue: 0,1:22:01.25,1:22:04.79,ENG,,0,0,0,,Come, come. inside the car. You're getting sick. Please.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:05.00,1:22:06.83,CHT,,0,0,0,,我要跟你談
Dialogue: 0,1:22:05.00,1:22:06.83,ENG,,0,0,0,,I want to talk to you.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:08.50,1:22:10.20,CHT,,0,0,0,,拜託！上車
Dialogue: 0,1:22:08.59,1:22:10.04,ENG,,0,0,0,,Please, come.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:12.14,1:22:15.44,CHT,,0,0,0,,我不在乎！去跟克露伊談
Dialogue: 0,1:22:12.17,1:22:15.43,ENG,,0,0,0,,I don't give a shit. Go home and tell it to Chloe.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:15.51,1:22:17.39,ENG,,0,0,0,,I can't. She left me.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:15.54,1:22:17.17,CHT,,0,0,0,,不行，克露伊走了
Dialogue: 0,1:22:17.68,1:22:20.56,ENG,,0,0,0,,She's with her mother. They both got scared.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:17.71,1:22:20.91,CHT,,0,0,0,,她去找她媽媽，她們嚇壞了
Dialogue: 0,1:22:21.02,1:22:24.58,CHT,,0,0,0,,我要跟你談談，我需要你
Dialogue: 0,1:22:21.02,1:22:23.85,ENG,,0,0,0,,Come. I want to talk to you. I need you.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:25.49,1:22:27.01,CHT,,0,0,0,,感覺如何？
Dialogue: 0,1:22:25.56,1:22:27.19,ENG,,0,0,0,,How does it feel?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:31.29,1:22:33.76,CHT,,0,0,0,,我覺得像孤兒
Dialogue: 0,1:22:31.36,1:22:33.19,ENG,,0,0,0,,I feel like an orphan.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:36.17,1:22:38.50,CHT,,0,0,0,,珍妮…
Dialogue: 0,1:22:36.20,1:22:38.24,ENG,,0,0,0,,Jenny. Jenny!
Dialogue: 0,1:22:41.94,1:22:43.10,CHT,,0,0,0,,停車
Dialogue: 0,1:22:41.95,1:22:43.04,ENG,,0,0,0,,Stop.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:53.38,1:22:57.68,CHT,,0,0,0,,“距離撞擊時間：5天”
Dialogue: 0,1:23:07.30,1:23:14.14,CHT,,0,0,0,,“方舟洞穴，密蘇里州”
Dialogue: 0,1:23:57.55,1:24:00.95,CHT,,0,0,0,,歡迎，我是橘254區領隊
Dialogue: 0,1:23:57.61,1:24:00.91,ENG,,0,0,0,,Welcome to the Ark. I'm section leader for Orange 254.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:00.99,1:24:03.87,ENG,,0,0,0,,Remember that. it's where you'll be calling home the next two years.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:01.05,1:24:03.72,CHT,,0,0,0,,記住，這是未來2年的家
Dialogue: 0,1:24:03.89,1:24:06.48,CHT,,0,0,0,,帶著行李跟我來
Dialogue: 0,1:24:03.95,1:24:07.45,ENG,,0,0,0,,So gather your things and follow me to the orientation gallery.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:09.46,1:24:13.21,ENG,,0,0,0,,If you have been designated as a civilian section officer,
Dialogue: 0,1:24:09.60,1:24:15.56,CHT,,0,0,0,,被選任區民官者
Dialogue: 0,1:24:13.67,1:24:17.51,ENG,,0,0,0,,report to section Red 116 upon entering.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:15.67,1:24:18.30,CHT,,0,0,0,,請來報到
Dialogue: 0,1:24:18.80,1:24:23.59,ENG,,0,0,0,,Once again, if you have been designated as a civilian section officer,
Dialogue: 0,1:24:18.84,1:24:23.40,CHT,,0,0,0,,被選任區民官者
Dialogue: 0,1:24:23.68,1:24:27.81,CHT,,0,0,0,,請來報到
Dialogue: 0,1:24:23.68,1:24:27.52,ENG,,0,0,0,,report to section Red 116 upon entering.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:29.31,1:24:30.44,ENG,,0,0,0,,Leo.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:29.32,1:24:30.51,CHT,,0,0,0,,里歐
Dialogue: 0,1:24:32.65,1:24:33.81,CHT,,0,0,0,,我不去
Dialogue: 0,1:24:32.73,1:24:34.27,ENG,,0,0,0,,I'm not coming.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:34.94,1:24:37.19,ENG,,0,0,0,,Leo, come with us right now.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:34.99,1:24:37.29,CHT,,0,0,0,,里歐，快跟我們來
Dialogue: 0,1:24:37.46,1:24:39.15,CHT,,0,0,0,,我要回去找莎拉
Dialogue: 0,1:24:37.53,1:24:39.40,ENG,,0,0,0,,I have to go back for Sarah.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:39.49,1:24:41.53,ENG,,0,0,0,,- Leo. - Mom, I'm going.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:39.76,1:24:42.09,CHT,,0,0,0,,媽，我決定了
Dialogue: 0,1:24:48.50,1:24:50.33,ENG,,0,0,0,,- Don, what are you doing? - I'm giving him something to trade.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:48.54,1:24:51.33,CHT,,0,0,0,,丹，你幹什麼？給他些東西去交換
Dialogue: 0,1:24:50.41,1:24:52.29,ENG,,0,0,0,,That's what I'm doing.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:52.46,1:24:55.46,ENG,,0,0,0,,- I want you to take this. - Dad, that's enough.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:52.51,1:24:53.67,CHT,,0,0,0,,帶著
Dialogue: 0,1:24:53.88,1:24:54.74,CHT,,0,0,0,,爸，夠了
Dialogue: 0,1:25:00.67,1:25:02.05,ENG,,0,0,0,,God damn it.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:00.85,1:25:04.44,CHT,,0,0,0,,可惡！好好照顧自己
Dialogue: 0,1:25:02.89,1:25:05.22,ENG,,0,0,0,,You take care of yourself, okay?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:08.27,1:25:09.93,ENG,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna make it.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:08.39,1:25:09.76,CHT,,0,0,0,,我會平安的
Dialogue: 0,1:25:12.80,1:25:13.85,CHT,,0,0,0,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,1:25:20.47,1:25:21.70,CHT,,0,0,0,,尹屈基呢？
Dialogue: 0,1:25:20.49,1:25:21.78,ENG,,0,0,0,,What about Entrekin?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:21.80,1:25:24.71,CHT,,0,0,0,,他兩週沒回我電話
Dialogue: 0,1:25:21.86,1:25:24.74,ENG,,0,0,0,,I don't know. He hasn't returned my call in over two weeks.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:24.81,1:25:26.04,CHT,,0,0,0,,抱歉，珍妮
Dialogue: 0,1:25:24.82,1:25:26.37,ENG,,0,0,0,,- Excuse me, Jenny. - Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:26.41,1:25:27.77,CHT,,0,0,0,,你父親來了
Dialogue: 0,1:25:26.45,1:25:28.20,ENG,,0,0,0,,Your father's here.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:33.37,1:25:36.17,ENG,,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:36.15,1:25:38.25,CHT,,0,0,0,,我不能久待
Dialogue: 0,1:25:36.25,1:25:40.80,ENG,,0,0,0,,I can't stay long. I'm leaving the city, but I wanted to show you something.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:38.36,1:25:40.65,CHT,,0,0,0,,只給你看樣東西
Dialogue: 0,1:25:40.88,1:25:43.97,ENG,,0,0,0,,I wanted to show you that you're not an orphan.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:40.96,1:25:43.65,CHT,,0,0,0,,讓你知道你不是孤兒
Dialogue: 0,1:25:47.86,1:25:51.89,CHT,,0,0,0,,我能證明你不是孤兒
Dialogue: 0,1:25:47.89,1:25:50.60,ENG,,0,0,0,,I have proof that you're not an orphan.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:50.93,1:25:52.06,ENG,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:55.47,1:25:56.67,CHT,,0,0,0,,你看
Dialogue: 0,1:25:55.60,1:25:56.73,ENG,,0,0,0,,Look.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:06.35,1:26:07.58,CHT,,0,0,0,,媽媽呢？
Dialogue: 0,1:26:06.37,1:26:07.74,ENG,,0,0,0,,Where's Mom?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:08.72,1:26:11.05,CHT,,0,0,0,,她拍的照
Dialogue: 0,1:26:08.87,1:26:10.54,ENG,,0,0,0,,Behind the camera.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:11.82,1:26:13.26,CHT,,0,0,0,,她拍的？
Dialogue: 0,1:26:11.91,1:26:13.41,ENG,,0,0,0,,She took this?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:14.04,1:26:15.71,ENG,,0,0,0,,And this one, too.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:14.13,1:26:15.62,CHT,,0,0,0,,這張也是
Dialogue: 0,1:26:17.25,1:26:20.09,ENG,,0,0,0,,She was such an artist, don't you think so?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:17.26,1:26:20.56,CHT,,0,0,0,,她拍得真好，對嗎？
Dialogue: 0,1:26:21.80,1:26:23.86,CHT,,0,0,0,,你不記得了？
Dialogue: 0,1:26:21.92,1:26:23.88,ENG,,0,0,0,,You don't remember when you take them?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:23.97,1:26:26.30,CHT,,0,0,0,,才5歲怎麼記得？
Dialogue: 0,1:26:23.97,1:26:26.97,ENG,,0,0,0,,I'm five years old. How would I remember that?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:27.43,1:26:31.39,ENG,,0,0,0,,Well, some people do remember when they were five years old.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:27.44,1:26:32.38,CHT,,0,0,0,,有人記得5歲的事
Dialogue: 0,1:26:34.18,1:26:39.17,CHT,,0,0,0,,當天天氣很好，在海邊
Dialogue: 0,1:26:34.27,1:26:36.39,ENG,,0,0,0,,It was such a beautiful day.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:36.56,1:26:38.44,ENG,,0,0,0,,All alone on the beach.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:40.73,1:26:43.61,ENG,,0,0,0,,And of course she would have been in the picture,
Dialogue: 0,1:26:40.79,1:26:43.62,CHT,,0,0,0,,她也該照張像
Dialogue: 0,1:26:43.69,1:26:47.11,ENG,,0,0,0,,but there was no one else to hold the camera,
Dialogue: 0,1:26:43.72,1:26:48.66,CHT,,0,0,0,,但誰替我們照
Dialogue: 0,1:26:48.03,1:26:50.70,ENG,,0,0,0,,and she insisted.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:49.73,1:26:51.39,CHT,,0,0,0,,她很堅持
Dialogue: 0,1:26:51.66,1:26:53.45,ENG,,0,0,0,,You know how she is.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:51.70,1:26:54.17,CHT,,0,0,0,,你知道她…
Dialogue: 0,1:26:54.50,1:26:56.53,CHT,,0,0,0,,你知道她的個性
Dialogue: 0,1:26:54.54,1:26:55.96,ENG,,0,0,0,,How she was.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:57.83,1:26:59.00,ENG,,0,0,0,,Jenny.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:57.84,1:26:58.90,CHT,,0,0,0,,珍妮
Dialogue: 0,1:27:04.31,1:27:08.91,CHT,,0,0,0,,美好的一天，令人難忘
Dialogue: 0,1:27:04.38,1:27:07.68,ENG,,0,0,0,,It was such a good day for all of us.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:08.93,1:27:10.64,ENG,,0,0,0,,Don't you remember?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:09.02,1:27:10.88,CHT,,0,0,0,,你忘了？
Dialogue: 0,1:27:17.59,1:27:19.06,CHT,,0,0,0,,你留著
Dialogue: 0,1:27:17.60,1:27:18.94,ENG,,0,0,0,,Keep them.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:22.23,1:27:23.92,CHT,,0,0,0,,再見
Dialogue: 0,1:27:22.32,1:27:23.52,ENG,,0,0,0,,Goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:57.13,1:28:00.26,CHT,,0,0,0,,已證實洲際飛彈…
Dialogue: 0,1:27:57.18,1:28:00.19,ENG,,0,0,0,,We have now confirmed the launch of all the Titan missiles
Dialogue: 0,1:28:00.27,1:28:03.44,ENG,,0,0,0,,from their positions in North Dakota and Wyoming.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:00.36,1:28:02.83,CHT,,0,0,0,,由北達科塔基地發射
Dialogue: 0,1:28:03.47,1:28:08.23,CHT,,0,0,0,,彗星約14小時後進入大氣層
Dialogue: 0,1:28:03.52,1:28:06.23,ENG,,0,0,0,,The comets are now approximately 14 hours
Dialogue: 0,1:28:06.32,1:28:08.53,ENG,,0,0,0,,outside of Earth's atmosphere,
Dialogue: 0,1:28:08.64,1:28:10.70,CHT,,0,0,0,,飛彈將於20分鐘內
Dialogue: 0,1:28:08.82,1:28:10.95,ENG,,0,0,0,,and we are told it should take these missiles
Dialogue: 0,1:28:10.81,1:28:13.57,CHT,,0,0,0,,攔截目標
Dialogue: 0,1:28:11.03,1:28:13.87,ENG,,0,0,0,,less than 20 minutes to reach their target.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:14.48,1:28:16.54,CHT,,0,0,0,,目前的情況是…
Dialogue: 0,1:28:14.58,1:28:16.70,ENG,,0,0,0,,Okay, here's what we're looking at.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:16.65,1:28:19.05,CHT,,0,0,0,,洲際飛彈已發射
Dialogue: 0,1:28:16.79,1:28:19.16,ENG,,0,0,0,,All of the Titans have been launched.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:19.15,1:28:21.58,CHT,,0,0,0,,不知結果如何
Dialogue: 0,1:28:19.25,1:28:22.46,ENG,,0,0,0,,We still won't know if they've made a difference.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:22.32,1:28:24.48,CHT,,0,0,0,,還要過一段時間…
Dialogue: 0,1:28:22.54,1:28:24.79,ENG,,0,0,0,,The comets have to travel for a while
Dialogue: 0,1:28:24.59,1:28:26.72,CHT,,0,0,0,,雷達偵測系統
Dialogue: 0,1:28:24.88,1:28:28.09,ENG,,0,0,0,,before the radar tracking stations can see if they've been pushed
Dialogue: 0,1:28:26.83,1:28:30.69,CHT,,0,0,0,,將告知最後結果
Dialogue: 0,1:28:28.17,1:28:30.97,ENG,,0,0,0,,to a safe course that'll bypass the Earth.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:31.20,1:28:34.89,CHT,,0,0,0,,我們只好再次等待
Dialogue: 0,1:28:31.34,1:28:34.39,ENG,,0,0,0,,So one more time, we have to wait.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:54.49,1:28:55.39,CHT,,0,0,0,,轉播中？
Dialogue: 0,1:28:54.74,1:28:57.24,ENG,,0,0,0,,Are we on? - We're on, Mr. President.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:56.02,1:28:57.82,CHT,,0,0,0,,是的，總統先生
Dialogue: 0,1:29:07.60,1:29:09.59,CHT,,0,0,0,,洲際飛彈失敗
Dialogue: 0,1:29:07.75,1:29:09.76,ENG,,0,0,0,,Our missiles have failed.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:11.27,1:29:14.87,CHT,,0,0,0,,彗星仍朝地球而來
Dialogue: 0,1:29:11.38,1:29:14.01,ENG,,0,0,0,,The comets are still headed for Earth,
Dialogue: 0,1:29:16.74,1:29:18.57,CHT,,0,0,0,,無法阻止
Dialogue: 0,1:29:16.89,1:29:19.72,ENG,,0,0,0,,and there's nothing we can do to stop them.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:22.28,1:29:24.11,CHT,,0,0,0,,就這樣了
Dialogue: 0,1:29:22.60,1:29:24.10,ENG,,0,0,0,,So this is it.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:25.25,1:29:28.05,CHT,,0,0,0,,若地球沒毀滅…
Dialogue: 0,1:29:25.44,1:29:27.44,ENG,,0,0,0,,If the world does go on,
Dialogue: 0,1:29:28.16,1:29:30.72,CHT,,0,0,0,,也將面臨大災難
Dialogue: 0,1:29:28.23,1:29:30.53,ENG,,0,0,0,,it will not go on for everyone.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:31.93,1:29:35.89,CHT,,0,0,0,,我們算出彗星最後軌道
Dialogue: 0,1:29:32.20,1:29:35.95,ENG,,0,0,0,,We have now been able to calculate the comets' final trajectories,
Dialogue: 0,1:29:36.00,1:29:38.90,CHT,,0,0,0,,知道將撞擊的地點
Dialogue: 0,1:29:36.03,1:29:39.33,ENG,,0,0,0,,and we have determined where they're going to strike.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:39.47,1:29:42.87,CHT,,0,0,0,,小彗星畢德曼先撞擊
Dialogue: 0,1:29:39.70,1:29:43.16,ENG,,0,0,0,,The smaller of the two comets, Biederman, will hit first
Dialogue: 0,1:29:42.97,1:29:45.20,CHT,,0,0,0,,在大西洋沿海
Dialogue: 0,1:29:43.25,1:29:44.87,ENG,,0,0,0,,somewhere along the Atlantic seaboard,
Dialogue: 0,1:29:44.96,1:29:48.04,ENG,,0,0,0,,probably in the waters off the coast of Cape Hatteras,
Dialogue: 0,1:29:45.31,1:29:47.87,CHT,,0,0,0,,赫特勒角附近
Dialogue: 0,1:29:47.98,1:29:49.27,CHT,,0,0,0,,12小時內
Dialogue: 0,1:29:48.13,1:29:51.80,ENG,,0,0,0,,in just under 12 hours, at 4:35 p.m. Eastern Daylight Time.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:49.38,1:29:52.35,CHT,,0,0,0,,下午4點35分
Dialogue: 0,1:29:52.61,1:29:55.11,CHT,,0,0,0,,彗星的撞擊將是…
Dialogue: 0,1:29:52.84,1:29:55.55,ENG,,0,0,0,,The impact of the comet is going to be,
Dialogue: 0,1:29:56.45,1:29:58.44,CHT,,0,0,0,,大災難
Dialogue: 0,1:29:56.64,1:29:58.26,ENG,,0,0,0,,well, disastrous.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:59.19,1:30:03.56,CHT,,0,0,0,,大西洋海潮會迅速升高
Dialogue: 0,1:29:59.39,1:30:01.39,ENG,,0,0,0,,There will be a very large tidal wave
Dialogue: 0,1:30:01.48,1:30:03.56,ENG,,0,0,0,,moving quickly through the Atlantic Ocean.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:03.64,1:30:07.73,ENG,,0,0,0,,It'll be 100 feet high, traveling at 1,100 miles an hour.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:03.66,1:30:07.69,CHT,,0,0,0,,高達1百呎，時速1千1百哩
Dialogue: 0,1:30:07.80,1:30:10.09,CHT,,0,0,0,,比音速還快
Dialogue: 0,1:30:07.81,1:30:10.48,ENG,,0,0,0,,That's faster than the speed of sound.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:10.67,1:30:13.16,CHT,,0,0,0,,潮水接觸淺灘速度減緩
Dialogue: 0,1:30:10.82,1:30:13.32,ENG,,0,0,0,,As the wave reaches shallow water it's going to slow down,
Dialogue: 0,1:30:13.27,1:30:17.17,CHT,,0,0,0,,但湧起的浪潮高度…
Dialogue: 0,1:30:13.40,1:30:17.74,ENG,,0,0,0,,but the wave height, depending on the depth of the shelf off the coast,
Dialogue: 0,1:30:17.67,1:30:22.04,CHT,,0,0,0,,可達1千至3千5百英呎
Dialogue: 0,1:30:17.82,1:30:21.74,ENG,,0,0,0,,will be anywhere from 1,000 to 3,500 feet high.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:23.48,1:30:26.35,CHT,,0,0,0,,海水將倒灌平地
Dialogue: 0,1:30:23.87,1:30:26.46,ENG,,0,0,0,,Where the land is flat, the wave will wash inland
Dialogue: 0,1:30:26.45,1:30:29.68,CHT,,0,0,0,,6、7百英哩
Dialogue: 0,1:30:26.54,1:30:28.83,ENG,,0,0,0,,600 to 700 miles.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:30.02,1:30:32.32,CHT,,0,0,0,,撞擊40分鐘後
Dialogue: 0,1:30:30.25,1:30:34.17,ENG,,0,0,0,,The wave will hit our nation's capital 40 minutes after impact.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:32.42,1:30:34.91,CHT,,0,0,0,,海潮襲向華府
Dialogue: 0,1:30:35.66,1:30:39.25,CHT,,0,0,0,,紐約市、波士頓、大西洋城
Dialogue: 0,1:30:35.84,1:30:40.55,ENG,,0,0,0,,New York City, Boston, Atlanta, Philadelphia,
Dialogue: 0,1:30:39.53,1:30:43.93,CHT,,0,0,0,,費城都將被摧毀
Dialogue: 0,1:30:42.35,1:30:44.18,ENG,,0,0,0,,all will be destroyed.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:44.39,1:30:48.23,ENG,,0,0,0,,If you have any means of getting away from the path of this wave,
Dialogue: 0,1:30:44.40,1:30:46.67,CHT,,0,0,0,,若想逃離此區
Dialogue: 0,1:30:46.77,1:30:49.36,CHT,,0,0,0,,即刻出發
Dialogue: 0,1:30:48.31,1:30:49.65,ENG,,0,0,0,,leave now.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:50.17,1:30:52.61,CHT,,0,0,0,,大彗星沃夫
Dialogue: 0,1:30:50.27,1:30:52.53,ENG,,0,0,0,,The impact of the larger comet
Dialogue: 0,1:30:52.71,1:30:56.11,CHT,,0,0,0,,將造成更大災難
Dialogue: 0,1:30:52.86,1:30:56.15,ENG,,0,0,0,,will be nothing less than an extinction-level event.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:56.45,1:30:59.08,CHT,,0,0,0,,將撞擊加拿大西部
Dialogue: 0,1:30:56.70,1:31:00.74,ENG,,0,0,0,,It will strike land in western Canada three hours after Biederman.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:59.18,1:31:01.15,CHT,,0,0,0,,在小彗星撞擊3小時後
Dialogue: 0,1:31:02.12,1:31:05.02,CHT,,0,0,0,,一週內，天空將佈滿塵埃
Dialogue: 0,1:31:02.24,1:31:05.08,ENG,,0,0,0,,Within a week, the skies will be dark with dust from the impact,
Dialogue: 0,1:31:05.16,1:31:07.95,CHT,,0,0,0,,兩年不見天日
Dialogue: 0,1:31:05.16,1:31:07.79,ENG,,0,0,0,,and they will stay dark for two years.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:08.39,1:31:09.66,CHT,,0,0,0,,所有植物將於…
Dialogue: 0,1:31:08.67,1:31:11.25,ENG,,0,0,0,,All plant life will be dead within
Dialogue: 0,1:31:09.76,1:31:13.72,CHT,,0,0,0,,4週內枯死
Dialogue: 0,1:31:12.88,1:31:14.21,ENG,,0,0,0,,four weeks.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:15.30,1:31:17.67,CHT,,0,0,0,,動物將於…
Dialogue: 0,1:31:15.51,1:31:17.30,ENG,,0,0,0,,Animal life within
Dialogue: 0,1:31:18.87,1:31:21.20,CHT,,0,0,0,,幾個月內死亡
Dialogue: 0,1:31:19.05,1:31:20.51,ENG,,0,0,0,,a few months.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:23.84,1:31:25.78,CHT,,0,0,0,,就這樣了
Dialogue: 0,1:31:24.02,1:31:25.47,ENG,,0,0,0,,So that's it.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:26.68,1:31:28.54,CHT,,0,0,0,,祝大家幸運
Dialogue: 0,1:31:26.94,1:31:28.73,ENG,,0,0,0,,Good luck to us all.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:49.54,1:31:53.37,CHT,,0,0,0,,“距撞擊時間：10小時37分”
Dialogue: 0,1:31:55.08,1:31:57.13,CHT,,0,0,0,,大家注意
Dialogue: 0,1:31:55.17,1:31:59.59,ENG,,0,0,0,,Could I bother everyone for a minute? Now, let's take a look at the big one.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:57.34,1:31:59.28,CHT,,0,0,0,,看那個大彗星
Dialogue: 0,1:31:59.55,1:32:02.11,CHT,,0,0,0,,彗尾氣體
Dialogue: 0,1:31:59.68,1:32:03.14,ENG,,0,0,0,,Now, the out-gassing has created a vent a half a mile wide
Dialogue: 0,1:32:02.22,1:32:04.74,CHT,,0,0,0,,有半里寬2里厚
Dialogue: 0,1:32:03.22,1:32:06.18,ENG,,0,0,0,,and at least 2 miles deep. Comet gets closer to the sun,
Dialogue: 0,1:32:04.85,1:32:08.15,CHT,,0,0,0,,彗星靠近太陽，冰融為氣體
Dialogue: 0,1:32:06.27,1:32:10.06,ENG,,0,0,0,,sun melts ice, ice turns to steam, we get a big hole. Okay?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:08.26,1:32:10.72,CHT,,0,0,0,,可以看到個大洞
Dialogue: 0,1:32:10.82,1:32:14.85,CHT,,0,0,0,,還剩多少核彈？
Dialogue: 0,1:32:11.02,1:32:14.98,ENG,,0,0,0,,So, how many nukes we have left in the back?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:14.96,1:32:16.16,CHT,,0,0,0,,4顆
Dialogue: 0,1:32:15.15,1:32:16.28,ENG,,0,0,0,,Four.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:17.30,1:32:20.70,CHT,,0,0,0,,若能將剩餘核彈…
Dialogue: 0,1:32:17.40,1:32:21.82,ENG,,0,0,0,,Okay. if we can get the remaining bombs in that vent,
Dialogue: 0,1:32:20.80,1:32:22.90,CHT,,0,0,0,,帶到彗星洞內
Dialogue: 0,1:32:22.99,1:32:26.20,ENG,,0,0,0,,there shouldn't be anything left of that comet bigger than a suitcase.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:23.00,1:32:26.03,CHT,,0,0,0,,彗星會被炸成碎片
Dialogue: 0,1:32:26.14,1:32:28.77,CHT,,0,0,0,,小彗星勢必將撞上
Dialogue: 0,1:32:26.29,1:32:29.33,ENG,,0,0,0,,Now, we can't do anything about the little one,
Dialogue: 0,1:32:29.48,1:32:32.07,CHT,,0,0,0,,但還能阻止大彗星
Dialogue: 0,1:32:29.66,1:32:32.79,ENG,,0,0,0,,but, you know, it just might give them a chance.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:33.31,1:32:35.28,CHT,,0,0,0,,沒密碼不能用定時器
Dialogue: 0,1:32:33.50,1:32:35.17,ENG,,0,0,0,,Now, without the arming codes, we're gonna have to wait
Dialogue: 0,1:32:35.25,1:32:39.13,ENG,,0,0,0,,to set the bomb timers until we get closer to Earth to raise Houston.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:35.38,1:32:38.94,CHT,,0,0,0,,得先聯絡上休士頓
Dialogue: 0,1:32:39.05,1:32:43.89,CHT,,0,0,0,,太空衣氧氣量不夠設置核彈
Dialogue: 0,1:32:39.22,1:32:41.18,ENG,,0,0,0,,We may not have enough life support left
Dialogue: 0,1:32:41.26,1:32:44.18,ENG,,0,0,0,,to get back into the cargo bay for the nukes,
Dialogue: 0,1:32:44.13,1:32:46.12,CHT,,0,0,0,,更別提登陸彗星
Dialogue: 0,1:32:44.39,1:32:46.31,ENG,,0,0,0,,much less to work down on the comet.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:46.30,1:32:50.79,CHT,,0,0,0,,彌賽亞號動力不夠再登陸
Dialogue: 0,1:32:46.39,1:32:48.64,ENG,,0,0,0,,And we sure as hell don't have enough propellant left in the Messiah
Dialogue: 0,1:32:48.73,1:32:50.35,ENG,,0,0,0,,to maneuver with.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:51.63,1:32:56.50,CHT,,0,0,0,,登上彗星怎麼回航？
Dialogue: 0,1:32:51.90,1:32:54.94,ENG,,0,0,0,,How are we supposed to get back off the surface once we've...
Dialogue: 0,1:32:55.02,1:32:57.15,ENG,,0,0,0,,Once we've gone down there?
Dialogue: 0,1:33:01.81,1:33:02.94,CHT,,0,0,0,,不回航
Dialogue: 0,1:33:02.03,1:33:03.32,ENG,,0,0,0,,We don't.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:11.92,1:33:13.89,CHT,,0,0,0,,往好處想
Dialogue: 0,1:33:12.17,1:33:14.63,ENG,,0,0,0,,Well, you look at the bright side.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:15.26,1:33:18.16,CHT,,0,0,0,,學校將以我們命名
Dialogue: 0,1:33:15.38,1:33:18.21,ENG,,0,0,0,,We'll all have high schools named after us.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:39.55,1:33:42.18,CHT,,0,0,0,,休士頓，彌賽亞呼叫
Dialogue: 0,1:33:39.69,1:33:45.16,ENG,,0,0,0,,Houston, this is Messiah.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:42.69,1:33:45.18,CHT,,0,0,0,,休士頓，彌賽亞呼叫
Dialogue: 0,1:33:57.97,1:33:59.73,CHT,,0,0,0,,真高興聽到呼叫
Dialogue: 0,1:33:58.13,1:34:00.25,ENG,,0,0,0,,Nice of you to call, Messiah.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:00.17,1:34:02.07,CHT,,0,0,0,,我們正在擔心
Dialogue: 0,1:34:00.34,1:34:02.38,ENG,,0,0,0,,We were beginning to wonder what the hell you were doing up there.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:02.17,1:34:03.80,CHT,,0,0,0,,地球真美
Dialogue: 0,1:34:02.47,1:34:05.55,ENG,,0,0,0,,- Admiring the view, Houston. - Fish, is that you?
Dialogue: 0,1:34:03.91,1:34:05.43,CHT,,0,0,0,,小魚，是你？
Dialogue: 0,1:34:05.64,1:34:07.37,CHT,,0,0,0,,對，沒時間聊天了
Dialogue: 0,1:34:05.64,1:34:08.30,ENG,,0,0,0,,Yep. We don't have time to talk, Houston.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:08.28,1:34:11.15,CHT,,0,0,0,,我們阻止不了小彗星但有個計劃
Dialogue: 0,1:34:08.39,1:34:11.31,ENG,,0,0,0,,There's nothing we can do about the smaller one, but we do have a plan.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:11.25,1:34:13.81,CHT,,0,0,0,,需要核彈引爆密碼
Dialogue: 0,1:34:11.39,1:34:13.89,ENG,,0,0,0,,We need the arming codes for the last four nukes.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:13.92,1:34:15.48,CHT,,0,0,0,,引爆密碼？幹嘛？
Dialogue: 0,1:34:13.98,1:34:15.60,ENG,,0,0,0,,Arming codes? What the hell for?
Dialogue: 0,1:34:15.59,1:34:18.11,CHT,,0,0,0,,米奇，要說或要做？隨你便
Dialogue: 0,1:34:15.69,1:34:18.69,ENG,,0,0,0,,Mitch, we can do or we can teach. What's your pleasure?
Dialogue: 0,1:34:20.26,1:34:22.12,CHT,,0,0,0,,找引爆密碼，快！
Dialogue: 0,1:34:20.28,1:34:22.82,ENG,,0,0,0,,Get the arming codes. Get the goddamn codes!
Dialogue: 0,1:34:23.03,1:34:25.22,CHT,,0,0,0,,直升機能載7人
Dialogue: 0,1:34:23.15,1:34:25.49,ENG,,0,0,0,,We have one helicopter. It holds seven people.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:25.36,1:34:27.59,CHT,,0,0,0,,載6人到高地
Dialogue: 0,1:34:25.57,1:34:27.74,ENG,,0,0,0,,We can ferry six people to high ground in West Virginia
Dialogue: 0,1:34:27.70,1:34:29.10,CHT,,0,0,0,,送珍妮上方舟
Dialogue: 0,1:34:27.82,1:34:30.74,ENG,,0,0,0,,and take Jenny to the Ark. Short stick goes.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:29.20,1:34:30.90,CHT,,0,0,0,,短簽抽中
Dialogue: 0,1:34:31.57,1:34:33.66,CHT,,0,0,0,,不是婦孺優先？
Dialogue: 0,1:34:31.75,1:34:33.75,ENG,,0,0,0,,I always thought it was women and children first.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:33.77,1:34:35.76,CHT,,0,0,0,,抽中可以放棄權利
Dialogue: 0,1:34:33.83,1:34:37.12,ENG,,0,0,0,,If you get the short one, you can give up your seat.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:38.54,1:34:40.03,CHT,,0,0,0,,謝天謝地
Dialogue: 0,1:34:38.63,1:34:39.96,ENG,,0,0,0,,Thank God.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:47.75,1:34:49.12,CHT,,0,0,0,,倒楣透了
Dialogue: 0,1:34:48.01,1:34:49.93,ENG,,0,0,0,,Well, that makes sense.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:51.93,1:34:54.62,CHT,,0,0,0,,我抽中了
Dialogue: 0,1:34:52.06,1:34:54.60,ENG,,0,0,0,,I got a stick. I got a stick.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:03.20,1:35:04.19,CHT,,0,0,0,,貝絲，抱歉
Dialogue: 0,1:35:03.40,1:35:06.32,ENG,,0,0,0,,- I'm sorry, Beth. - Okay, honey, here we go.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:04.30,1:35:06.07,CHT,,0,0,0,,我們走
Dialogue: 0,1:35:07.04,1:35:08.34,CHT,,0,0,0,,走了
Dialogue: 0,1:35:07.28,1:35:08.74,ENG,,0,0,0,,Let's go now.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:10.58,1:35:12.87,ENG,,0,0,0,,- Beth. - There's always the road.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:11.11,1:35:13.48,CHT,,0,0,0,,還有道路，沒事的
Dialogue: 0,1:35:12.95,1:35:15.91,ENG,,0,0,0,,We'll be okay. Come on. That's my girl.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:13.58,1:35:15.78,CHT,,0,0,0,,走了，好乖
Dialogue: 0,1:35:18.59,1:35:20.45,CHT,,0,0,0,,好，散會
Dialogue: 0,1:35:18.83,1:35:20.46,ENG,,0,0,0,,Okay, that's it.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:29.46,1:35:31.13,CHT,,0,0,0,,莎拉
Dialogue: 0,1:35:29.64,1:35:34.31,ENG,,0,0,0,,Sarah!
Dialogue: 0,1:35:32.87,1:35:34.34,CHT,,0,0,0,,莎拉
Dialogue: 0,1:35:49.16,1:35:51.20,ENG,,0,0,0,,Come on, where's that key?
Dialogue: 0,1:35:49.32,1:35:50.38,CHT,,0,0,0,,鑰匙？
Dialogue: 0,1:35:51.52,1:35:52.54,CHT,,0,0,0,,鑰匙呢？
Dialogue: 0,1:35:51.70,1:35:53.33,ENG,,0,0,0,,Where's the key?
Dialogue: 0,1:36:55.62,1:36:57.15,CHT,,0,0,0,,快！快走！
Dialogue: 0,1:36:55.76,1:36:57.89,ENG,,0,0,0,,Come on, hurry up. Come on.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:57.99,1:36:58.72,CHT,,0,0,0,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,1:36:58.22,1:37:00.43,ENG,,0,0,0,,- No, wait. - What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,1:36:58.82,1:36:59.88,CHT,,0,0,0,,搞什麼！
Dialogue: 0,1:37:02.27,1:37:04.48,ENG,,0,0,0,,Come on, Jenny, we have to go now. We have to go now.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:03.30,1:37:05.86,CHT,,0,0,0,,我們得走了，快啊！
Dialogue: 0,1:37:04.56,1:37:06.19,ENG,,0,0,0,,Come on. Come on!
Dialogue: 0,1:37:11.67,1:37:13.37,CHT,,0,0,0,,貝絲，你幹嘛？珍妮，快啊
Dialogue: 0,1:37:11.99,1:37:13.57,ENG,,0,0,0,,- Beth. Beth, what are you doing? - Jenny, we have to go!
Dialogue: 0,1:37:13.47,1:37:16.34,CHT,,0,0,0,,路上塞車，無法及時逃離
Dialogue: 0,1:37:13.66,1:37:16.24,ENG,,0,0,0,,The road was so crowded, it was obvious we weren't gonna make it,
Dialogue: 0,1:37:16.33,1:37:19.33,ENG,,0,0,0,,so I thought, well, if the wave does come, that we should be here
Dialogue: 0,1:37:16.44,1:37:19.10,CHT,,0,0,0,,巨浪來襲時我們待在這裡
Dialogue: 0,1:37:19.21,1:37:20.24,CHT,,0,0,0,,她喜歡這裡…
Dialogue: 0,1:37:19.41,1:37:23.37,ENG,,0,0,0,,because she likes it here and... l mean, we're on the 15th floor,
Dialogue: 0,1:37:20.35,1:37:25.18,CHT,,0,0,0,,在15樓或許能躲過
Dialogue: 0,1:37:23.46,1:37:25.50,ENG,,0,0,0,,- so maybe we'll be okay. - Come on, honey.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:25.29,1:37:27.31,CHT,,0,0,0,,跟珍妮再見
Dialogue: 0,1:37:25.59,1:37:27.59,ENG,,0,0,0,,- Say goodbye to Jenny. - Jenny, we got no time left.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:27.39,1:37:29.58,CHT,,0,0,0,,快！走了！珍妮，你幹什麼！
Dialogue: 0,1:37:27.67,1:37:30.71,ENG,,0,0,0,,- Jenny, what are you doing? Caitlin! - Move! Come on!
Dialogue: 0,1:37:29.66,1:37:34.99,CHT,,0,0,0,,天啊！凱特琳…
Dialogue: 0,1:37:30.80,1:37:35.09,ENG,,0,0,0,,- Oh, my God, Caitlin! Caitlin! Caitlin! - Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,1:37:39.02,1:37:41.81,ENG,,0,0,0,,Come on, come on. Faster, faster. Come on!
Dialogue: 0,1:37:39.33,1:37:42.13,CHT,,0,0,0,,走！快！…
Dialogue: 0,1:37:42.20,1:37:44.93,CHT,,0,0,0,,珍妮，讓我再抱抱她
Dialogue: 0,1:37:42.39,1:37:43.44,ENG,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,1:37:45.01,1:37:46.67,CHT,,0,0,0,,快！走了…
Dialogue: 0,1:37:45.23,1:37:48.52,ENG,,0,0,0,,Come on, come on! Let's go, let's go! Hang on. There's no room for this.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:47.04,1:37:48.63,CHT,,0,0,0,,不能帶行李
Dialogue: 0,1:37:48.61,1:37:50.98,ENG,,0,0,0,,- You're taking her? Please! - She's going with you!
Dialogue: 0,1:37:49.64,1:37:51.44,CHT,,0,0,0,,她跟你走
Dialogue: 0,1:37:51.07,1:37:52.49,ENG,,0,0,0,,- What? - You're taking my seat!
Dialogue: 0,1:37:51.55,1:37:52.98,CHT,,0,0,0,,我的位子讓你
Dialogue: 0,1:37:52.57,1:37:55.41,ENG,,0,0,0,,- Let's go! Come on! - Go, go.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:53.21,1:37:54.11,CHT,,0,0,0,,快！
Dialogue: 0,1:37:54.35,1:37:57.22,CHT,,0,0,0,,快去
Dialogue: 0,1:37:55.49,1:37:57.37,ENG,,0,0,0,,- Jenny, thank you. - Let's go. Come on. Go!
Dialogue: 0,1:37:57.29,1:37:58.55,CHT,,0,0,0,,讓她上機
Dialogue: 0,1:37:57.45,1:37:59.70,ENG,,0,0,0,,- Get her in. Get her in there. - Wait, that's too many.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:58.65,1:38:00.38,CHT,,0,0,0,,太多人了    我不走
Dialogue: 0,1:37:59.79,1:38:01.75,ENG,,0,0,0,,- I'm not going. - What do you mean, you're not going?
Dialogue: 0,1:38:00.46,1:38:03.39,CHT,,0,0,0,,什麼意思？  我不走！
Dialogue: 0,1:38:01.83,1:38:04.75,ENG,,0,0,0,,I'm not going, Eric. Go!
Dialogue: 0,1:38:03.99,1:38:05.15,CHT,,0,0,0,,快走！
Dialogue: 0,1:38:12.01,1:38:13.38,ENG,,0,0,0,,Oh, my God.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:01.56,1:39:03.18,ENG,,0,0,0,,Shove it, buddy!
Dialogue: 0,1:39:07.83,1:39:08.99,CHT,,0,0,0,,莎拉
Dialogue: 0,1:39:08.06,1:39:11.82,ENG,,0,0,0,,Sarah!
Dialogue: 0,1:39:10.44,1:39:11.87,CHT,,0,0,0,,莎拉…
Dialogue: 0,1:39:30.42,1:39:32.21,ENG,,0,0,0,,You're so full of it!
Dialogue: 0,1:39:32.73,1:39:33.75,CHT,,0,0,0,,莎拉，看！
Dialogue: 0,1:39:33.05,1:39:34.71,ENG,,0,0,0,,- Sarah, look! - Leo!
Dialogue: 0,1:39:33.86,1:39:35.35,CHT,,0,0,0,,里歐
Dialogue: 0,1:39:40.57,1:39:43.44,CHT,,0,0,0,,里歐，里歐畢德曼
Dialogue: 0,1:39:40.76,1:39:41.85,ENG,,0,0,0,,Leo!
Dialogue: 0,1:39:42.22,1:39:43.64,ENG,,0,0,0,,Leo Biederman! Leo!
Dialogue: 0,1:39:47.02,1:39:48.06,ENG,,0,0,0,,Leo!
Dialogue: 0,1:39:47.04,1:39:48.13,CHT,,0,0,0,,里歐
Dialogue: 0,1:39:55.86,1:39:57.44,ENG,,0,0,0,,- Leo! - Thank God.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:56.12,1:39:57.18,CHT,,0,0,0,,謝天謝地
Dialogue: 0,1:39:59.42,1:40:01.18,CHT,,0,0,0,,沒時間了，快離開
Dialogue: 0,1:39:59.45,1:40:01.37,ENG,,0,0,0,,You don't have any time. You have to go now.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:01.29,1:40:02.45,CHT,,0,0,0,,穿上
Dialogue: 0,1:40:01.45,1:40:02.66,ENG,,0,0,0,,- Dad. No, no, no. - Put this on, put this on.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:02.56,1:40:04.58,CHT,,0,0,0,,爸，爸，你幹什麼？
Dialogue: 0,1:40:02.74,1:40:05.16,ENG,,0,0,0,,Daddy. Daddy, what are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,1:40:05.46,1:40:08.33,CHT,,0,0,0,,你帶著嬰兒不…媽
Dialogue: 0,1:40:05.62,1:40:08.46,ENG,,0,0,0,,- I want you to take the baby. - Why? No, no, no, no, no, Mom.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:08.43,1:40:10.90,CHT,,0,0,0,,別爭了，拜託    不…
Dialogue: 0,1:40:08.54,1:40:11.67,ENG,,0,0,0,,- Yes. No arguments, Sarah. Please! - No, no, no, no, no. I don't wanna go!
Dialogue: 0,1:40:11.00,1:40:13.19,CHT,,0,0,0,,我不要走  你必須走
Dialogue: 0,1:40:11.75,1:40:14.46,ENG,,0,0,0,,- I don't wanna go! - Grab his foot, honey.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:19.78,1:40:21.71,CHT,,0,0,0,,媽…
Dialogue: 0,1:40:20.09,1:40:21.89,ENG,,0,0,0,,- Mom, Mom. - Come on. No, listen to me.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:21.81,1:40:25.04,CHT,,0,0,0,,甜心，聽我說，戴上！我愛你
Dialogue: 0,1:40:21.97,1:40:24.55,ENG,,0,0,0,,Sweetheart, listen to me. Let go. Put this on!
Dialogue: 0,1:40:24.64,1:40:26.43,ENG,,0,0,0,,- I love you. - I love you, too.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:25.15,1:40:25.91,CHT,,0,0,0,,我也愛你
Dialogue: 0,1:40:26.45,1:40:27.64,CHT,,0,0,0,,我永遠愛你
Dialogue: 0,1:40:26.52,1:40:29.06,ENG,,0,0,0,,- I've always loved you. - I love you.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:28.05,1:40:29.14,CHT,,0,0,0,,我愛你
Dialogue: 0,1:40:29.25,1:40:30.74,CHT,,0,0,0,,我不要走
Dialogue: 0,1:40:30.85,1:40:31.91,CHT,,0,0,0,,保重
Dialogue: 0,1:40:31.15,1:40:32.85,ENG,,0,0,0,,- Take care, honey. - I'll see you soon.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:32.26,1:40:33.55,CHT,,0,0,0,,再見了
Dialogue: 0,1:40:32.94,1:40:36.40,ENG,,0,0,0,,- Put this on. - I'll see you soon. I'll see you soon.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:33.76,1:40:36.75,CHT,,0,0,0,,再見…
Dialogue: 0,1:40:36.61,1:40:37.78,ENG,,0,0,0,,- Yes, you will. - Get out of here, Leo.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:36.86,1:40:39.73,CHT,,0,0,0,,里歐，快走，到高地去
Dialogue: 0,1:40:37.86,1:40:39.74,ENG,,0,0,0,,Go. Go to high ground.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:55.91,1:42:00.47,CHT,,0,0,0,,我11歲時偷拿過你皮夾裡的32元
Dialogue: 0,1:41:56.11,1:41:59.52,ENG,,0,0,0,,When I was 11, I took $32 from your wallet.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:04.72,1:42:06.88,CHT,,0,0,0,,你嬰兒時…
Dialogue: 0,1:42:04.86,1:42:06.66,ENG,,0,0,0,,When you were a baby,
Dialogue: 0,1:42:07.72,1:42:11.56,CHT,,0,0,0,,我失手害你摔到頭
Dialogue: 0,1:42:07.78,1:42:10.29,ENG,,0,0,0,,I once dropped you on your head.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:17.80,1:42:20.96,CHT,,0,0,0,,你那天帶照片來
Dialogue: 0,1:42:17.92,1:42:21.13,ENG,,0,0,0,,When you came to the studio and you brought those pictures,
Dialogue: 0,1:42:21.07,1:42:23.44,CHT,,0,0,0,,我騙你說我不記得
Dialogue: 0,1:42:21.21,1:42:23.84,ENG,,0,0,0,,I lied when I said I didn't remember.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:24.94,1:42:27.31,CHT,,0,0,0,,我都記得
Dialogue: 0,1:42:25.18,1:42:27.05,ENG,,0,0,0,,I remember everything.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:27.41,1:42:30.64,CHT,,0,0,0,,我們當時在那裡
Dialogue: 0,1:42:27.51,1:42:30.18,ENG,,0,0,0,,I remember that we were right over there
Dialogue: 0,1:42:30.26,1:42:33.48,ENG,,0,0,0,,and that's when Mom got that picture of the house.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:30.75,1:42:33.74,CHT,,0,0,0,,媽以房子為背景拍照
Dialogue: 0,1:42:36.32,1:42:39.55,CHT,,0,0,0,,快樂的一天
Dialogue: 0,1:42:36.40,1:42:38.98,ENG,,0,0,0,,It was a perfect, happy day.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:42.02,1:42:44.99,CHT,,0,0,0,,我來告訴你這件事
Dialogue: 0,1:42:42.24,1:42:44.86,ENG,,0,0,0,,I came down here to let you know that.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:45.09,1:42:46.43,CHT,,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,1:42:45.24,1:42:46.57,ENG,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:51.93,1:42:54.23,CHT,,0,0,0,,我一直想念你
Dialogue: 0,1:42:52.12,1:42:54.25,ENG,,0,0,0,,I've missed you since then.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:02.48,1:43:04.47,CHT,,0,0,0,,我也想你
Dialogue: 0,1:43:02.71,1:43:04.38,ENG,,0,0,0,,I missed you, too.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:34.11,1:43:35.34,CHT,,0,0,0,,畢德曼彗星
Dialogue: 0,1:43:34.16,1:43:35.50,ENG,,0,0,0,,Biederman.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:37.88,1:44:39.14,CHT,,0,0,0,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,1:44:38.02,1:44:39.23,ENG,,0,0,0,,Daddy.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:08.01,1:45:12.57,CHT,,0,0,0,,“維吉尼亞海灘，6英哩”
Dialogue: 0,1:45:25.16,1:45:26.06,CHT,,0,0,0,,抓緊
Dialogue: 0,1:45:25.44,1:45:26.69,ENG,,0,0,0,,Hold on.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:21.19,1:46:24.10,CHT,,0,0,0,,彌賽亞號呼叫，將接近彗星
Dialogue: 0,1:46:21.29,1:46:24.21,ENG,,0,0,0,,This is Messiah. We're ready to begin our run.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:24.20,1:46:25.99,CHT,,0,0,0,,我們家屬到了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,1:46:24.29,1:46:27.75,ENG,,0,0,0,,- Are our families there yet? - They're on their way, Messiah.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:26.10,1:46:27.57,CHT,,0,0,0,,正在路上
Dialogue: 0,1:46:31.61,1:46:33.87,CHT,,0,0,0,,取消自動裝置
Dialogue: 0,1:46:31.63,1:46:33.42,ENG,,0,0,0,,Disengage auto path.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:34.94,1:46:36.20,CHT,,0,0,0,,出發了
Dialogue: 0,1:46:35.18,1:46:36.55,ENG,,0,0,0,,Here we go.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:40.11,1:46:41.34,CHT,,0,0,0,,最近點
Dialogue: 0,1:46:40.31,1:46:44.06,ENG,,0,0,0,,We're at perigee. Wolf contact in four minutes, 45 seconds.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:41.45,1:46:44.32,CHT,,0,0,0,,4分45秒接觸沃夫
Dialogue: 0,1:46:45.02,1:46:48.61,CHT,,0,0,0,,再不能離家這麼近了
Dialogue: 0,1:46:45.19,1:46:48.48,ENG,,0,0,0,,We'll never be closer to home than we are right now.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:07.17,1:47:08.25,ENG,,0,0,0,,Come on.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:08.08,1:47:10.64,CHT,,0,0,0,,彌賽亞號，有家屬趕來了
Dialogue: 0,1:47:08.33,1:47:12.00,ENG,,0,0,0,,Messiah, we've got some people here that wanna talk to you.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:12.72,1:47:14.05,CHT,,0,0,0,,親愛的溫蒂
Dialogue: 0,1:47:12.84,1:47:14.34,ENG,,0,0,0,,Wendy, honey.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:15.72,1:47:19.52,CHT,,0,0,0,,答應我繼續去教堂
Dialogue: 0,1:47:15.84,1:47:19.05,ENG,,0,0,0,,You promise me you keep doing your church thing,
Dialogue: 0,1:47:20.39,1:47:24.02,CHT,,0,0,0,,我會去，在你身旁
Dialogue: 0,1:47:20.51,1:47:23.31,ENG,,0,0,0,,and I'll be there, right next to you,
Dialogue: 0,1:47:24.53,1:47:25.93,CHT,,0,0,0,,陰魂不散
Dialogue: 0,1:47:24.81,1:47:26.27,ENG,,0,0,0,,haunting you.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:28.00,1:47:30.93,CHT,,0,0,0,,你一定要來
Dialogue: 0,1:47:28.15,1:47:30.56,ENG,,0,0,0,,You better come back and haunt me.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:31.19,1:47:32.57,ENG,,0,0,0,,I love you.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:31.23,1:47:32.72,CHT,,0,0,0,,我愛你
Dialogue: 0,1:47:34.84,1:47:37.57,CHT,,0,0,0,,看！是媽
Dialogue: 0,1:47:35.03,1:47:37.24,ENG,,0,0,0,,There's Mommy. Hello, Mommy.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:38.53,1:47:41.57,ENG,,0,0,0,,Hey, you'll take care of Daddy for me, okay?
Dialogue: 0,1:47:40.11,1:47:41.77,CHT,,0,0,0,,替我照顧爸爸
Dialogue: 0,1:47:41.66,1:47:44.95,ENG,,0,0,0,,She will. She does a good job. She misses Mommy.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:41.88,1:47:44.68,CHT,,0,0,0,,她很乖，她想媽媽
Dialogue: 0,1:47:44.78,1:47:46.15,CHT,,0,0,0,,我想你
Dialogue: 0,1:47:45.04,1:47:48.04,ENG,,0,0,0,,- I miss you. - I love you, Mommy.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:46.35,1:47:48.25,CHT,,0,0,0,,我愛你，媽
Dialogue: 0,1:47:48.72,1:47:52.02,CHT,,0,0,0,,我非常愛你
Dialogue: 0,1:47:48.87,1:47:51.38,ENG,,0,0,0,,I love you very, very much.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:53.72,1:47:55.25,CHT,,0,0,0,,大衛
Dialogue: 0,1:47:53.88,1:47:55.13,ENG,,0,0,0,,David.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:58.36,1:48:00.49,CHT,,0,0,0,,你知道我要說的
Dialogue: 0,1:47:58.47,1:48:00.51,ENG,,0,0,0,,You know what I wanna say.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:00.60,1:48:01.90,CHT,,0,0,0,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,1:48:00.64,1:48:01.85,ENG,,0,0,0,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:10.44,1:48:12.67,CHT,,0,0,0,,莎拉，快！
Dialogue: 0,1:48:12.02,1:48:13.23,ENG,,0,0,0,,Come on!
Dialogue: 0,1:48:13.48,1:48:16.34,CHT,,0,0,0,,沃夫彗星2分30秒後接觸
Dialogue: 0,1:48:13.57,1:48:16.28,ENG,,0,0,0,,Wolf contact in two minutes, 30 seconds.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:17.72,1:48:19.01,CHT,,0,0,0,,歐仁
Dialogue: 0,1:48:17.90,1:48:21.61,ENG,,0,0,0,,Oren, Mariette's at your folks' place up in Utah.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:19.18,1:48:21.68,CHT,,0,0,0,,瑪莉葉現在猶他州
Dialogue: 0,1:48:21.70,1:48:24.41,ENG,,0,0,0,,We sent a plane for her, but she isn't here yet.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:21.79,1:48:24.52,CHT,,0,0,0,,已派飛機去還沒趕到
Dialogue: 0,1:48:24.49,1:48:27.04,ENG,,0,0,0,,Fish, your sons are both on active duty.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:24.62,1:48:28.79,CHT,,0,0,0,,小魚，你兒子在當班
Dialogue: 0,1:48:27.12,1:48:31.00,ENG,,0,0,0,,We tried to get them back, but we couldn't get them here on time.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:28.89,1:48:32.19,CHT,,0,0,0,,已聯絡他們無法趕到，抱歉
Dialogue: 0,1:48:31.08,1:48:32.42,ENG,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:34.07,1:48:39.37,CHT,,0,0,0,,米奇，我要跟瑪麗說再見
Dialogue: 0,1:48:34.25,1:48:38.13,ENG,,0,0,0,,Well, Mitch, I wanna say goodbye to Mary.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:39.57,1:48:41.51,CHT,,0,0,0,,告訴她我愛她
Dialogue: 0,1:48:39.68,1:48:41.55,ENG,,0,0,0,,I wanna tell her I love her,
Dialogue: 0,1:48:41.61,1:48:46.41,CHT,,0,0,0,,分開後我天天都想她
Dialogue: 0,1:48:41.64,1:48:45.72,ENG,,0,0,0,,and that ever since we've been apart, every day I think about her.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:47.91,1:48:49.44,CHT,,0,0,0,,瑪麗，我回來了
Dialogue: 0,1:48:48.14,1:48:50.02,ENG,,0,0,0,,Mary, I'm coming home.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:51.52,1:48:54.65,CHT,,0,0,0,,接近目標，625英哩
Dialogue: 0,1:48:51.60,1:48:54.19,ENG,,0,0,0,,Coming up on target, 625 miles.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:57.06,1:48:59.22,CHT,,0,0,0,,射程，600英哩
Dialogue: 0,1:48:57.23,1:48:58.86,ENG,,0,0,0,,Range, 600 miles.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:01.63,1:49:04.32,CHT,,0,0,0,,等一下…等等！
Dialogue: 0,1:49:01.70,1:49:04.07,ENG,,0,0,0,,Wait. Oh, God, wait!
Dialogue: 0,1:49:06.83,1:49:09.70,CHT,,0,0,0,,等一下！我來了
Dialogue: 0,1:49:06.95,1:49:09.41,ENG,,0,0,0,,Wait! I'm coming.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:12.54,1:49:13.20,CHT,,0,0,0,,歐仁
Dialogue: 0,1:49:12.92,1:49:14.29,ENG,,0,0,0,,Oren!
Dialogue: 0,1:49:14.14,1:49:15.84,CHT,,0,0,0,,歐仁，聽得到嗎？
Dialogue: 0,1:49:14.38,1:49:15.96,ENG,,0,0,0,,Oren, are you there?
Dialogue: 0,1:49:16.41,1:49:19.74,CHT,,0,0,0,,瑪莉葉，我聽得到
Dialogue: 0,1:49:16.59,1:49:19.55,ENG,,0,0,0,,Mariette? I'm here. I can hear you.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:20.25,1:49:21.61,CHT,,0,0,0,,甜心
Dialogue: 0,1:49:20.38,1:49:21.80,ENG,,0,0,0,,Hi, sweetie.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:21.82,1:49:24.91,CHT,,0,0,0,,瑪莉葉寶貝，是爸爸
Dialogue: 0,1:49:21.93,1:49:24.51,ENG,,0,0,0,,- Mariette? - Baby, this is your father.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:25.75,1:49:28.55,CHT,,0,0,0,,他叫歐仁，以你為名
Dialogue: 0,1:49:26.01,1:49:28.72,ENG,,0,0,0,,His name is Oren. I named him after you.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:28.66,1:49:30.12,CHT,,0,0,0,,歐仁，你好
Dialogue: 0,1:49:28.81,1:49:30.23,ENG,,0,0,0,,Hello, Oren.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:30.99,1:49:32.32,CHT,,0,0,0,,給爸爸看
Dialogue: 0,1:49:31.06,1:49:33.94,ENG,,0,0,0,,- Show him what you brought him. - What happened?
Dialogue: 0,1:49:32.43,1:49:33.66,CHT,,0,0,0,,是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,1:49:34.31,1:49:36.65,ENG,,0,0,0,,He's holding up a little rocket.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:34.36,1:49:36.42,CHT,,0,0,0,,是玩具火箭
Dialogue: 0,1:49:38.11,1:49:40.94,ENG,,0,0,0,,That's a mighty powerful rocket you got there.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:38.13,1:49:40.62,CHT,,0,0,0,,你的火箭威力強大
Dialogue: 0,1:49:41.03,1:49:42.53,ENG,,0,0,0,,He's laughing.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:41.07,1:49:42.40,CHT,,0,0,0,,他笑了
Dialogue: 0,1:49:43.27,1:49:44.97,CHT,,0,0,0,,我聽到了
Dialogue: 0,1:49:43.49,1:49:45.41,ENG,,0,0,0,,I can hear him. I know.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:45.51,1:49:46.70,CHT,,0,0,0,,瑪莉葉
Dialogue: 0,1:49:45.78,1:49:49.49,ENG,,0,0,0,,Mariette, I'm hugging you both right now.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:47.81,1:49:51.75,CHT,,0,0,0,,我正擁抱著你們擁抱著你們
Dialogue: 0,1:49:50.54,1:49:52.16,ENG,,0,0,0,,I'm holding you.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:53.42,1:49:54.71,CHT,,0,0,0,,25秒
Dialogue: 0,1:49:53.54,1:49:56.42,ENG,,0,0,0,,- Twenty-five seconds. - Prepare to synchronize the nukes.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:54.98,1:49:56.32,CHT,,0,0,0,,四枚核彈同時引爆
Dialogue: 0,1:49:56.49,1:49:57.62,CHT,,0,0,0,,23
Dialogue: 0,1:49:56.50,1:50:01.34,ENG,,0,0,0,,Twenty-three, 22, 21,
Dialogue: 0,1:49:58.52,1:49:59.56,CHT,,0,0,0,,22
Dialogue: 0,1:50:00.49,1:50:01.46,CHT,,0,0,0,,21
Dialogue: 0,1:50:02.83,1:50:03.79,CHT,,0,0,0,,20
Dialogue: 0,1:50:02.84,1:50:07.43,ENG,,0,0,0,,20, 19, 18,
Dialogue: 0,1:50:04.89,1:50:07.52,CHT,,0,0,0,,19、18
Dialogue: 0,1:50:08.63,1:50:13.13,CHT,,0,0,0,,17、16、15
Dialogue: 0,1:50:08.81,1:50:12.89,ENG,,0,0,0,,17, 16, 15...
Dialogue: 0,1:50:15.00,1:50:17.50,CHT,,0,0,0,,很榮幸與你共事，指揮官
Dialogue: 0,1:50:15.19,1:50:18.36,ENG,,0,0,0,,it's been a pleasure serving with you, Commander.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:19.44,1:50:21.43,CHT,,0,0,0,,是我的榮幸
Dialogue: 0,1:50:19.61,1:50:21.69,ENG,,0,0,0,,The honor's all mine, Andy.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:27.12,1:50:29.68,CHT,,0,0,0,,要乖喔，歐仁
Dialogue: 0,1:50:27.12,1:50:29.24,ENG,,0,0,0,,Be good, Oren.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:32.36,1:50:33.75,CHT,,0,0,0,,要乖喔
Dialogue: 0,1:50:32.54,1:50:33.79,ENG,,0,0,0,,Be good.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:44.80,1:51:48.20,CHT,,0,0,0,,核彈炸碎的彗星殞石
Dialogue: 0,1:51:44.94,1:51:47.90,ENG,,0,0,0,,We watched as the bombs shattered the second comet
Dialogue: 0,1:51:47.99,1:51:49.91,ENG,,0,0,0,,into a million pieces of ice and rock
Dialogue: 0,1:51:48.30,1:51:50.36,CHT,,0,0,0,,如雨落下
Dialogue: 0,1:51:49.99,1:51:52.33,ENG,,0,0,0,,that burned harmlessly in our atmosphere
Dialogue: 0,1:51:50.47,1:51:54.34,CHT,,0,0,0,,照亮天空
Dialogue: 0,1:51:52.41,1:51:54.70,ENG,,0,0,0,,and lit up the sky for an hour.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:55.88,1:51:59.31,CHT,,0,0,0,,地球仍遭小彗星蹂躪
Dialogue: 0,1:51:56.08,1:51:59.50,ENG,,0,0,0,,Still, we were left with the devastation of the first.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:59.98,1:52:02.51,CHT,,0,0,0,,海水倒灌至俄亥俄
Dialogue: 0,1:52:00.21,1:52:04.34,ENG,,0,0,0,,The waters reached as far inland as the Ohio and Tennessee valleys.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:02.62,1:52:04.38,CHT,,0,0,0,,與田納西州
Dialogue: 0,1:52:04.89,1:52:08.08,CHT,,0,0,0,,沖垮了農村和城市
Dialogue: 0,1:52:05.13,1:52:07.88,ENG,,0,0,0,,It washed away farms and towns,
Dialogue: 0,1:52:08.26,1:52:11.38,CHT,,0,0,0,,森林…和摩天大樓
Dialogue: 0,1:52:08.51,1:52:10.97,ENG,,0,0,0,,forests and skyscrapers.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:12.29,1:52:16.63,CHT,,0,0,0,,但海水退去了
Dialogue: 0,1:52:12.47,1:52:16.14,ENG,,0,0,0,,But the water receded.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:17.83,1:52:20.46,CHT,,0,0,0,,海嘯也襲擊歐洲、非洲
Dialogue: 0,1:52:17.98,1:52:20.52,ENG,,0,0,0,,The wave hit Europe and Africa, too.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:20.80,1:52:23.33,CHT,,0,0,0,,上百萬人失蹤
Dialogue: 0,1:52:21.06,1:52:22.81,ENG,,0,0,0,,Millions were lost,
Dialogue: 0,1:52:24.24,1:52:27.17,CHT,,0,0,0,,無家可歸者不計其數
Dialogue: 0,1:52:24.53,1:52:26.73,ENG,,0,0,0,,countless more left homeless.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:28.91,1:52:32.54,CHT,,0,0,0,,但海水退去了
Dialogue: 0,1:52:29.15,1:52:31.86,ENG,,0,0,0,,But the waters receded.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:34.32,1:52:36.68,CHT,,0,0,0,,城市淹沒
Dialogue: 0,1:52:34.58,1:52:36.20,ENG,,0,0,0,,Cities fall,
Dialogue: 0,1:52:38.05,1:52:40.45,CHT,,0,0,0,,能再重建
Dialogue: 0,1:52:38.16,1:52:40.00,ENG,,0,0,0,,but they are rebuilt.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:40.59,1:52:42.56,CHT,,0,0,0,,英雄捐軀
Dialogue: 0,1:52:40.71,1:52:42.25,ENG,,0,0,0,,And heroes die,
Dialogue: 0,1:52:43.36,1:52:46.35,CHT,,0,0,0,,名垂千古
Dialogue: 0,1:52:43.54,1:52:45.67,ENG,,0,0,0,,but they are remembered.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:46.90,1:52:49.83,CHT,,0,0,0,,每塊重建的磚瓦
Dialogue: 0,1:52:47.13,1:52:49.76,ENG,,0,0,0,,We honor them with every brick we lay,
Dialogue: 0,1:52:50.07,1:52:52.97,CHT,,0,0,0,,每粒希望的種子
Dialogue: 0,1:52:50.30,1:52:52.26,ENG,,0,0,0,,with every field we sow,
Dialogue: 0,1:52:53.07,1:52:55.20,CHT,,0,0,0,,撫慰孩童的心靈
Dialogue: 0,1:52:53.30,1:52:57.10,ENG,,0,0,0,,with every child we comfort and then teach to rejoice
Dialogue: 0,1:52:55.30,1:52:57.00,CHT,,0,0,0,,教導他們不忘感恩
Dialogue: 0,1:52:57.11,1:52:59.77,CHT,,0,0,0,,珍惜失而復得的…
Dialogue: 0,1:52:57.18,1:52:59.39,ENG,,0,0,0,,in what we have been re-given.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:01.81,1:53:03.34,CHT,,0,0,0,,我們的星球
Dialogue: 0,1:53:02.02,1:53:03.40,ENG,,0,0,0,,Our planet.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:05.75,1:53:07.38,CHT,,0,0,0,,我們的家
Dialogue: 0,1:53:06.02,1:53:07.28,ENG,,0,0,0,,Our home.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:10.42,1:53:14.02,CHT,,0,0,0,,大家攜手…重建家園
Dialogue: 0,1:53:10.53,1:53:13.57,ENG,,0,0,0,,So now, let us begin.
